NK132(no)001:1: // bzang spyod smon 'grel 'phags mchog gsang mdzod bzhugs so //
NK132(no)001:3: 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa smon lam gyi rgyal
NK132(no)001:4: po'i rgya cher 'grel pa 'phags mchog rnams kyi gsang
NK132(no)001:6: de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'phags pa kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:7: 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa smon lam gyi rgyal po'i don cung zad bshang bar bya ste /
NK132(no)001:8: de la 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam
NK132(no)001:9: thams cad yongs su 'dus pa smon lam gyi mdo
NK132(no)001:11: tshigs bcad 'di nyid logs su byung ba mdo sde rang rkang tshugs pa zhig tu yang 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:12: spyir ni 'phags pa sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK132(no)001:14: 'phags pa sdong po bkod pa'i mdo zhes bya ba /
NK132(no)001:15: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rab 'byams mtha' yas ston pa zhig ste /
NK132(no)001:16: dam tshig gsum bkod kyi rtog pa las /
NK132(no)001:17: theg pa chen po'i mdo sde mchog tu basngagasa so //
NK132(no)001:18: mdo sde de nyid kyi mjug gi cha la gnas pa las smon lam 'di phyung ba'o //
NK132(no)001:19: logs su bzhugs pa la mdo sde rang rkang tshugs par 'gyur pa dang /
NK132(no)001:20: tshig de nyid mdo sde rgyas pa gzhan gyi nang na yod pa yang mi 'gal te /
NK132(no)001:21: 'phags pa tshigs bcad gcig pa dang /
NK132(no)001:23: sher phyin brgya lnga bcu pa dang /
NK132(no)001:24: sgo nyer lnga pa la sogs pa mdo rgyud du mar snang ba bzhin no //
NK132(no)001:25: de yang spyir sdong po bkod pa yongs rdzogs kyi
NK132(no)001:26: dbang du byas na ni 'byam klas pa zhig yod
NK132(no)001:27: pa las / deng sang dzam bu'i gling du spyad pa 'di ni /
NK132(no)001:28: nor bzang gis dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten tshul phyogs gcig pa ste /
NK132(no)001:29: 'on kyang 'di kho na'i don tsam yang gzhal bar daka'o //
NK132(no)001:30: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK132(no)001:31: dag pa'i sa la gnas nges pa zhig tshong dpon
NK132(no)001:33: nor bzang zhes bya ba zhig gis /
NK132(no)001:34: 'phags pa 'jam dpal nas byams pa'i bar gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten te /
NK132(no)001:35: mthar dpag tshad brgya rtsa bcu'i pha rol nas 'jam dpal gyi phyag brkyang ba /
NK132(no)001:36: grong khyer yid bde ba mngon du gyur pa zhes
NK132(no)001:37: bya ba na nor bzang yod pa'i spyi bor bzhag
NK132(no)001:38: ste ched du brjod pa mdzad do //
NK132(no)001:39: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu nor bzang ye shes kyi spyod yul mtha' yas pa thob pa /
NK132(no)001:40: 'jam dpal gyi byin rlabs kyis kun tu bzang po'i
NK132(no)001:41: spyod pa'i dkyil 'khor la 'jug nus par byin gyis
NK132(no)001:42: brlabs shing / rdo rje rin po che pad+ma'i gdan la bzhag ste /
NK132(no)001:43: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi seng ge'i khri la mngon du phyogs par 'dug go //
NK132(no)001:44: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK132(no)001:45: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po mthong bar 'gyur ba'i
NK132(no)001:46: ltas ngo mtshar mtha' yas pa bcu tshan gnyis nor
NK132(no)001:48: de nas 'phags pa kun tu bzang po nyid mthong
NK132(no)001:49: na thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob pa dang 'dra
NK132(no)001:51: skad cig de nyid las ye shes mtha' yas pa 'phel bar gyur te /
NK132(no)001:52: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyang mngon sum du mthong /
NK132(no)001:53: de'i spyan snga na byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad kyang mthong /
NK132(no)001:54: de nas byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po
NK132(no)001:55: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang mnyam pa nyid
NK132(no)001:56: rjes su thob pa de yang rin chen pad+ma'i khri
NK132(no)001:58: de'i ba spu'i khung bu re re nas kyang 'jig
NK132(no)001:59: rten gyi khams thams cad kyi rdul shin tu phra
NK132(no)001:60: ba snyed kyi 'od zer gyi sprin mang po thon
NK132(no)001:61: nas / nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa snang bar byas te /
NK132(no)001:62: sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal rab tu zhi
NK132(no)001:63: bar byed pa la sogs pa rnam par thar pa
NK132(no)001:64: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i cho 'phrul chen po'i nyi
NK132(no)001:66: de nas nor bzang dga' ba dang yid bde ba skyes nas /
NK132(no)001:67: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i sku lus kyi cha shas rnam par phye nas /
NK132(no)001:68: mthar ba spu'i khung bu gcig la yang /
NK132(no)001:69: dbus su mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams dang bcas
NK132(no)001:70: pa'i phyogs bcu rab 'byams mu med pa'i 'jig rten
NK132(no)001:71: gyi khams kyi bkod pa mtha' dag dang de dag
NK132(no)001:72: kyang / bskal pa chags pa dang 'jig pa'i bar gyi tshul rnams ma lus pa /
NK132(no)001:73: gzugs brnyan gyi tshul du mthong ngo //
NK132(no)001:74: skabs 'di na 'dod pa'i khams kyi yul dang bcas /
NK132(no)001:75: gzugs kyi khams kyi yul dang bcas /
NK132(no)001:76: gzugs med pa'i khams kyi yul dang bcas /
NK132(no)001:82: gzugs med khams la snod kyi 'jig rten yod pa'i tshigs yang dang yang du 'byung bas /
NK132(no)001:83: gzugs med ces pa dman pa la dgag pa'i sgra'o //
NK132(no)001:84: kun tu bzang po de'i mtshan bzang bo re re
NK132(no)001:85: la yang sngon gyi mtha' mur thug pa'i bar gyi
NK132(no)001:86: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad dang /
NK132(no)001:87: sangs rgyas rnams dang 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor yang bstan /
NK132(no)001:88: phyi ma'i mu mthar thug gi bar gyi yang bstan /
NK132(no)001:89: sangs rgyas re re'i drung na kun tu bzang po re re yang 'dug /
NK132(no)001:90: de dag gi lus re re la yang dus gsum
NK132(no)001:91: du byung ba'i shes bya thams cad kyi gzugs brnyan
NK132(no)001:92: yang mngon par bstan par mthong /
NK132(no)001:93: de nas kun tu bzang po nyid kyi da lta
NK132(no)001:94: rnam par 'phrul pa mtha' yas pas 'gro ba'i don
NK132(no)001:95: spyod tshul dang / sangs rgyas mnyes par byed tshul /
NK132(no)001:96: de dag gi rgyur sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa mtha' yas pa sbyang tshul gsungs te /
NK132(no)001:97: sangs rgyas rnam snang gi spyan snga na bzhugs pa'i
NK132(no)001:98: kun tu bzang pos phyag brkyang ste nor bzang gi
NK132(no)001:100: phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi
NK132(no)001:101: rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi 'jig rten gyi
NK132(no)001:103: sangs rgyas re re'i zhabs 'bring na yang kun tu bzang po re re bzhugs pa'i phyag g.yas pa'ang /
NK132(no)001:104: nor bzang gi spyi bor bzhag par gyur zhing /
NK132(no)001:105: chos kyi sgo mang po sna tshogs la zhugs par gyur to //
NK132(no)001:106: de nas rnam 'phrul de la brten pa'i zhu lan cung zad mdzad nas /
NK132(no)001:107: rnam 'phrul de lta bu'i rgyu spyod pa mtha' yas pa spyad tshul rnams gsungs te /
NK132(no)001:108: nga'i lus rnam par dag pa la ltos shig gsungs nas /
NK132(no)001:109: kun tu bzang po'i ba spu'i khung bu re rer
NK132(no)001:110: yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgya mtsho brjod du med
NK132(no)001:111: pa'i yang brjod du med pa /
NK132(no)001:112: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ston pa la sogs pa mtha' yas pa'ang mthong /
NK132(no)001:113: kun tu bzang po'i gdams ngag dang rjes bstan yang thos nas /
NK132(no)001:114: de'i sku lus kyi khongs su gtogs pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du zhugs nas /
NK132(no)001:115: sems can smin par byed par gyur la /
NK132(no)001:116: de nas nor bzang rang nyid kyis kyang rnam par thar pa mtha' yas pa de thob nas /
NK132(no)001:117: de lta bu ston par gyur to //
NK132(no)001:119: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang pos bskal pa dang /
NK132(no)001:120: bskal pa rgya mtsho 'byams klas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:121: 'jig rten gyi khams gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa /
NK132(no)001:122: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod
NK132(no)001:123: du med pa'i rdul phra ba snying po de dag
NK132(no)001:124: brnan te mngon par brjod pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:125: tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyis smon lam btab pa /
NK132(no)001:126: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na sogs 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)001:127: 'di ni zhing khams rnam par dag par byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:128: rnam par thar pa mtha' yas pa de lta bu thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:129: rjes 'jug rnams kyis kyang smon lam 'di gdab dgos so zhes pa dang /
NK132(no)001:130: 'di'i don bzhin du byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa de ni /
NK132(no)001:131: rnam par thar pa 'di la gdon mi za bar 'jug par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:132: zhes go bar bya ba'i phyir te /
NK132(no)001:133: de yang bskal pa dang bskal pa zhes lan gnyis zlos pa ni /
NK132(no)001:135: bskal pa de tsam du phyogs bcu'i zhing khams brjod
NK132(no)001:136: du med pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul gyi
NK132(no)001:137: grangs dang mnyam pa rnams re re bzhin yang bskal
NK132(no)001:138: pa rgya mtsho 'byam klas pa'i bar du chags 'jig
NK132(no)001:139: gi rim pas spel zhing brgyud nas byung ba /
NK132(no)001:140: de tsam gyi zhing khams thams cad yongs su sbyong ba dang /
NK132(no)001:141: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK132(no)001:142: de thams cad stong pa nyid dang snying rje dang
NK132(no)001:143: thabs la mkhas pa'i ye shes gcig gi ngo bor
NK132(no)001:144: blos yang yang bsdams pa na spyangs smin legs par
NK132(no)001:145: grub cing zhing khams la dbang 'byor ba thob pa
NK132(no)001:146: ni brnan te zhes pa'i don yin no //
NK132(no)001:147: 'di la kun tu bzang po'i smon lam zhes bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:148: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang pos gsungs pa'am /
NK132(no)001:149: bdag gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa thob pas kun tu mdzes pa dang /
NK132(no)001:150: skyon thams cad bral bas kun tu kun nas bzang ba'i phyir sangs rgyas dang /
NK132(no)001:151: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi spyi ming yin la /
NK132(no)001:152: smon lam 'di la yang byang chub kyi spyod pa thams cad 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:153: sangs rgyas byang sems kun gyi smon lam mo //
NK132(no)001:154: yang bzang po spyod pa zhes bya ba ni kun
NK132(no)001:155: tu bzang po spyod pa'i dbang du byas pa dang
NK132(no)001:156: / yang na bzang po yang yin la spyod pa yang yin pa ni bzang po spyod pa ste /
NK132(no)001:157: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa /
NK132(no)001:158: thog mar thos pa'i dus na dge /
NK132(no)001:159: bar du bsam bsgom gyi dus na'ang dge /
NK132(no)001:160: mthar 'bras su sangs rgyas pa'i dus na'ang dge ba'o //
NK132(no)001:161: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' gzhon nu'i sa pa ste /
NK132(no)001:162: rdzi bo lta bur sems bskyed pa'i smon lam zhes kyang zer ro //
NK132(no)001:164: dpal phyogs kyi glang po'i 'grel pa las yan lag bdun po re re nas bgrang ba dang /
NK132(no)001:167: phan yon te don gyi rnam grangs bcu'i bsdus don mdzad do //
NK132(no)001:168: 'dir 'di skad ces byas na bzung bla bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:169: rgyud dag par bya ba yan lag bdun pa /
NK132(no)001:170: dngos gzhi smon lam gyi rab dbye /
NK132(no)001:171: smon lam gyi mtha' dang phan yon bstan pa /
NK132(no)001:172: phan yon can gyi smon lam nyid bsngo ba ste don bzhi las /
NK132(no)001:177: bsod nams la yi rangs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:180: dge ba bsngo ba ste bdun no //
NK132(no)001:183: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK132(no)001:184: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge gang //
NK132(no)001:185: bdag gis ma lus de dag thams cad la //
NK132(no)001:186: lus dang ngag yid dang bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:187: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten ji snyed na su dag bzhugs pa zhes sbyar ste /
NK132(no)001:189: bcu la sogs pa'i grangs tshad can ma yin par /
NK132(no)001:190: phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa na bzhugs pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:191: de yang da ltar bzhugs pa kho nar ma zad kyi /
NK132(no)001:192: dus gsum du gshegs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:193: gshegs pa'i don byung ba yin pas /
NK132(no)001:196: ma 'ongs pa 'byung 'gyur thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:197: su zhig gis phyag 'tshal zhe na /
NK132(no)001:199: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi khyad par dang ldan pa su la phyag 'tshal zhe na /
NK132(no)001:200: mi'i seng ge ni sangs rgyas /
NK132(no)001:202: ma lus pa ste mtha' dag go //
NK132(no)001:203: de dag thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:205: gzhan gyis bskul ba sogs ma yin par /
NK132(no)001:206: rab tu dang ba ste dang ba chen po'i sgo
NK132(no)001:207: nas lus dang ngag dang yid gsum car gyi phyag
NK132(no)001:209: ci'i phyir sangs rgyas la mi yi seng ge zhes bya na /
NK132(no)001:210: seng ge ni ri dwags thams cad zil gyis gnon
NK132(no)001:211: cing bag tsha ba med pa ltar mi'i skye bar
NK132(no)001:212: yang ston la / bdud dang phyir rgol ba sogs /
NK132(no)001:213: lha mi thams cad zil gyis gnon cing /
NK132(no)001:214: rang gi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang phrin las bya ba la bag tsha ba med pa'o //
NK132(no)001:215: mang po la phyag 'tshal ba'i dgos pa ci snyam na /
NK132(no)001:216: sangs rgyas gcig la phyag byas pa'i bsod nams yang
NK132(no)001:217: mtha' yas na sangs rgyas mtha' yas pa la phyag
NK132(no)001:218: 'tshal ba'i bsod nams gzhal du med pa las kyang
NK132(no)001:220: rgyas bshad la gsum las lus kyi phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK132(no)001:221: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam stobs dag gis //
NK132(no)001:222: rgyal ba thams cad yid kyis mngon sum du //
NK132(no)001:223: zhing gi rdul snyed lus rab btud pa yis //
NK132(no)001:224: rgyal ba kun la rab tu phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:225: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam ni /
NK132(no)001:226: bzang po spyod pa la smon pa ste /
NK132(no)001:227: spyod pa de la 'dun pa'i stobs dag gis /
NK132(no)001:228: rgyal ba ste sangs rgyas mngon sum du mthong bar nus kyang rung mi mthong na yang ste /
NK132(no)001:229: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba ma lus thams cad yid kyis mos pas mngon sum du dmigs te /
NK132(no)001:230: de re re'i sku mdun du yang rang gi lus
NK132(no)001:231: zhing ste 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rdul ji snyed
NK132(no)001:232: yod pa de snyed du sprul te /
NK132(no)001:233: lus de dag thams cad rab tu btud pa ste /
NK132(no)001:234: thal mo sbyar zhing yan lag lnga sa la gtugs pa yis /
NK132(no)001:235: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun la rab tu'am shin tu ste /
NK132(no)001:236: dus mtha' yas par yang nas yang du'am rtag tu phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:237: sangs rgyas rnams la ci'i phyir rgyal ba zhes bya na /
NK132(no)001:239: sdig pa mi dge'i chos las nga rgyal te //
NK132(no)001:240: de phyir nyer 'gro nga ni rgyal ba yin //
NK132(no)001:242: lus mang pos phyag 'tshal bar mos pa'i dgos pa yang /
NK132(no)001:243: lus gcig tu 'du shes pas phyag btsal ba yang phan yon che na /
NK132(no)001:244: mtha' yas par mos pas lta ci smos pa'o //
NK132(no)001:245: gnyis pa yid kyi phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK132(no)001:246: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
NK132(no)001:247: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa dag /
NK132(no)001:248: de ltar chos kyi dbyings rnams ma lus pa //
NK132(no)001:249: thams cad rgyal ba dag gis gang bar mos //
NK132(no)001:250: rdul phra rab gcig gi steng ste go sa na yang /
NK132(no)001:251: sangs rgyas kyi zhing ma lus pa'i rdul gyi grangs
NK132(no)001:252: ji snyed pa de snyed dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas
NK132(no)001:254: de yang gcer ba dang dog pa ma yin par /
NK132(no)001:255: sangs rgyas rnams kyang rang gi sras te byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK132(no)001:256: mchod pa'i bkod pa sogs dpag tu med pa dang bcas te /
NK132(no)001:257: zhing khams kyi dbus na bzhugs pa dag yin la /
NK132(no)001:258: rdul gcig na yod pa de bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:259: chos kyi dbyings rnams ma lus pa ste chos kyi
NK132(no)001:260: dbyings kyis ji ltar khyab pa de ltar rdul gyis
NK132(no)001:261: khyab pa thams cad du yang /
NK132(no)001:262: phyogs thams cad rgyal ba mang po dag gis gang bar mos te /
NK132(no)001:263: de dag la yid kyis dad pa bla na med pa sgom mo //
NK132(no)001:264: de la sangs rgyas zhes pa ni /
NK132(no)001:265: ma rigs pa thams cad sangs shing mkhyen pa thams cad rgyas pa'o //
NK132(no)001:266: byang chub sems dpa' la sras zhes bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:267: chos las skyes pa'i sras so //
NK132(no)001:268: de ni sems dang po bskyed pa yan chad kyang yin la /
NK132(no)001:269: yang na 'phags pa sa bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)001:270: sa dang po thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni /
NK132(no)001:271: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su skye ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:273: de bzhin gshegs pa dang sku gsung thugs rnam pa 'dra bar gyur pa'i don no //
NK132(no)001:274: rdul gcig tu sangs rgyas mang po bzhugs pa sogs ni /
NK132(no)001:275: rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod yul gyi rdul la de ltar snang ba dang /
NK132(no)001:276: las dang po pas ni mos pa yid byed kho nar zad do //
NK132(no)001:277: sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes kyi spyod yul yang de dang 'dra mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:278: ye shes kyi snang ba kho na yin pas /
NK132(no)001:280: ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod yul tsam la gnas shing mi spyod de /
NK132(no)001:281: rdul dang spyod yul de dag ni don dam pa'i ye shes kyi ngor med pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:282: chos kyi dbyings kyi khyab tshad du 'jog pa ni /
NK132(no)001:283: chos kyi dbyings kyis ma khyab pa mi srid pa'i don te /
NK132(no)001:284: nam mkhas gar khyab tu de ltar snang ba yin mod /
NK132(no)001:285: de yang kun tu bzang po'i smon lam 'di /
NK132(no)001:286: yongs su grub pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la snang ba ni yin la /
NK132(no)001:287: smon lam de yang sa dang po nas dngos su rab tu sgrub cing /
NK132(no)001:288: sa brgyad pa nas ni legs par grub pa yin par shes so //
NK132(no)001:289: yang nges pa'i don mthar thug pa na /
NK132(no)001:290: ye shes nyid la chos kyi dbyings ma lus pa
NK132(no)001:291: thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor du mngon
NK132(no)001:292: sum du snang ba yin te /
NK132(no)001:293: de lta na 'di ni bde gshegs snying po mkha' mnyam yin pas /
NK132(no)001:294: sa bcu pa thob pa yan chad kyi spyod yul yin te /
NK132(no)001:295: de man chad kyi byang chub sems dpa' ni mos pa'i yul du bya ba tsam mo //
NK132(no)001:297: de lta bu la dad par byas pas 'bras bu mtha' yas pa ni 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)001:298: gsum pa ngag gi phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK132(no)001:299: de dag basngagasa pa mi zad rgya mtsho rnams //
NK132(no)001:300: dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra kun gyis //
NK132(no)001:301: rgyal ba kun gyi yon tan rab brjod cing //
NK132(no)001:302: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad bdag gis bstod //
NK132(no)001:303: mtha' yas pa'i sangs rgyas de dag bstong par bgyi zhes pa ni /
NK132(no)001:304: gnyis pa'i don la dang po ste de dag la bstod par bgyi ba'o //
NK132(no)001:305: yid kyi yul du ji ltar byas pa'i sangs rgyas de dag la /
NK132(no)001:306: bstod cing basngagasa pa yon tan rgya mtsho zad mi
NK132(no)001:307: shes pa rnams brjod pa'i sgo thams cad nas bstod
NK132(no)001:308: pa'i tshul yang mi zad pa rgya mtsho lta bu
NK132(no)001:309: rnams / ngag gis brjod tshul phun sum tshogs pa
NK132(no)001:310: dbyangs kyi yan lag lnga la sog sa pa yan
NK132(no)001:311: lag ste snyan pa la sogs pa'i khyad par mtha'
NK132(no)001:312: yas pa rgya mtsho lta bu'i sgra skad de lha
NK132(no)001:313: mo dbyangs can ma'i ngag bzhin no //
NK132(no)001:314: de lta bu'i sgo nas rgyal ba thams cad kun
NK132(no)001:315: gyi yon tan rab tu brjod cing ste brjod pa'i
NK132(no)001:316: tshul gyis // bde bar gshegs pa de dag thams cad la bdag gis bstod par bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:317: de nas chos dbyings dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas re re'i drung du /
NK132(no)001:318: lus zhing gi rdul rnyed du sprul pa dang /
NK132(no)001:319: lus de lta bus sangs rgyas re re'i zhabs la 'dud cing /
NK132(no)001:320: lus re re la yang mgo de snyed dang /
NK132(no)001:321: mgo bo re re la yang lce'i rtse mo de snyed dang /
NK132(no)001:322: lce de snyed las kyang bstod dbyangs de snyed 'byung bar mos pa'o //
NK132(no)001:323: yang bshad pa'i rnam grangs gzhan rgya mtsho zhes smos pa rnams /
NK132(no)001:324: rgya mtsho lta bu'i dpe don du mi sbyor bar /
NK132(no)001:325: grangs kyi gnas rgya mtsho zhes bya ba rgya skad sa mu dri'i sgra las /
NK132(no)001:326: sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis mtsho yas su bsgyur ba de'o //
NK132(no)001:327: de ni gcig bcu brgya stong khri 'bum sa ya bye ba dung phyur ther 'bum rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:331: mtsho yas zhes 'jig rten du grags pa ltar yin no //
NK132(no)001:332: zhes kyang bshad de 'on kyang dpe don du sbyor ba kho na 'thad do //
NK132(no)001:333: gnyis pa la bla na yod pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:334: bla na med pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:336: me tog dam pa phreng ba dam pa dang //
NK132(no)001:337: sil snyan rnams dang byug pa gdugs mchog dang //
NK132(no)001:338: mar me mchog dang bdug spos dam pa yis //
NK132(no)001:339: rgyal ba de dag la yang mchod par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:340: na bza' dam pa rnams dang dri mchog dang //
NK132(no)001:341: phye ma'i phur ma ri rab mnyam pa dang //
NK132(no)001:342: bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa'i mchog kun gyis //
NK132(no)001:343: rgyal ba de dag la yang machodapara bgyi //
NK132(no)001:344: de la dam pa shes pa rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:345: mchog ces pa rnams kyi don ni /
NK132(no)001:347: dngos po de dang de yang rgyu bzang ba /
NK132(no)001:348: kha dog dang dbyibs mdzes pa /
NK132(no)001:349: gzhan yang sgra dri ro reg phun sum tshogs pa dang bkod pa legs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:350: des na sna tshogs pa'i me tog bzang po dang /
NK132(no)001:351: rin po che dang me tog gi dra ba sogs phreng ba dam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:352: sil snyan te rol mo'i bye brag rgyud can dang /
NK132(no)001:353: 'bud dkrol dang brdung bya sna tshogs pa sgra snyan
NK132(no)001:354: po rnams dang dri zhim po'i byug pa rnams dang
NK132(no)001:355: / gdugs mchog la sogs pa ba dan dang /
NK132(no)001:358: mar me la sogs pa snang gsal gyi mchog mtha' yas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:359: sbyar ba dang ma sbyar ba'i dri zhim po sreg pa'i bdug spos dam pa rnams kyis /
NK132(no)001:360: gang mngon sum dang yid kyi spyod yul du dmigs
NK132(no)001:361: pa'i rgyal ba de dag la ni nyin re bzhin
NK132(no)001:363: bar 'dir rgya dpe 'ga' zhig las 'byung ba /
NK132(no)001:364: phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba kha cig gis bsgyur pa na //
NK132(no)001:365: rin chen mchog dang do shal mchog rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:366: rnam bkra lha rdzas bla re mchog rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:367: rgyal mtshan mchog dang ba dan mchog kun gyis //
NK132(no)001:368: rgyal ba de dag la yang mchod par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:369: zhes pa yang snang ba sngon gyi 'grel pa rnams las mi 'byung zhing /
NK132(no)001:370: bod dpe rnying ba kun la yang med la /
NK132(no)001:371: deng sang du yang mi 'don pa'i phyir 'dir yang bshad pa ma bris te go ni sla'o //
NK132(no)001:372: lha dang mi las gyur pa'i na bza' dam pa rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:373: chag chag gis btab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:375: gong bu'i rdzas dri zhim po mchog rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:376: dri bzang gi phye ma'i phur ma te thum por
NK132(no)001:377: byas pa rnam pa sna tshogs spungs pa'i phung po
NK132(no)001:378: ri rab dang mnyam pa dang mchod pa de thams
NK132(no)001:379: cad kyang bkod pa mdzes pas khyad par du 'phags
NK132(no)001:381: rgyal ba de dag la ni mchod par bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:382: dngos su smos pa de dag ni mtshon pa tsam te /
NK132(no)001:383: 'jig rten du ji tsam yod pa de tsam du
NK132(no)001:384: mchod pa bzang po dang bkod pa legs pa thams
NK132(no)001:385: cad / dngos su bshams pa dang yid kyis sprul pa'i tshul gyis 'bul ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:386: gnyis pa bla na med pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:387: mchod pa gang rnams bla med rgya che ba //
NK132(no)001:388: de dag rgyal ba thams cad la yang mos //
NK132(no)001:389: bzang po spyod la dad pa'i stobs dag gis //
NK132(no)001:390: rgyal ba kun la phyag 'tshal mchod par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:391: mchod pa gang bgyis pa rnams bla na med pa ste lha'i 'jig rten man chad na /
NK132(no)001:392: de bas lhag pa lta ci smos /
NK132(no)001:393: de dang mnyam pa 'ga' yang med pa ste /
NK132(no)001:394: byang chub sems dpa' mthu thob pa rnams kyis byas pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:396: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams thams cad rgyas par 'gengs pas rgya che ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:397: mchod pa de dag gong du smos pa'i rgyal ba thams cad la yang /
NK132(no)001:398: lhag par mos pa bla na med pa'i dad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:399: bzang po spyod pa la phan yon dpag tu med
NK132(no)001:400: pa zhig yod par yid ches pa'i dad pa'i stobs
NK132(no)001:402: rgyal ba kun la phyag 'tshal zhing mchod par bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:403: de ltar na phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:404: bla na med pa'i mchod pa 'di dag /
NK132(no)001:405: dngos su sgrub mi nus pas ni mos pas sgrub pa dang /
NK132(no)001:406: ma 'ongs pa na de lta bu 'grub par smon
NK132(no)001:407: lam 'debs pa nyid don gyi gtso bo yin te
NK132(no)001:408: / bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam stobs dag gis zhes dang /
NK132(no)001:409: bzang po spyod la dad pa'i stobs dag gis /
NK132(no)001:410: zhes gsungs pa'i don yang yin no //
NK132(no)001:412: tshangs pa gsum po 'di dag ni de bzhin gshegs
NK132(no)001:413: pa la mchod pa dang rim gro bya ba bla
NK132(no)001:414: na med pa'o // mchod pa'i las bla na med pa'i bsod nams tshad med pa 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)001:416: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems skyed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:417: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK132(no)001:418: ji ltar thos pa'i chos rnams de bzhin du sgrub pa'o //
NK132(no)001:419: ces bla na med pa'i mchod pa de gsum du bshad la /
NK132(no)001:420: 'dir yang sangs rgyas la mos pa dang /
NK132(no)001:421: bzang po'i spyod pa la dad pa gnyis bla na
NK132(no)001:422: med pa'i mchod pa'i khyad chos su bshad de gnad
NK132(no)001:424: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dbang gis ni //
NK132(no)001:425: lus dang ngag dang de bzhin yid kyis kyang //
NK132(no)001:426: sdig pa bdag gis bgyis pa ci mchis pa //
NK132(no)001:427: de dag thams cad bdag gis so sor bshags //
NK132(no)001:428: de la nyes pa'i rgyu ni dug gsum ste /
NK132(no)001:429: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang gti mug gis kun nas blangs pa'i dbang gis na'o //
NK132(no)001:430: nyes pa'i gzhi ni lus dang ngag dang de bzhin du yid kyis kyang bgyis pa ste /
NK132(no)001:431: srog gcod pa la sogs pa ni lus kyis so //
NK132(no)001:432: rdzun la sogs pa ni ngag gis so //
NK132(no)001:433: gnod sems la sogs pa ni yid kyis so //
NK132(no)001:434: byed pa po ni bdag gis bgyis pa zhes pa'o //
NK132(no)001:436: de lta bu'i sdig pa ci mchis pa ste gang
NK132(no)001:437: yod pa de dag thams cad ba dag gis so
NK132(no)001:439: su zhig gi spyan sngar zhe na /
NK132(no)001:440: rdul gcig steng na zhes sogs su ji skad bstan pa ltar /
NK132(no)001:441: sangs rgyas sras bcas mtha' yas pa rnams kyi spyan sngar ro //
NK132(no)001:442: de la ma bshags pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK132(no)001:443: sngar byas la 'byor pa med pas /
NK132(no)001:444: sdig pa la rung bar 'dzin pa na /
NK132(no)001:445: sdig pa'i rgyun de nyid 'phel bar 'gyur zhing /
NK132(no)001:446: phyin chad mi sdom pas las ngan zad pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:447: de las ngan song du brgyud mar 'gro ste thar
NK132(no)001:448: pa lta ci smos mtho ris kyang thob par daka'o
NK132(no)001:449: // sdig pa bshags pa'i phan yon ni /
NK132(no)001:450: 'gyod cing bshags pa kho nas sngar gyi rgyun mi 'phel zhing byang bar yang 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:451: phyin chad 'dzem zhing zlog pas mi dge ba rgyun chad de /
NK132(no)001:452: ngan 'gro las zlog cing mtho ris su 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)001:453: dge ba'i sa bon brtas te thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyur yang 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:455: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba kun dang sangs rgyas sras //
NK132(no)001:456: rang rgyal rnams dang slob dang mi slob dang //
NK132(no)001:457: 'gro ba kun gyi bsod nams gang la yang //
NK132(no)001:458: de dag kun la rjes su bdag yi rang //
NK132(no)001:459: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK132(no)001:460: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun dang /
NK132(no)001:461: sangs rgyas kyi sras byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK132(no)001:467: mi slob pa dgra bcom pa dang /
NK132(no)001:468: 'gro ba ni 'gro ba drug gi so so skye bo rnams kyi /
NK132(no)001:470: dge ba ci dang ci bgyis pa gang la yang /
NK132(no)001:471: de dag kun la rjes su bdag yi rang bar bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:472: de la yi rang ba ni rab tu dga' ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:473: rjes su zhes pa ni gang dang gang gi bya
NK132(no)001:474: ba byas pa'am 'bras bu thob pa'i gnas skabs de
NK132(no)001:475: la / slar yang dmigs nas 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:476: sngar song pa de'i rjes su zhugs pa lta bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:478: bsod nams dang bsod nams ma yin pa dang /
NK132(no)001:479: mi g.yo ba'i las gsum du phye ba'i bsod nams
NK132(no)001:480: dang ye shes kyi zlas drangs pa'i bsod nams sogs
NK132(no)001:481: yod kyang / 'dir ni dge ba'i chos thams cad do //
NK132(no)001:482: bshags pa dang yi rang ba 'di dag la //
NK132(no)001:483: dge ba'am sdig pa rang gis bgyis pa dang /
NK132(no)001:484: gzhan bgyid du bstsal ba dang /
NK132(no)001:485: gzhan gyis bya ba la rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK132(no)001:486: de dang de'i basngagasa pa brjod cing bstod pa rnams kyang /
NK132(no)001:487: bshags pa dang rjes su yi rang par bya ba ste /
NK132(no)001:488: 'on kyang bshags bya'i sdig pa ni rang gis byas pa gtso bo yin la /
NK132(no)001:489: yi rang gi yul ni gtso bor gzhan gyi dge ba'o //
NK132(no)001:490: rang gis bgyis pa'i dge ba la yang /
NK132(no)001:492: nga rgyal med cing dga' ba bsgoms na dge ba 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:493: gzhan gyi dge ba la rjes su yi rang ba ni /
NK132(no)001:494: gzhan gyi dge ba bri ba yang med la /
NK132(no)001:495: rang gi rtsol ba med cing ma byas kyang /
NK132(no)001:496: dge ba chen po rgyud la thob par 'gyur pas /
NK132(no)001:497: rmad du byung ba'i dge ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:498: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa chos kyi dbyings mngon sum du rtogs shing /
NK132(no)001:499: ji snyed pa thams cad la yang gsal snang thob pa dag gis ni /
NK132(no)001:500: rang gi dmigs pa'i yul du gsal bar snang ba'i
NK132(no)001:501: 'jig rten gyi dge ba ji tsam pa de tsam
NK132(no)001:502: de dang de la yi rang bas kyang thob par
NK132(no)001:503: 'gyur te / dper na stong sum cu'i 'jig rten
NK132(no)001:504: gyi khams kyi sems can rnams kyi bskal pa brgya'i
NK132(no)001:505: bar du byas pa'i dge ba rnams /
NK132(no)001:506: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa gcig gi mngon shes
NK132(no)001:507: kyis thams cad ma 'dres par gsal ba snang bar
NK132(no)001:508: mthong la / de thams cad la gcig car du
NK132(no)001:509: dmigs pa med pa'i yi rang thun gcig tsam bsgoms
NK132(no)001:510: mthong la / pas kyang / sems can de rnams
NK132(no)001:511: kyi dus de tsam du bsags pa'i dge ba de
NK132(no)001:512: snyed cig yi rang de'i mthu las skad cig de
NK132(no)001:513: la byang chub sems dpa' de'i rgyud la thob par
NK132(no)001:514: mthong la / pas kyang / 'gyur ro // de
NK132(no)001:515: bzhin du mtha' med pa'i bar du yang sbyar bar
NK132(no)001:516: mthong la / pas kyang / 'gyur ro // bya'o
NK132(no)001:517: // de la 'dod pa'i khams kyi sems can ni
NK132(no)001:518: mnyam par ma bzhag pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:519: gzugs kyi khams pa ni bsam gtan bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa dang /
NK132(no)001:520: gzugs med khams pa yang gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug
NK132(no)001:521: gi ting nge 'dzin la ma nyam par bzhag pa
NK132(no)001:522: kho na'o // nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)001:523: 'phags pa lhag bcas thams cad ni lus kyi rten
NK132(no)001:524: khams gsum du gtogs pa yin mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:525: nyan rang dgra bcom pa rnams kyi sems kyi rten ni /
NK132(no)001:526: khams gsum las 'das pa kho na yin la /
NK132(no)001:527: slob pa rnams kyi sems kyang /
NK132(no)001:528: khams gsum gyi sems dang bcas pa yin gyi /
NK132(no)001:529: sems can gyi ngo bo gang 'phags pa'i rgyud du gyur pa'i cha de ni /
NK132(no)001:530: khams gsum las 'das pa yin par shes par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:531: dgra bcom pa lhag med kyi yid lus dang /
NK132(no)001:532: lhag bcas kyi dbang po'i lus dang /
NK132(no)001:533: theg chen 'phags pa rnams kyi ni /
NK132(no)001:534: lus kyang khams gsum las 'das na sems ltar smos kyang ci dgos /
NK132(no)001:535: de ltar na khams gsum du gtogs pa'i so so skye bo la yang /
NK132(no)001:536: lam du zhugs pa dang ma zhugs pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK132(no)001:538: byang chub sems dpa' dang slob pa'i khongs su bsdus te /
NK132(no)001:539: 'gro ba kun ces pa ni thar pa'i lam du
NK132(no)001:540: ma zhugs pa kho na'i dbang du byas pa'i khams
NK132(no)001:541: gsum gyi sems can thams cad do //
NK132(no)001:542: nyan thos tshogs lam pa dang sbyor lam pa rnams ni /
NK132(no)001:543: nyan thos 'phags pa slob pa'i rgyu nye ba yin pas /
NK132(no)001:544: de'i khongs su gtogs par dgongs te ma smos pa dang /
NK132(no)001:545: rang rgyal gyi tshogs lam la gnas pa yang de dang 'dra la /
NK132(no)001:546: sbyor lam pa dang 'phags pa slob pa'ang cung zang yod mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:547: yun thung bar dgongs nas slob pa zur du ma smos so //
NK132(no)001:548: de la gang zag gi bdag med pa gtso bor
NK132(no)001:549: gyur pa'i bden pa bzhi'i don mngon sum du rtogs
NK132(no)001:551: ma rtogs pa ni so so skye bo'o //
NK132(no)001:552: nyan thos kyi tshogs sbyor gyi rtogs pa sngon du song nas /
NK132(no)001:553: bden pa bzhi'i don mngon sum gyis mthong bas /
NK132(no)001:554: khams gsum du gtogs pa'i nyon mongs kyi nang nas
NK132(no)001:555: lta ba ngan pa dang the tshom la sogs pa
NK132(no)001:556: mthong spangs kyi char gyur pa rnams ni spangs mod
NK132(no)001:557: kyang / spyir khams gsum du gtogs pa'i nyon mongs
NK132(no)001:558: ma spangs pa de ni rgyun du zhugs pa zhes
NK132(no)001:559: kyang / bya ba la / 'dis ma spangs pa'i nyon mongs de dag la /
NK132(no)001:560: sgom pas spang bar bya ba zhes bya zhing /
NK132(no)001:561: de'i nang gi 'dod khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs sum gnyis ni spangs /
NK132(no)001:562: sum cha lus pa na 'phags pa phyir 'ong zhes bya'o //
NK132(no)001:563: 'dod khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs thams cad spangs pa na /
NK132(no)001:564: 'phags pa phyir mi 'ong ba zhes bya'o //
NK132(no)001:565: 'di la sgom spangs su gtogs pa gzugs khams dang
NK132(no)001:566: gzugs med khams kyi nyon mongs ci yang ma spangs
NK132(no)001:567: pa dang / cung zad spangs pa nas /
NK132(no)001:568: phal cher spangs pa'i bar du rtogs pa mtho dman sna tshogs pa yod do //
NK132(no)001:569: khams gsum du gtogs pa'i nyon mongs thams cad spangs pa ni dgra bcom pa'o //
NK132(no)001:570: de yang myur ba srid pa gsum gyi mthar zhes pa ltar /
NK132(no)001:571: nyung mtha' yang skye ba gsum du tshogs bsags pa las 'byung la /
NK132(no)001:572: skye ba gsum la lam lnga sbyong tshul bshad kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges so //
NK132(no)001:573: rgyun zhugs sogs bzhi po de gang zag gcig gis rim can kho nar mngon du byed pa'ang yod /
NK132(no)001:574: bar pa gnyis med par sgom spang khams gsum gyi
NK132(no)001:575: nyon mongs rnams chab gcig tu spong pa'i rigs can
NK132(no)001:576: thogs mtha' gnyis kho na mngon du byed pa'ang yod
NK132(no)001:577: / so so skye bo'i dus na 'jig rten pa'i
NK132(no)001:578: lam gyis bsam gtan gzugs med kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK132(no)001:580: nam bden pa mthong ba na phyir mi 'ong du
NK132(no)001:581: 'gyur bas 'bras bu phyi ma gnyis kho na mngon
NK132(no)001:582: du byed pa sogs sna tshogs pa yod de /
NK132(no)001:583: de dag ni nyan thos 'phags pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:584: rang rgyal ni bskal pa brgyar tshogs bsags pa sngon du 'gro ba yin yang /
NK132(no)001:585: gnas skabs de dag tu phal cher tshogs lam la gnas pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:586: sbyor mthong sgom gsum mnyam gzhag thun gcig la bgrod par byas nas /
NK132(no)001:587: de'i bar ma chad pa la zad pa dang mi skye ba shes pa ste /
NK132(no)001:588: dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu dang mthar phyin pa'i lam mngon du byed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:589: rang rgyal gyi gtso bo bse ru lta bu yin la /
NK132(no)001:590: tshogs la spyod pa'i rang rgyal la ni de ltar ma nges te /
NK132(no)001:591: 'on kyang thams cad mthun par sngon gyi skye bar sangs rgyas la bya ba byas shing /
NK132(no)001:592: nyan thos lam la slob pa rnams dang 'dra bar byas pa yin yang /
NK132(no)001:593: lhag por rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba la ches mkhas par byas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:594: smon lam gyi dbang gi srid pa tha ma'i gnas skabs su /
NK132(no)001:596: bstan pa med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams su /
NK132(no)001:597: bla ma med pa rang gi bag chags kyi stobs sang pa kho nas /
NK132(no)001:598: byang chub mngon du byed pa'o //
NK132(no)001:599: nyan thos 'phags pa la ni dbang po rno brtul sna tshogs yod la /
NK132(no)001:601: byang chub sems dpa' ni sems dang po bskyed pa
NK132(no)001:602: nas bzung ste bsod nams kyi tshogs mtha' yas pa
NK132(no)001:603: bsags te / byang chub tu smon lam btab theg
NK132(no)001:604: pa chen po la thos bsam sgom gsum du byas
NK132(no)001:605: pas tshogs kyi lam du yang yon tan du mthong
NK132(no)001:606: bsags te / la / sbyor ba'i lam du gnas
NK132(no)001:607: lugs kyi rtogs pa 'phags mchog rnams dang rjes mthun
NK132(no)001:608: bsags te / la / pa grub cing / ting
NK132(no)001:609: nge 'dzin dang gzungs dang mngon shes mtha' yas pa'ang
NK132(no)001:610: bsags te / la / pa grub cing / bsgrubs
NK132(no)001:611: nas / mthong lam du chos nyid spros bral rnam
NK132(no)001:612: pa thams cad pa'i don mngon du byas pas /
NK132(no)001:613: bden bzhi'i don sogs nyan rang gi spangs rtogs thams cad zhor la thob cing /
NK132(no)001:614: byang sems 'phags par gyur pa zhes bya la /
NK132(no)001:615: de nyid kyi rgyun las dang po nas bcu pa'i
NK132(no)001:616: bar du yon tan mtha' yas gong 'phel du thob
NK132(no)001:618: rgyal ba'i sras po zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)001:619: de ltar na dbye ba 'di dag mngon pa sogs
NK132(no)001:620: gsung rab gzhan shes pa dag la skabs 'dir bshad
NK132(no)001:621: mi dgos kyang / shin tu las dang po dag la go ba phyogs tsam mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:623: rnam par dbye ba mtha' yas pa ni dus ji snyed par brjod par mi nus te /
NK132(no)001:624: 'phags pa rnams kyis so sor rang gis rig par bya ba nyid pas /
NK132(no)001:625: gzhung rgya chen po smra ba rnams kyis 'chad tshul mang po'i sgo nas /
NK132(no)001:626: dka' ba du ma dang bcas te 'chad mod kyang /
NK132(no)001:627: rgya mtsho chen po las skra rtse gcig gis blangs
NK132(no)001:628: pa'i chu thig gi tshad tsam yang ma yin no
NK132(no)001:631: gang rnams phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten sgron ma dag /
NK132(no)001:632: byang chub rim par sangs rgyas ma chags brnyes //
NK132(no)001:633: mgon po de dag bdag gis thams cad la //
NK132(no)001:634: 'khor lo bla na med par bskor bar bskul //
NK132(no)001:635: gang sangs rgyas rnams zhes spyir smos te /
NK132(no)001:636: de yang phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rnams na /
NK132(no)001:637: sems can gti mug gi mun par 'khyams pa rnam la lam ston par mdzad pas /
NK132(no)001:638: 'jig rten gyi sgron mar gyur pa sangs rgyas rnams
NK132(no)001:639: byang chub sgrub par byed pa'i lam gyi rim pa
NK132(no)001:640: / lam lnga dang sa bcu la sogs pa'i rim pa ma lus par sngon du song bas /
NK132(no)001:641: bla na med pa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang ma chags ma thogs par brnyes pa'am /
NK132(no)001:642: yang na de ltar lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa thob kyang /
NK132(no)001:643: thob pa de la zhen pa mi mnga' bas ma
NK132(no)001:644: chags pa'i mgon po sangs rgyas de dag thams cad
NK132(no)001:645: la bdag gis 'khor lo bla na med pa ste
NK132(no)001:646: / dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul lo //
NK132(no)001:647: 'khor lo ni shing rta'i 'khor lo lta bu ste /
NK132(no)001:648: ngo bo brtan pa'i dngos po yin yang /
NK132(no)001:650: pha rol gyi gnas su phyin par byed pa dang 'dra bar /
NK132(no)001:651: nyon mongs pa sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis mi
NK132(no)001:652: shigs par gnas pas shin tu brtan par chos kyi
NK132(no)001:653: lam ston pa po'i rgyud la mnga' ba de /
NK132(no)001:654: nyan pa po'i rgyud la 'phos pa dang 'dra bar
NK132(no)001:655: rtogs pa skyed nus pa ni chos kyi 'khor lo'o
NK132(no)001:656: // bla na med pa ni 'jig rten las 'das pa yin pa dang /
NK132(no)001:657: lha dang drang srong rnams kyis bstan pa'i chos dang thun mong ma yin pa'o //
NK132(no)001:659: sbrul pa'i sku sangs rgyas nas ring po ma lon pa /
NK132(no)001:660: da ltar 'jig rten du chos 'khor ye ma bskor ba la /
NK132(no)001:661: chos 'khor spyi ldog nas bskor bar gsol ba 'debs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:662: spyir chos 'khor bskor bzhin pa yin yang /
NK132(no)001:663: skabs su babs pa de dang de'i chos gsung bar gsol ba 'debs pa'ang 'di'i khongs su bsdu'o //
NK132(no)001:664: sangs rgyas thugs rje can zang zing la chags pa dang mi mkhyen pa mi mnga' bas /
NK132(no)001:666: chos la gus pa skyed pa'i phyir bskul dgos pa'ang yin la /
NK132(no)001:667: gtso bor ni sangs rgyas chos mi gsung bar mi srid kyang /
NK132(no)001:668: rang gi blo sems can la snying brtse ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)001:669: tshogs bsags pa'i slad du blo'i rim pa sbyang tshul lo //
NK132(no)001:671: mya ngan 'da' ston gang bzhed de dag la //
NK132(no)001:672: 'gro ba kun la phan zhing bde ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)001:673: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed bzhugs par yang //
NK132(no)001:674: bdag gis thal mo rab sbyar gsol ba 'debs //
NK132(no)001:676: sangs rgyas yongs su mya ngan las mi 'da' mod /
NK132(no)001:677: mya ngan las 'da' bar bstan pas 'dul ba rnams
NK132(no)001:678: la yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul ston
NK132(no)001:679: par gang bzhed pa de dag la /
NK132(no)001:680: dgos pa sangs rgyas 'jig rten du bzhugs na phan
NK132(no)001:681: bde mtha' yas pa lhun grub tu 'byung ba nyid
NK132(no)001:682: yin pas / 'gro ba kun la 'phral du phan par 'gyur zhing yun du bde ba'i phyir du /
NK132(no)001:683: dus kyi khyad par bskal pa chen po phyogs bcu'i
NK132(no)001:684: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing khams kyi rdul phra
NK132(no)001:685: rab kyi grangs snyed du bzhugs par yang gsol ba
NK132(no)001:686: 'debs pa po bdag gis gsol ba 'debs te ji
NK132(no)001:688: thal mo rab tu sbyar bas gsol ba 'debs par bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:689: 'phral du bde ba ni 'byor pa dang /
NK132(no)001:690: dbang phyug la sogs pa dang yun du phan pa ni mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK132(no)001:692: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK132(no)001:693: rjes su yi rang bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
NK132(no)001:694: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
NK132(no)001:695: thams cad rdzogs pa'i byang chub phyir bsngo'o //
NK132(no)001:697: yul mchog la lus ngag yid kyis phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK132(no)001:698: mchod pa rnam pa gnyis kyis mchod cing /
NK132(no)001:699: stobs bzhi'i sgo nas sdig pa bshags pa dang /
NK132(no)001:700: skye 'phags kyi dge ba thams cad la rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK132(no)001:701: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul zhing /
NK132(no)001:702: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar bzhugs su gsol ba ste /
NK132(no)001:703: yan lag drug po de byas pa las byung ba'i
NK132(no)001:704: dge ba cung zad bdag gis gang dang ci bsags
NK132(no)001:705: pa de dag thams cad ces pa ste /
NK132(no)001:706: dngos su ni de tsam yin yang rang gis dus
NK132(no)001:707: gsum du dge ba byas pa dang byed du bcug
NK132(no)001:709: basngagasa pa brjod pa thams cad dang /
NK132(no)001:710: 'gro ba thams cad kyi dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba thams cad kyang /
NK132(no)001:711: blos gcig tu bsdams nas bsngo dgos te /
NK132(no)001:712: de dag thams cad kyang chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa nyid du byas nas so //
NK132(no)001:713: cung zad dang ci bsags pa zhes pa'i tshig gis kyang zur gyis 'phangs pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:714: bsngo rgyu'i dge ba de rnams gang du bsngo zhe na /
NK132(no)001:715: byang chub chen po bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi phyir bsngo'o //
NK132(no)001:716: sus bsngo bar byed ce na bdag gis so //
NK132(no)001:717: gal te byang chub mchog tu ma bsngosa na /
NK132(no)001:718: rang rang gi 'bras bu phyung nas zad par 'gyur te /
NK132(no)001:719: 'khor ba pa rnams kyi ni bde 'gro tshun du zad la /
NK132(no)001:720: nyan rang gi de dag kyang lhag med kyi dbyings su zad pa'o //
NK132(no)001:721: sangs rgyas su bsngosa na ni /
NK132(no)001:722: de ma thob kyi bar du yang lha mi'i bde skyid sogs bde ba gong 'phel du 'gyur zhing /
NK132(no)001:723: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob zin nas /
NK132(no)001:724: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa brnyes pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:725: nam mkha' ji srid pa'i bar du gnas shing /
NK132(no)001:726: sems can thams cad kyi don spyod pas bsod nams
NK132(no)001:727: kyi 'bras bu nam yang zad pa mi srid pa
NK132(no)001:728: yin no // bsngo ba de yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis /
NK132(no)001:729: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu basngagasa pa ste //
NK132(no)001:731: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis basngagasa pa'i bsngo ba ni /
NK132(no)001:732: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa khri brgyad stong pa sogs las /
NK132(no)001:733: sbyin pa de yang sems can thams cad dang thun mong du byas nas /
NK132(no)001:734: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yongs su bsngo bar byed /
NK132(no)001:735: de yongs su bsngosa pa na /
NK132(no)001:736: ci nas mtshan mar yang dag par yongs su mi mthong ba ste /
NK132(no)001:737: de lta bu'i tshul gyis yongs su bsngo bar byed de /
NK132(no)001:738: bdag gis ci zhig sbyin par byed /
NK132(no)001:740: ci zhig yongs su bsngo bar bya /
NK132(no)001:741: su zhig yongs su bsngo bar byed /
NK132(no)001:742: gang du bsngosa na bla na med pa yang dag
NK132(no)001:743: par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngosa pa'i dngos po
NK132(no)001:744: de / yang dag par rjes su ma mthong ngo //
NK132(no)001:745: de ci'i phyir zhe na nang stong pa nyid kyi stong pa dang /
NK132(no)001:747: stong nyid rnams la rim gyis sbyar nas /
NK132(no)001:748: rang gi mtshan nyid stong pa nyid kyis stong pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:749: des gang du yongs su bsngo bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:750: ci zhig yongs su bsngo bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:751: gang gis yongs su bsngo bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:753: de ltar yongs su bsngosa na legs par yongs su bsngosa par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:755: bsngo ba'i yul bla na med pa'i byang chub dang //
NK132(no)001:756: ched du bya ba gzhan don kho na dang //
NK132(no)001:757: yid la byed pa'i rnam pa ni /
NK132(no)001:758: bsngo bya'i dge ba 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:759: bsngo ba nyid kyang 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:760: khyad par gsum dang ldan pa'i bsngo ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:761: yongs su bsngo ba'i khyad par rgyas pa ni /
NK132(no)001:762: 'phags pa rdo rje mtshan gyis bsngo ba'i le'u las rtogs par bya'o ////
NK132(no)001:763: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa smon lam gyi rab dbye la /
NK132(no)001:764: dbal phyogs kyi glang po la sogs pa sngon gyi
NK132(no)001:765: mkhas pa rnams kyis don tshan rnam pa bcu drug
NK132(no)001:766: tu mdzad do // de yang sdom ni /
NK132(no)001:767: lhag bsam byang sems mi brjed dang //
NK132(no)001:768: ma gos phan bde go cha dang //
NK132(no)001:769: skal mnyam 'grogs dang bshes gnyen bsten //
NK132(no)001:770: sangs rgyas mngon gyur dam chos 'dzin //
NK132(no)001:771: mi zad mdzod thob 'jug pa dang //
NK132(no)001:772: stobs dang bsgrub pa las dang ni //
NK132(no)001:773: rjes su slob dang 'jug sdud do //
NK132(no)001:774: de yang bsam pa dag pa'i sgo nas smon pa dang //
NK132(no)001:775: byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa'i sgo nas smon pa dang /
NK132(no)001:776: de bzhin du sbyar te ma gos pa'i sbyor ba'i dang /
NK132(no)001:777: gzhan la phan bde ba'i dang /
NK132(no)001:781: sangs rgyas mngon gyur gyi dang /
NK132(no)001:782: dam chos yongs bzung gi dang /
NK132(no)001:783: mi zad pa'i mdzod thob pa'i dang /
NK132(no)001:789: thams cad kyi don bsdu ba'i sgo nas smon pa'i smon lam rnams so //
NK132(no)001:790: dang po bsam pa dag pa'i sgo nas smon pa ni /
NK132(no)001:791: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang zhes pa nas /
NK132(no)001:792: re ba'ang 'grub par shog gi bar yin la /
NK132(no)001:793: de la'ang don tshan bzhi las /
NK132(no)001:794: sangs rgyas la mchod pa'i bsam pa dang ni /
NK132(no)001:796: dgongs pa yongs su skong ba'i ni /
NK132(no)001:798: zhing yongs su dag pa'i ni /
NK132(no)001:800: sems can la phan gdags pa'i bsam pa ni /
NK132(no)001:801: phyogs bcu'i sems can sogs so //
NK132(no)001:802: gnyis pa byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa la /
NK132(no)001:803: byang chub spyod pa dag ni bdag spyod cing ces pa nas /
NK132(no)001:804: yongs su byang bar shog gi bar te /
NK132(no)001:805: tshe rabs sogs kyis rtag tu rab tu 'byung ba dang /
NK132(no)001:806: tshul khrims spyod pa sogs kyis tshul khrims dag pa dang /
NK132(no)001:807: lha'i sogs kyis skad sna tshogs pas chos ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:808: des shing sogs kyis dge ba la brtson pa dang /
NK132(no)001:809: rgyu bzhi sngon du 'gro ba'i byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:810: sdig pa sogs kyis de'i mi mthun phyogs spong bar ston no //
NK132(no)001:811: yang na 'di la tshe rabs dran pa dang /
NK132(no)001:812: rab tu byung ba so sor phye nas /
NK132(no)001:813: rgyu lngar byas kyang legs par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:814: gsum pa ma gos pa'i sbyor pa'am ma chags pa ni /
NK132(no)001:815: las dang ces pa la sogs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:816: bzhi pa gzhan la phan bde ni /
NK132(no)001:817: zhing gi khyon dang sogs so //
NK132(no)001:818: lnga pa go cha bgo ba ni /
NK132(no)001:819: byang chub spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing sogs te /
NK132(no)001:820: sangs rgyas kyi chos rdzogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:821: sems can gyi spyod pa dang mthun par 'jug pa dang /
NK132(no)001:822: dam pa'i chos ston pa gsum la rim pas sbyar ro //
NK132(no)001:823: drug pa skal mnyam gyi grogs dang 'grogs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:824: bdag gi spyod dang sogs so //
NK132(no)001:825: bdun pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten cing mnyes par byed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:827: brgyad pa sangs rgyas mngon gyur la mchod pa sogs bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:828: sangs rgyas sras kyis sogs te /
NK132(no)001:829: 'khor dang dus dang bsam pa skyo ba med pa dang /
NK132(no)001:830: mchod pa ste don tshan bzhi rim can du sbyar ro //
NK132(no)001:831: dgu pa dam chos yongs su bzung ba ni rgyal ba rnams kyi sogs te /
NK132(no)001:834: rab tu sbyor ba gsum rim gyis so //
NK132(no)001:835: bcu pa mi zad pa'i mdzod thob par bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:836: srid pa thams cad sogs te /
NK132(no)001:837: tshogs gnyis dang mthu thob par bya ba'o //
NK132(no)001:838: bcu gcig pa 'jug pa du ma'i sgo nas smon pa ni /
NK132(no)001:839: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te /
NK132(no)001:841: drung du bdag mchi 'o'i bar ro //
NK132(no)001:843: dang po zhing dang bcas pa'i sangs rgyas lta ba la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:845: gnyis pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:847: gsum pa chos 'khor bskor ba la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:849: bzhi pa bskal pa'i sgo nas 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:851: lnga pa de bzhin gshegs pa la blta bas 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:853: drug pa de'i spyod yul la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:855: bdun pa zhing sgrub pa la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:857: brgyad pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i drung du 'gro ba pa la 'jug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:858: gang yang ma byon sogs so //
NK132(no)001:860: zhing blta gsung dang chos 'khor dang //
NK132(no)001:861: bskal pa sangs rgyas spyod yul dang //
NK132(no)001:862: zhing sgrub pa dang drung du 'gro //
NK132(no)001:863: 'jug pa brgyad du shes pa yin //
NK132(no)001:864: spyi don bcu gnyis pa stobs kyi sgo nas smon pa ni /
NK132(no)001:866: yang dag sgrub par byed kyi bar ro //
NK132(no)001:867: bcu gsum pa bsgrub pa'am gnyen pa'i sgo nas smon pa ni /
NK132(no)001:868: las kyi stobs rnams sogs te /
NK132(no)001:869: las nyon bdud gsum 'joms pa dang /
NK132(no)001:870: gnyen po dngos te don tshan bzhi rim can dang /
NK132(no)001:871: bcu bzhi pa phrin las kyi sgo nas smon pa ni /
NK132(no)001:873: mi skyo spyad par bgyi ces pa'i bar te /
NK132(no)001:874: 'di la yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing dag pa dang /
NK132(no)001:875: sems can smin par byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:877: rjes thob kyi ye shes thob pa dang /
NK132(no)001:878: spyod pa mtha' yas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:881: bskal pa mtha' med par 'jug pa ste don brgyad rim can no //
NK132(no)001:882: bco lnga pa rjes su slob pa ni /
NK132(no)001:883: gang yang dus gsum sogs te /
NK132(no)001:884: 'di la sangs rgyas kyi rjes su slob pa dang /
NK132(no)001:885: sems dpa' chen po'i rjes su slob pa'o //
NK132(no)001:886: bcu drug pa don bsdu ba'i bsngo ba bstan pa ni /
NK132(no)001:887: spyod pa dag ni tshad yod ma gyur cig sogs so //
NK132(no)001:888: de ltar na bsdus pa'i don gyi rim pa 'di ni /
NK132(no)001:889: rgya 'grel phal cher gyi bshad pa mgrin gcig pa yang yin la //
NK132(no)001:890: khyad par mkhan po ye shes sde'i zhal snga nas ji skad gsungs pa ltar bkod pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:891: de bas na bsdus don 'di ni shin tu khungs che ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:892: 'di la gces spras su bya zhing mi nub pa'i don du bkod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:893: sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel par ni don tshan bcu
NK132(no)001:894: drug po spyi tsam nas 'dra ba las dang po
NK132(no)001:895: la byang chub tu sems bskyed pa zhes ming 'dogs
NK132(no)001:896: pa dang / sems bskyed pa sogs don tshan bcu
NK132(no)001:897: rim pa bzhin mos spyod kyi sa'i phar phyin bcu
NK132(no)001:898: pa dang / dang sbyor zhing / mchod par gyur ces pas /
NK132(no)001:901: nyi zla'i dpes chags sdang gis ma gos pa dang /
NK132(no)001:902: grang dro'i bya ba byed kyang /
NK132(no)001:903: chags sdang gi rnam rtog med pas bzod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:904: sangs rgyas mngon du 'gyur bas smon lam gyi stobs
NK132(no)001:905: yin pa sogs rgyu mtshan dang bcas nas 'chad la
NK132(no)001:906: / sangs rgyas kyi zhing lta ba la sogs pa 'jug pa brgyad kyi /
NK132(no)001:907: de bzhin gshegs pa lta ba'i 'jug pa dang /
NK132(no)001:908: de'i spyod yul la 'jug pa gcig tu bsdams nas
NK132(no)001:909: gzhung tshan bdun po des dang po rab tu dga'
NK132(no)001:910: ba sogs lhag bsam dag pa'am ma dag sa bdun
NK132(no)001:911: la rim gyis sbyor ba dang /
NK132(no)001:912: don tshan bcu gnyis pa stobs kyi smon pas brgyad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:913: bcu gsum pa la mi mthun phyogs nyams ces zer te sa dgu pa dang /
NK132(no)001:914: bcu bzhi pa la yon tan yongs su sbyong zhes 'dogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:915: bco lnga pa rjes su slob pa la gnyis su phye nas /
NK132(no)001:916: gang yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yi /
NK132(no)001:917: zhes sogs la yon tan thams cad rdzogs par bya ba zhes gsung zhing /
NK132(no)001:918: rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi thu bo pa sogs /
NK132(no)001:920: tshogs gnyis bzung bas byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i
NK132(no)001:921: rjes su slob pa ste don tshan bcu bzhi pa
NK132(no)001:922: dang bco lnga pa bsdams pas sa bcu pa bshad
NK132(no)001:923: cing / sa bcu bstan pas 'phags lam gyi phar phyin bcu yang bshad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:924: bcu drug pa thams cad kyi don bsdus ni kun
NK132(no)001:925: tu 'od kyis rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su smon lam
NK132(no)001:926: 'debs pa'o // zhes bzhed de legs par bshad pa'ang yod la /
NK132(no)001:927: ji bzhin mi 'byor ba yang 'ga' re snang ngo //
NK132(no)001:928: 'on kyang sngon gyi dus 'phags pa'i yul du theg
NK132(no)001:929: pa chen po pha rol tu phyin pa'i bshad sgrub
NK132(no)001:930: kyi bstan pa rnam par dag pa dar por yod
NK132(no)001:931: pa'i gnas skabs su legs par grags pa'i mkhas pas
NK132(no)001:933: 'dir yang lugs de go ba'i phyir rnam grangs su cung zad blangs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:934: 'on kyang 'dir bshad sla zhing go bde ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:935: bsdus don gzhan gyi sgo nas brjod na /
NK132(no)001:936: 'di la mdor bstan rgyas bshad don bsdu gsum las /
NK132(no)001:940: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang phyogs bcu yi //
NK132(no)001:941: 'jig rten dag na gang bzhugs mchod par gyur //
NK132(no)001:942: gang yang ma byon de dag rab myur bar //
NK132(no)001:943: bsam rdzogs byang chub rim par sangs rgyas sbyon //
NK132(no)001:944: sngon byon pa 'das pa'i sangs rgyas su rab tu grags pa rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:945: da ltar phyogs bcu yi 'jig rten gyi khams dag
NK132(no)001:946: na gang 'gro ba'i don la bzhugs pa thams cad
NK132(no)001:947: la / mchod pa'i bye brag thams cad kyis mchod par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:948: gang yang ma byon pa'i sangs rgyas ste /
NK132(no)001:949: 'og min du sangs rgyas zin nas /
NK132(no)001:950: gdul bya dus la ma babs par /
NK132(no)001:951: 'jig rten du sprul pa'i sku mi ston pa rnams sam /
NK132(no)001:952: myur du 'tshang rgya bar rung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po de dag rnams /
NK132(no)001:953: dka' ba dang 'bad rtsol med bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:954: rab tu myur bar rang rang gi dgongs pa'i bsam pa rdzogs nas /
NK132(no)001:956: dga' ldan du skye ba ston pa la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:957: byang chub mngon du brnyes pa'i rim pa tshul dang mthun par bstan nas /
NK132(no)001:958: sangs rgya bar sbyon cig ste shog cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:959: de yang 'og min du sangs rgyas zin rnams /
NK132(no)001:960: so so'i gdul bya smin pa sogs dgongs pa myur
NK132(no)001:961: du rdzogs nas sprul sku myur du 'byon par shog
NK132(no)001:962: shig pa dang / sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi
NK132(no)001:963: dgongs pa'i bsam pa tshogs gnyis kyi lhag ma myur
NK132(no)001:964: shig pa dang / du rdzogs nas / sangs rgyas
NK132(no)001:965: brnyes par gyur cig pa ste sangs rgyas dang byang
NK132(no)001:966: sems chen po de rnams kyi smon lam rdzogs par
NK132(no)001:968: de dag gi phyir du rang gi smon lam rdzogs
NK132(no)001:969: par yang bya da gos pas mchod pa dang bskul
NK132(no)001:971: rang gzhan gyi smon lam nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir du smon lam 'debs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:973: phyogs bcu ga la'i zhing rnams ji snyed pa //
NK132(no)001:974: de dag rgya cher yongs su dag par gyur //
NK132(no)001:975: byang chub shing dbang drung gshegs rgyal pa dang //
NK132(no)001:976: sangs rgyas sras kyis rab tu gang bar shog /
NK132(no)001:977: phyogs bcu ga la ba'i ma dag pa'i zhing ji
NK132(no)001:978: snyed pa de dag thams cad bde ba can gyi
NK132(no)001:979: zhing bzhin du mchog tu rgya che zhing /
NK132(no)001:980: ngan song la sogs pa'i skyon thams cad dang bral nas /
NK132(no)001:981: yongs su dag par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:982: zhing khams de thams cad kyang shing gi rnam pa thams cad kyi /
NK132(no)001:983: rab dang mchog dang gtso bo mthar thug pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:984: shing gi dbang po ste byang chub kyi shing gi drung du gshegs te /
NK132(no)001:985: mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas zin pa'i rgyal ba dang /
NK132(no)001:986: de dag gi 'khor du sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi sras /
NK132(no)001:987: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:988: sems can mtha' yas pa dge ba la 'god par
NK132(no)001:989: mdzad pa rnams kyis rab tu gang bar shog cig
NK132(no)001:990: pa ste / snod dang bcud dag par smon pa tshig rkang gnyis gnyis so //
NK132(no)001:991: de ni zhing yongs su sbyong ba'i smon lam mo //
NK132(no)001:993: phyogs bcu'i sems can gang rnams ji snyed pa //
NK132(no)001:994: de dag rtag tu nad med bde bar gyur //
NK132(no)001:995: 'gro ba kun gyi chos kyi don rnams ni //
NK132(no)001:996: mthun par gyur cing re ba'ang 'grub par shog /
NK132(no)001:997: phyogs bcu'i sems can gang rnams ji snyed pa //
NK132(no)001:998: de dag rtag tu nad kyi rigs mtha' dag spangs shing med la /
NK132(no)001:1000: mtho ris kyi sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral zhing /
NK132(no)001:1001: 'dod yon dang ting nge 'dzin gyi bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur la /
NK132(no)001:1002: 'gro ba kun gyi chos kyi don te mtho ris
NK132(no)001:1003: dang thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyur gyur
NK132(no)001:1004: pa'i spyod pa rnams byas pa la /
NK132(no)001:1005: phan tshun thams cad blo gros mthun par gyur cing /
NK132(no)001:1006: chos dang mi 'gal ba'i re ba'i don thams cad
NK132(no)001:1007: kyang 'grub par shog cig re ba don gyi mthar
NK132(no)001:1008: thug pa ni / bla na med pa'i byang chub yin par 'gyur te /
NK132(no)001:1009: sems can thams cad kyang rang nyid bde ba dam pa thob par 'dod pa yin na /
NK132(no)001:1010: bde ba dam pa mthar thug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1011: de las gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1012: dud 'gro'i skye gnas tshun chad kyi yang /
NK132(no)001:1013: re smon gyi gnas ni rdzogs pa'i byang chub yin par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:1014: de bas na dngos su smon par mi byed kyang
NK132(no)001:1015: 'dod pa'i tshul la dpag nas bsgrub na de ltar
NK132(no)001:1017: de dag ni sems can yongs su smin par byed pa'i smon lam ste /
NK132(no)001:1018: mdor bstan 'dis ni rdzogs smin sbyang gsum tshang par bstan cing /
NK132(no)001:1019: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa thams cad dam /
NK132(no)001:1020: smon lam gyi yul thams cad gsum po der 'dus pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:1022: theg pa chen po'i spyod pa thun mong ba'i rim pa dang sbyar ba'i smon lam dang /
NK132(no)001:1023: byang chub sems dpa'i gsang ba thun mong ma yin pa'i dbang du byas pa'i smon lam dang /
NK132(no)001:1024: gnyis kar du 'jug pa'i rnam grangs sna tshogs pa bstan pa'i smon lam mo //
NK132(no)001:1026: byang chub spyod pa dag ni nas /
NK132(no)001:1027: kun tu spyod par gyur ces pa'i bar te /
NK132(no)001:1028: de la byang chub spyod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1029: gzhan don du bdag nyid bla na med pa yang
NK132(no)001:1030: dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob pa'i phyir du
NK132(no)001:1031: spyod pa ste / bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi chos rdzogs pa'i rgyur gyur pa'i ldog cha 'dzin la /
NK132(no)001:1032: bzang po spyod pa ni sems can gzhan rnams kho
NK132(no)001:1033: na sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'jog pa'i phyir spyod
NK132(no)001:1034: pa ste sems can gzhan smin cing grol bar byed
NK132(no)001:1035: pa'i rgyu'i ldog cha 'dzin pa yin cing /
NK132(no)001:1036: gnyis ka yang snying rje chen po dang 'khor gsum
NK132(no)001:1037: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi kun nas
NK132(no)001:1038: blangs pa'i / sbyin sogs phar phyin bcu /
NK132(no)001:1039: thabs mkhas phun sum tshogs pas zin pas /
NK132(no)001:1040: rang rgyud grol zhing gzhan rgyud smin par byed pa la ni 'dra'o //
NK132(no)001:1041: des na byang chub sems dpa' gcig kho nas kyang /
NK132(no)001:1042: spyod pa gnyis kar spyad dgos te /
NK132(no)001:1043: sems can gyi don du gang rlabs che ba /
NK132(no)001:1044: skabs su gang bab pa de nyid la 'jug dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:1046: sems bskyed pa dang po'i gnas skabs kyi smon lam gyi khyad par las /
NK132(no)001:1047: byang chub sems dpa' 'dod chen pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1050: byang chub spyod pa pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1051: thog mar bdag nyid sangs rgyas su gyur nas 'khor ba ji srid kyi bar gzhan don byed pa /
NK132(no)001:1052: rgyal po lta bu'i sems bskyed dang ldan pa'i byang sems zhes bya'o //
NK132(no)001:1054: sems can gcig kyang ma lus par /
NK132(no)001:1055: sangs rgyas kyi sa la ma bzhag gi bar du /
NK132(no)001:1056: sems can kho na sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1057: bdag nyid 'khor ba na gnas par bya yi /
NK132(no)001:1058: 'tshang rgya bar ma gyur cig ces smon lam 'debs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1059: bzang po spyod pa ba ste /
NK132(no)001:1060: rdzi bo lta bu'i sems bskyed dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems dapa'o //
NK132(no)001:1061: de bas na de gnyis sems dang po bskyed pa'i smon lam dang 'dun pa'i khyad par yin gyis /
NK132(no)001:1062: bar du spyod pa ni gnyis kar spyod la /
NK132(no)001:1063: mtha' 'bras bu la yang khyad par med do //
NK132(no)001:1064: 'o na byang chub spyod pa pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1065: 'phags pa byams pa bzhin du 'jig rten na 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:1066: bzang po spyod pa ba ni kun tu bzang po dang 'jam dpal la sogs pa bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:1067: tshogs rdzogs kyang dam bca' ma rdzogs pas mngon par sangs mi rgya ba ste /
NK132(no)001:1068: 'bras bu rigs gnyis yod pa ma yin nam snyam na /
NK132(no)001:1069: tshogs rdzogs nas sangs mi rgya ba ni mi srid de /
NK132(no)001:1070: sgrib gnyis byang zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa de nyid sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:1071: sngon gyi dam bca' dang smon lam yang /
NK132(no)001:1072: blo sbyong ba'i phyir yin gyi /
NK132(no)001:1073: dmigs yul dngos po la zhugs pa ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1074: mthar phyin par spyod dgos pa yang ma yin no //
NK132(no)001:1075: kun tu bzang po dang 'jam dpal la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:1076: zhing khams rkun tu byang chub sems dpar snang ba yang /
NK132(no)001:1077: byang chub sems dpa' 'dul ba la de ltar bstan pa yin gyi /
NK132(no)001:1079: sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba'i zhing khams mang por sangs
NK132(no)001:1080: rgyas nyid du yang bstan zin cing ston bzhin pa
NK132(no)001:1082: rgyal ba byams pa la sogs pa bzhin zhing 'dir sangs rgyas su ston pa rnams kyang /
NK132(no)001:1083: zhing gzhan dang gnas skabs gzhan du byang chub sems
NK132(no)001:1084: dpas 'dul ba la slar yang byang chub sems dpa'
NK132(no)001:1085: 'byung ste / 'o skol gyi ston pa bskal pa
NK132(no)001:1086: mtha' yas pa'i sngon rol du sangs rgyas zin pa
NK132(no)001:1087: 'byung ste / yang / phyi nas kyang byang chub
NK132(no)001:1088: sems dpa'i spyod pa rgyun mi 'chad par bstan pa
NK132(no)001:1089: 'byung ste / yang / bzhin no // de bas na /
NK132(no)001:1090: sangs rgyas rnams kyi rtsa ba'i zhing dang sku lus
NK132(no)001:1091: 'og min stug po bkod pa'i zhing du longs spyod
NK132(no)001:1093: gang tshogs gnyis rdzogs tshad de ma thag tu zhing
NK132(no)001:1094: der longs sku'i rten du mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK132(no)001:1095: rgya bar gdon mi za la /
NK132(no)001:1096: ma dag pa'i zhing du sprul pa ston pa la ni /
NK132(no)001:1097: sangs rgyas dang sems dpa' chen po gnyis su yang 'byung mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:1098: der ma zad sprul pa mtha' yas pa'i tshul gyis 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)001:1099: des na 'jam dpal la sogs pa sngon gyi dam bca' mi 'dor ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1100: da dung sangs ma rgyas so zhes gsungs pa ltar yod srid na'ang /
NK132(no)001:1101: dgos pa bzang po spyod pa dang 'brel ba'i dam bca' yang dag pa la /
NK132(no)001:1102: gdul bya rnams spro ba skye zhing 'god nus pa'i dgos pa yod par gzigs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1103: dgongs gzhi byang chub sems dpas 'dul ba'i ngor byang chub sems dpa'i tshul 'dzin pa yang /
NK132(no)001:1104: rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par 'byung ba la dgongs so //
NK132(no)001:1105: gzhan du na tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas sangs mi rgya ba zhig srid na ni de'i rgyu gang yin /
NK132(no)001:1106: sgrib pa'i cha cung zad bzung bas so snyam na /
NK132(no)001:1107: sa bcu pa'i ye shes kyis 'bad rtsol med par /
NK132(no)001:1108: yun thung ngus kyang sgrib pa mtha' dag spong bar 'gyur na /
NK132(no)001:1109: yun ring po de nyid ci'i phyir spang par mi 'gyur /
NK132(no)001:1110: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin yang tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i phyir mi thob pa mi srid la /
NK132(no)001:1111: des sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas par spong bar mi 'gyur na ni /
NK132(no)001:1112: sangs rgyas gzhan rnams kyis kyang thams cad mkhyen pa la sgrib pa ma spangs par yang 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:1113: des de spangs na sgrib pa ci zhig lus par 'gyur /
NK132(no)001:1114: gzhan yang tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas sgrib pas lus pa yang mi srid de /
NK132(no)001:1115: nyi ma shar bas mun pa bzhin no //
NK132(no)001:1116: tshogs ma rdzogs pa yang mi srid de /
NK132(no)001:1117: dus mtha' yas par gzhan rnams las kyang lhag par
NK132(no)001:1118: spyod pa rgya che ba rtag tu spyad pa'i phyir
NK132(no)001:1119: ro // 'jam dpal la sogs pas sgrib pa'i cha
NK132(no)001:1120: cung zad bzung ba ltar bshad pa yod du chug
NK132(no)001:1121: kyang gdul bya 'ga' zhig la snang tshul byung ba
NK132(no)001:1122: la dgongs pa'i drang don yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:1123: shin tu spros bas chog go //
NK132(no)001:1125: gzhung 'dir byang chub spyod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1126: bzang po spyod pa zhes pa rnams de ltar nges par byas nas /
NK132(no)001:1130: spyod pa spyi la slob pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1131: khyad par du tshul khrims la slob pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1132: mngon shes dang ldan pas chos ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1133: byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa rnams la bslabs pas /
NK132(no)001:1134: sgrib pa mtha' dag byang ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1136: chags pa med pa'i gnas thob pa na /
NK132(no)001:1137: sems can rnams sdug bsngal zhi zhing bde ba dang dge ba la 'god par byed /
NK132(no)001:1138: khyad par du mtha' yas pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa thob nas /
NK132(no)001:1139: chos bstan pas 'gro ba'i don mtha' med du spyod pa 'gyur ro zhes pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1140: lam gyi rim pa dang po 'di'i skabs kyi bsdus pa'i don yin te /
NK132(no)001:1141: de dang mthun par smon lam 'debs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1143: sems bskyed skye ba dran dang rab tu byung //
NK132(no)001:1144: spyod pa spyi dang tshul khrims mngon shes ston //
NK132(no)001:1145: byang sems mi brjed sgrib byang skyon gsum grol //
NK132(no)001:1146: chags med zhi bder 'god dang rnam 'phrul thob //
NK132(no)001:1147: 'gro don spyod de don tshan bcu gsum yin //
NK132(no)001:1149: don tshan dang po gsum ni /
NK132(no)001:1150: byang chub spyod pa dag ni bdag spyod cing //
NK132(no)001:1151: 'gro ba kun tu skye ba dran par gyur //
NK132(no)001:1152: tshe rabs kun tu 'chi 'pho skye ba na //
NK132(no)001:1153: rtag tu bdag ni rab tu 'byung bar shog /
NK132(no)001:1155: byang chub spyod pa gzhan don du rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par 'dod cing /
NK132(no)001:1156: byang chub kyi phyir du pha rol tu phyin pa
NK132(no)001:1157: drug la spyod par 'dod pa'i sems bskyed blangs shing
NK132(no)001:1158: / de dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dag ni bdag spyod cing /
NK132(no)001:1159: de las 'jig rten pha rol 'gro ba'i gnas kun las /
NK132(no)001:1161: rtag tu skye ba dran pas sngon sems bskyed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1162: chos spyad pa yang dran par 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:1163: tshe rabs kun gyi gnas skabs su'am /
NK132(no)001:1164: 'chi 'pho ba dang skye bas bsdus pa'i skye ba bzung zhing gson pa'i gnas skabs thams cad na /
NK132(no)001:1165: dus rtag tu bdag ni rab tu 'byung bar shog cig /'dir rab tu byung ba ni gnyis te /
NK132(no)001:1166: so so skye bo'i gnas skabs su khyim spangs te
NK132(no)001:1167: rab tu byung nas sdom pa yang dag par blangs
NK132(no)001:1168: pas rab byung du 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1169: theg chen 'di la 'phags pa'i sa thob tshad chos nyid kyi rab byung thob pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1170: don tshan bzhi pa dang lnga pa spyod pa spyi dang tshul khrims la bslabs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1171: rgyal ba kun gyi rjes su slob gyur te //
NK132(no)001:1172: bzang po spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
NK132(no)001:1173: tshul khrims spyod pa dri med yang dag pa //
NK132(no)001:1174: rtag tu ma nyams skyon med spyod par shog /
NK132(no)001:1176: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon sum du mjal ba'am lkog
NK132(no)001:1177: tu gyur kyang gsung rab thos pa la rten nas
NK132(no)001:1178: / rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun gyi gdams ngag chos las ji ltar 'byung ba ltar /
NK132(no)001:1179: rjes su slob par gyur te /
NK132(no)001:1180: bzang po spyod pa'i rgyu'am sgrub pa pha rol tu
NK132(no)001:1181: phyin pa drug la yang dag par bslabs pas yongs
NK132(no)001:1182: su rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i thabs la 'jug par byed
NK132(no)001:1184: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims rnam pa gsum gyi spyod pa /
NK132(no)001:1185: nyon mongs spangs pas dri ma med la /
NK132(no)001:1186: rang don theg pa dman pa'i sems kyis ma gos pas yongs su dag pa /
NK132(no)001:1187: 'chal tshul ltung ba'i nyes pas rtag tu ma gos pas ma nyams pa /
NK132(no)001:1188: dus gsum gyi dngos po thob par sred pa med pa'am /
NK132(no)001:1189: bden dngos su 'dzin pa dang bral bas skyon med pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1190: de lta bu'i tshul khrims la spyod par shog cig /
NK132(no)001:1191: don tshan drug pa mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pas chos ston pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1192: lha yi skad dang glu dang gnod sbyin skad //
NK132(no)001:1193: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1194: 'gro ba kun gyi skad rnams ji tsam par //
NK132(no)001:1195: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos ston no //
NK132(no)001:1196: byang chub sems dpa' mthu thob pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK132(no)001:1200: grul bum la sogs pa dag gi skad dang /
NK132(no)001:1201: mi'i skad tha dad sna tshogs rnams kyi skad dang
NK132(no)001:1202: de dag la sogs pa 'gro ba kun gyi sgra
NK132(no)001:1203: skad rnams ji tsam yod pa de tsam thams cad
NK132(no)001:1204: kyi skad du / bdag gis chos bstan to ste ston par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1206: lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes kyi dbang du byas pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:1207: mngon shes de'i mthu ni thag ring ba dang shin
NK132(no)001:1208: tu phra ba sogs lkog tu gyur pa'i sgra thams
NK132(no)001:1209: cad kyang shes / 'gro ba tha dad pa'i skad rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:1210: 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra rnams kyang go //
NK132(no)001:1211: rang gi skad dang ngag tshig gcig gis kyang sems
NK132(no)001:1212: can gzhan rnams la de dang de'i skad sna tshogs
NK132(no)001:1213: pa so sor go bar nus pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1216: klu la klu'i skad la sogs pa dus gcig gam rim can du ston par nus so //
NK132(no)001:1217: 'dir lha ni 'dod pa'i lha rigs drug go //
NK132(no)001:1218: klu ni brang 'gro sbrul gyi ming yin yang /
NK132(no)001:1219: de rnams kyi nang nas rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa rnams la /
NK132(no)001:1220: spyi ming bye brag la btags pa'i tshul te /
NK132(no)001:1222: bod kyi brda' rnying pa rnams la glu 'brug tu grags pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1223: gnod sbyin ni rgyal chen bzhi rigs kyi lha rnams la'ang grags mod kyis /
NK132(no)001:1224: 'dir lha las logs su bkar ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1225: bar snang la rgyu ba'am sa steng du rgyu ba'i mdangs 'phrog pa po rnams so //
NK132(no)001:1226: grul bum ni gshin rje'i rigs su gtogs pa yi dwags kyi 'gro ba'i khyad par /
NK132(no)001:1228: bdun pa byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1229: des shing pha rol phyin la rab brtson te /
NK132(no)001:1230: byang chub sems ni nam yang brjed ma gyur /
NK132(no)001:1231: des pa ni mdzangs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1233: mkhas la zhib pa'i blo ste /
NK132(no)001:1235: pha rol tu phyin pa rnams la skyo ba med
NK132(no)001:1236: par ngang gis 'jug pa'i rab tu brtson pa dang
NK132(no)001:1237: / byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ba ni rnam pa gnyis te /
NK132(no)001:1238: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas la 'god par 'dod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1239: chos kyi dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes la mnyam par 'jog pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1240: de lta bu'i byang chub kyi sems dus dang gnas
NK132(no)001:1241: skabs thams cad du nam yang brjed par ma gyur
NK132(no)001:1242: cig ces pa'o // de la des pa ni rgyud 'jam pa'i phyir snying rje mi brjed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1243: mkhas pa'i phyir stong nyid mi brjed pa ste rgyu'o //
NK132(no)001:1244: pha rol tu phyin pa la ngang gis brtson pa
NK132(no)001:1245: yang de rnams mi brjed pa ste yan lag go
NK132(no)001:1246: // de yang gzhan gyis ma bstan par sbyin pa'i
NK132(no)001:1247: pha rol tu phyin pa la 'jug pa la sogs
NK132(no)001:1248: pa byang chub sems dpa'i chos ma 'dres pa bco
NK132(no)001:1249: brgyad rnams 'di dag tu 'dus pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:1250: de yang mos spyod kyi sa la ni ci rigs par thob cing /
NK132(no)001:1251: 'phags pa'i sa la ni rdzogs par thob pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1252: de dag kyang 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin las gsungs te /
NK132(no)001:1253: ma bstan pa pha rol tu phyin pa drug la 'jug pa ste drug dang /
NK132(no)001:1254: ma bstan par bsdu dngos dang thabs la mkhas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1255: theg pa mchog gi 'byung ba zhes pa ste gsum dang /
NK132(no)001:1256: theg chen las ma nyams pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1258: zung dang s+n+rel zhi'i rgyud la mkhas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1259: ye shes sngon du 'gro zhing 'du mi byed pas dge sdig gi blang dor la mkhas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1260: bzod pa'i lus kyi sems can mi gtong pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1261: 'gro kun dga' bar ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1262: byis pa dang nyan thos kyi nang du thams cad mkhyen pa'i sems mi nyams pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1263: sangs rgyas kyi chos tshol ba las mi zlog pa rnams so //
NK132(no)001:1264: don 'di nyid zhib mor rtog par 'dod na /
NK132(no)001:1265: bden pa po'i le'u las rgyas par bshad pas der blta'o //
NK132(no)001:1266: byang chub spyod pa zhes pa nas /
NK132(no)001:1267: de yan chad ni bzang po spyod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1268: byang chub spyod pa sgrub pa'i dbang du byas shing /
NK132(no)001:1269: mos spyod kyi sa la gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1270: thun mong ba'i yon tan gyi dbang du byas pa'i smon lam mo //
NK132(no)001:1271: don tshan brgyad dgu bcu pa /
NK132(no)001:1272: sdig sgrib byang ba dang skyon gsum las grol ba dang ma chags pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1273: sdig pa gang rnams sgrib par gyur pa dag /
NK132(no)001:1274: de dag ma lus yongs su byang bar shog /
NK132(no)001:1275: las dang nyon mongs bdud kyi las rnams las //
NK132(no)001:1276: grol zhing 'jig rten 'gro ba rnams su yang //
NK132(no)001:1277: ji ltar pad+mo chu mi chags pa dang //
NK132(no)001:1278: nyi zla nam mkhar thogs pa med ltar spyad //
NK132(no)001:1279: de la sdig pa ni sdig to mi dge ba'i chos te /
NK132(no)001:1280: 'dod pa'i khams kyi nyon mongs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1281: des kun nas blangs pa'i las thams cad do //
NK132(no)001:1283: nyon mongs pa thams cad yin te /
NK132(no)001:1284: de bas na sdig pa gang rnams thar pa la sgrib par gyur pa dag ste /
NK132(no)001:1285: de dag sa bon dang bcas pa la ma lus pa yongs su byang bar shog cig /
NK132(no)001:1286: skyon gsum ni las nyon bdud gsum mo //
NK132(no)001:1287: las ni khams gsum du skye bar 'gyur ba'i las dang /
NK132(no)001:1288: nyon mongs pa ni kun tu sbyor ba dgu'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1289: bdud ni chos kyi 'tsho ba la bar du gcod par byed pa'i gdon te /
NK132(no)001:1293: nad la sogs pa bskyed cing /
NK132(no)001:1294: gsod par byed pa'i las can nam /
NK132(no)001:1295: de bzhin du lam bzang po las zlog tu bcug nas dka' thub ngan pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1296: lta ba ngan pa la sogs pa la yang sbyor bar byed pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1297: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bdag po la sogs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1298: gang byang chub sems dpa' ting nge 'dzin gyi lus thob pa phan chad du /
NK132(no)001:1299: rang nyid la ni bdud kyi las kyis 'jug pa med la /
NK132(no)001:1300: de las gzhan la ni yod do //
NK132(no)001:1301: las dang nyon mongs pa'i skyon gyis 'khrid pa yang de dang 'dra la /
NK132(no)001:1302: 'on kyang de gnyis spangs pa'i dus ni /
NK132(no)001:1303: mthong ba'i lam ste chos nyid la bzod pa 'bring po thob pa na'o //
NK132(no)001:1304: ma gos pa'am ma chags pa'i yon tan ni /
NK132(no)001:1305: rang nyid gang du gnas shing spyod pa'i 'jig rten gyi 'gro ba rnams /
NK132(no)001:1306: gang du spyod kyang rung ste /
NK132(no)001:1307: ji ltar pad+mo chu nang du gnas kyang chu mi chags pa bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:1308: rtag tu 'khor bar gnas kyang 'khor ba'i skyon las dang nyon mongs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1309: skye shi la sogs pas mi gos pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1310: nyi zla nam mkha' la thogs pa med par rgyu ba na /
NK132(no)001:1312: sman rnams bskyed pa la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:1313: gzhan gyi don mang po spyod kyang /
NK132(no)001:1314: lan la re ba med cing rloms sems dang rnam par rtog pa med pa ltar /
NK132(no)001:1315: byang chub sems dpa' de yang sbyin pa rnam pa
NK132(no)001:1316: bzhi la sogs pas sems can la phan pa rgya
NK132(no)001:1317: chen po rtag tu sgrub kyang /
NK132(no)001:1318: lan la re ba dang rloms sems med pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1319: bdag kyang de ltar spyod par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1320: bcu gcig pa sems can bde ba la 'god pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1321: zhing gi khyon dang phyogs rnams ji tsam par //
NK132(no)001:1322: ngan song sdug bsngal rab tu zhi bar byed //
NK132(no)001:1323: bde ba dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing //
NK132(no)001:1324: 'gro ba thams cad la ni phan par spyad //
NK132(no)001:1325: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi khyon dang /
NK132(no)001:1326: phyogs bcu rnams ji tsam yod par /
NK132(no)001:1327: ngan song gis mtshon pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi sdug
NK132(no)001:1328: bsngal ma lus pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar
NK132(no)001:1329: byed la / 'jig rten pa'i bde ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1331: phun sum tshogs pa dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing /
NK132(no)001:1332: de tsam du ma zad 'gro ba de rnams thams cad la ni /
NK132(no)001:1333: thar pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos kyis rtag tu phan par spyod nus par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:1334: don tshan bcu gnyis bcu gsum pa mtha' yas pa'i rnam 'phrul dang /
NK132(no)001:1335: 'gro don mi zad par spyod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1336: byang chub spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
NK132(no)001:1337: sems can dag gi spyod dang mthun par 'jug /
NK132(no)001:1338: bzang po spyod pa dag ni rab ston cing //
NK132(no)001:1339: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:1340: bdag nyid byang chub spyod pa'i sgo nas //
