NK132(no)001:1341: pha rol tu phyin pa drug po dag ni yongs su rdzogs par byed cing /
NK132(no)001:1342: sems can gzhan rnams kyi khams dang /
NK132(no)001:1345: bag la nyal rnams shes pa de rnams kyi spyod pa dang mthun par /
NK132(no)001:1346: gang gis 'dul bar 'gyur ba'i thabs kyis 'jug ste /
NK132(no)001:1347: khyim pas 'dul ba la khyim pa'i gzugs dang /
NK132(no)001:1348: rab tu byung bas 'dul ba la rab byung gi gzugs dang /
NK132(no)001:1349: de bzhin du sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK132(no)001:1356: rgyal po la sogs pa gzugs sna tshogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1357: spyod pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1358: bshad pa sna tshogs pa'i sgo nas sems can rnams smin par byed pa'i nus pa thob pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1359: gzhan don du 'khor bar skyo ba med pa'i rang
NK132(no)001:1360: bzhin can de ni 'gro ba'i don 'di ltar spyod
NK132(no)001:1361: de / rang gi rtogs pa dang mthun pa'i bzang po spyod pa dag gi chos ni /
NK132(no)001:1362: sems can rnams la rab tu ston cing spyod pa de la 'god par mdzad pas so //
NK132(no)001:1363: de ltar rang gi spyod pa rdzogs pa dang nus pa thob pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1365: rang gzhan gyi don gsum po de yang /
NK132(no)001:1366: dus re zhig spyod par ma zad ma 'ongs pa'i
NK132(no)001:1367: bskal pa mtha' med pa'i bar du kun tu spyod
NK132(no)001:1369: gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa'i gsang ba thun mong
NK132(no)001:1370: ma yin pa'i dbang du byas pa'i smon lam la
NK132(no)001:1371: / grogs phun sum tshogs pa dang lhan cig par smon lam dag pas mtshams sbyar /
NK132(no)001:1372: bshes gnyen dam pa rtag tu bsten cing mnyes par byas /
NK132(no)001:1373: thun mong gi skabs su bshad pa'i spyod pa rnam
NK132(no)001:1374: dag la gnas pas chos kyi sgo'i ting nge 'dzin
NK132(no)001:1376: tshogs gnyis kyi mthu las byang chub sems dpa'i rgyan rnams thob /
NK132(no)001:1377: zhing mtha' yas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi drung du byang
NK132(no)001:1378: chub sems dpa'i spyod pa spyad pas slar yang spyod
NK132(no)001:1379: pa shin tu smin pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK132(no)001:1380: kun khyab tu rdzogs smin sbyangs gsum nus pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1381: yul dus mnyam nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1382: rgyal ba'i gsung mtha' dag la 'jug pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1383: rgyal tshab kyi sa la gnas pa'i spyod pa mtha' dag ston pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK132(no)001:1384: rim pa de dang mthun par smon lam du byas pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1387: grogs dang bshes gnyen sgo gnyis sgrub //
NK132(no)001:1388: tshogs las rgyan thob sangs rgyas mchod //
NK132(no)001:1389: yangs dogs med dang gsung dbyangs 'grub //
NK132(no)001:1390: rgyal tshab mchog gi spyod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1391: brgyad pa de la dbang 'byor drug /
NK132(no)001:1392: chos ston dus dang mthong ba dang //
NK132(no)001:1393: spyod yul zhing khams mdzad pa la'o //
NK132(no)001:1394: rtsa ba'i don tshan brgyad du 'dod //
NK132(no)001:1396: de la 'di ni phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i
NK132(no)001:1397: gtam la yang dag par 'jug pa'i tshul yin te
NK132(no)001:1398: / dang po nyid du mos pa'i dge ba phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu /
NK132(no)001:1399: bsod nams khyad par can sgrub pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1400: grogs bzang po dang spyod pa gcig tu spyod cing smon lam sgrub pa yin pas /
NK132(no)001:1402: bdag gi spyod dang mtshungs par gang spyod pa //
NK132(no)001:1403: de dag dang yang rtag tu 'grogs par shog /
NK132(no)001:1404: lus dang ngag rnams dang ni sems kyis kyang //
NK132(no)001:1405: spyod pa dag dang smon lam gcig tu spyad //
NK132(no)001:1406: bdag byang chub spyod pa dang bzang po spyod pa la sbyor ba na /
NK132(no)001:1407: bdag gi spyod pa dang mtshungs par spyod pa'i grogs
NK132(no)001:1408: gang yin pa de dag dang yang dus rtag tu
NK132(no)001:1410: lus dang ngag rnams dang ni sems kyis kyang ste /
NK132(no)001:1411: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa de dag gcig tu mthun par spyod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1412: smon lam rnams kyang gcig tu mthun par spyad pa ste mthun par smon lam 'debs pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1413: de yang grogs ni zang zing gi sbyin pa gtong ba la dga' la /
NK132(no)001:1414: bdag gis ni tshul khrims kho na basngagasa te /
NK132(no)001:1415: zang zing gi sbyin pa smod par byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1416: grogs ni bdag dben par gnas pa la dga' la /
NK132(no)001:1417: rang nyid ni khyim gyi 'tsho chis la dga' ba mi 'bor ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1418: grogs de ni kun rdzob rten 'brel gyi chos la ches cher 'dzin cing mos la /
NK132(no)001:1419: rang gis ni don dam stong pa'i gtam gyis ur
NK132(no)001:1420: gnon du byed pa la sogs pa ni gnyis kar
NK132(no)001:1421: chos spyod pa yin du chug kyang /
NK132(no)001:1422: spyod pa mi mthun par spyod pa yin pas de ltar mi bya bar /
NK132(no)001:1423: grogs byang chub sems dpa' chos la spyod pa de nyid dang /
NK132(no)001:1424: bsam pa mthun cing sbyor ba yang mthun /
NK132(no)001:1425: basngagasa pa brjod pa yang mthun /
NK132(no)001:1426: smon lam gdab pa yang mthun par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:1427: de ltar na de tsam grogs su 'grogs pa dang
NK132(no)001:1428: phyogs gcig tu tshogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK132(no)001:1429: cad / spyir so so nas dge ba la brtson par ma zad /
NK132(no)001:1430: phan tshun gcig gcig gi dge ba la yi rang zhing /
NK132(no)001:1431: phan tshun du bltas nas mthun par spyod cing /
NK132(no)001:1432: gzhan re re dag gi chos mthun gyi 'dun pa mi 'dra ba gsar du skyes pa rnams kyang /
NK132(no)001:1433: mthong zhing thos na phyin chad thams cad kyis de dang 'dra bar spyod pa'am yi rang byed na /
NK132(no)001:1434: spyod pa gcig tu spyad pa zhes bya zhing smon
NK132(no)001:1435: lam yang spyi sgrigs shig ma gtogs gzhan 'debs su
NK132(no)001:1436: mi rung ba lta ma yin mod /
NK132(no)001:1437: dang po nyid nas spyi mthun na ni legs /
NK132(no)001:1438: thog ma 'dod pa so so'i smon lam tha dad pa yod du chug kyang /
NK132(no)001:1439: de 'dra de nas mthong zhing thos la go ba
NK132(no)001:1440: na phan tshun gcig gcig so sos de dang de
NK132(no)001:1441: la khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1442: gshe ba dang ngan du mi zer bar smon lam
NK132(no)001:1443: mthun par 'debs pa ni smon lam gcig pa ste
NK132(no)001:1444: / 'di ni spyir chos byed tsam dang /
NK132(no)001:1445: sgos su da lta'i dbang du byas na /
NK132(no)001:1446: chos brgyud gcig pa dang gnas gzhi gcig pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1447: bla ma gcig pa rnams la nyams len mi dgos ka med pa gcig yin te /
NK132(no)001:1448: tshe 'di dang skye ba gzhan gyi gnas skabs thams cad du /
NK132(no)001:1449: rten 'brel rnam dag bsgrig pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1451: 'gro ba smin pa sogs la 'di kho na gal che bar yod pas /
NK132(no)001:1452: lag len la thebs par 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)001:1453: gal te dngos su spyod pa mi mthun yang /
NK132(no)001:1454: phan tshun gnang ba sbyin pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1455: gdams ngag dang rjes su bstan pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1456: rjes su yi rang ba dang mos pa'i sems dang ma bral ba de ni /
NK132(no)001:1457: spyod pa mthun pa nyid yin te /
NK132(no)001:1458: blo gros mthun par gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:1459: de bzhin du chos min ni bzlog dgos pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:1460: mthun par byed pa ma yin no //
NK132(no)001:1461: de ltar spyod pa dang smon lam gcig tu spyad pa de ni /
NK132(no)001:1462: tshe 'adi'am skye ba gzhan du mos pa'i dge ba phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:1463: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten cing mnyes par byed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1464: bdag la phan par 'dod pa'i grogs po dag /
NK132(no)001:1465: bzang po spyod pa rab tu ston pa rnams //
NK132(no)001:1466: de dag dang yang rtag tu 'phrad par shog /
NK132(no)001:1467: de dag bdag gis nam yang yid mi dbyung //
NK132(no)001:1468: bdag la bzang po spyod pa'i chos kyi lag len rab tu ston pas /
NK132(no)001:1469: mthar thug tu phan 'dogs par 'dod pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen /
NK132(no)001:1470: 'khor ba dang theg dman las yongs su skyob cing /
NK132(no)001:1471: theg chen gyi bde ba ster ba'i grogs po ste /
NK132(no)001:1472: bla ma dam pa gang dag yod pa de rnams dag dang yang /
NK132(no)001:1473: dus rtag tu 'phrang ba ste mjal bar shog cig /
NK132(no)001:1474: bla ma dam pa de dag bdag gis dus nam
NK132(no)001:1475: yang lan gcig gam skad cig gcig kyang thugs yid
NK132(no)001:1478: yid 'byung ba ni mi dgyes pa yin pas mi
NK132(no)001:1479: dbyung ba ni rtag tu bla ma mnyes pa'i thabs
NK132(no)001:1480: la 'bad pa'o // de lta bu'i bshes gnyen dam
NK132(no)001:1481: pa bsten pa'i tshul ni 'phags pa sdong po bkod
NK132(no)001:1482: la 'bad pa'o // pa las / khye'u dpal 'byung gi rnam thar las rtogs par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:1483: mos pa'i dge ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa de ni /
NK132(no)001:1484: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i gtam gyi chos dang /
NK132(no)001:1485: de ston pa'i bshes gnyen dam pa 'phrad par 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)001:1486: snga ma'i mjug thog tu 'di bstan pa yin cing /
NK132(no)001:1487: bla ma dam pa mnyes par byed dgos par gsungs
NK132(no)001:1488: la de mnyes pa'i thabs kyang chos spyod las gzhan
NK132(no)001:1489: du med pas byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rnams
NK132(no)001:1490: la slob dgos par grub la /
NK132(no)001:1491: de'i thun mong gi spyod pa rnams ni sngar bshad zin cing /
NK132(no)001:1492: thun mong ma yin pa'i spyod pa yang /
NK132(no)001:1493: spyod pa dang smon lam gcig par bshad pa nyid kyis shugs las grub pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:1494: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po gcig par shes pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1496: sems can bdag mtshungs kyi byams pa rnams yod na /
NK132(no)001:1497: spyod smon gcig tu spyod pa khyad par du 'phags pa 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:1498: bzang po spyod pa rab tu ston byed pa zhes pas kyang shugs las bstan te /
NK132(no)001:1499: don dam par na kun tu bzang po ni /
NK132(no)001:1500: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po rtag tu bzang ba de yin la /
NK132(no)001:1501: de la dmigs nas spyad pa spyod pa'i phyir yang /
NK132(no)001:1502: thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang ba rnams la las
NK132(no)001:1503: dang po pa'i sa la gnas pas kyang sgrub par
NK132(no)001:1505: de ltar grogs bzang po dang spyod pa gcig tu spyad /
NK132(no)001:1506: bla ma dam pa yongs su bsten te spyod pa
NK132(no)001:1507: la nan tan du gnas pa des ni rim gyis
NK132(no)001:1508: dad pa'i sa dang mos pa la spyod pa'i sa
NK132(no)001:1510: de nas ni skabs 'dir sgo dang po chos kyi
NK132(no)001:1511: sgo'i ting nge 'dzin ni thob pa'i dbang du byas
NK132(no)001:1512: te / sangs rgyas sras kyis bskor ba'i mgon po rnams //
NK132(no)001:1513: mngon sum rtag tu bdag gis rgyal ba lta //
NK132(no)001:1514: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
NK132(no)001:1515: de dag la yang mchod pa rgya cher bgyi //
NK132(no)001:1516: sangs rgyas rnams sras byang chub sems dpas bskor ba yang yin la /
NK132(no)001:1517: mtha' yas pa'i 'gro ba thams cad kyi mgon por gyur pa rnams ni /
NK132(no)001:1519: de rnams bdag gis dus rtag tu mngon sum du blta zhing mthong bar gyur la /
NK132(no)001:1520: lan gcig tsam ma yin par dus de nas bzung
NK132(no)001:1521: ste ma 'ongs pa'i bskal pa kun tu rgyun mi
NK132(no)001:1522: 'chad par sangs rgyas de dag la yang /
NK132(no)001:1523: mchod pa rgya cher bgyi la /
NK132(no)001:1524: dus yun ring mo dang dka' ba chen pos mchod par byed pa la yang /
NK132(no)001:1525: yid mi skyo bar rtag tu dga' ba dang spro ba chen pos mchod par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1526: sangs rgyas mngon sum du mthong zhing mchod par byed pa tsam ni /
NK132(no)001:1527: dad pa'i sa chen po la gnas pas rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi thob pa yan chad du /
NK132(no)001:1528: thams cad la yod pa yin yang /
NK132(no)001:1529: rtag tu mthong zhing skyo ba mi srid par bshad pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1530: mos spyod kyi sa chen por chos kyi rgyun gyi
NK132(no)001:1531: ting nge 'dzin ni thob pa yan chad kho na'o
NK132(no)001:1532: // de thob pa na chos kyi sgo gnyis pa gzungs khyad par can yang thob pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:1534: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK132(no)001:1535: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK132(no)001:1536: bzang po spyod pa rnam par spyang pa yang //
NK132(no)001:1537: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyad par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:1538: ji tsam mngon du gyur pa'i rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung /
NK132(no)001:1539: lung gi dam pa'i chos gsung rab yan lag bcu
NK132(no)001:1540: gnyis po thams cad mi brjed pa'i gzungs kyi sgo
NK132(no)001:1542: sems can rnams la byang chub spyod pa'i lam kun tu ston cing snang bar byed la /
NK132(no)001:1543: bdag nyid kyis bzang po spyod pa yang dag par blangs shing /
NK132(no)001:1544: cung zad ngam ci rigs par grub pa de nyid /
NK132(no)001:1546: 'phel ba dang dag par byed par shog cig /
NK132(no)001:1547: de la sbyong ba'i don 'phel ba ni /
NK132(no)001:1548: rtsal sbyong ba lta bu dang /
NK132(no)001:1549: spyod pa de'i skyon dag par byed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1550: rims nad spyong pa lta bu'o //
NK132(no)001:1551: de ltar spyod pa sbyong ba yang /
NK132(no)001:1552: spyod pa la zhugs pa nas brtsams nas /
NK132(no)001:1553: ma 'ongs pa'i bskal pa mtha' med pa kun tu spyad par bagyi'o zhes smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1554: skabs de dag tu tshogs gnyis mang du gsog pas tshogs gnyis kyi stobs rnyed pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1555: byang chub sems dpa'i yon tan gyi rgyan rnams kyang thob par 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)001:1557: srid pa thams cad du yang 'khor ba na //
NK132(no)001:1558: bsod nams ye shes dag ni mi zad rnyed //
NK132(no)001:1559: thabs dang shes rab ting 'dzin rnam thar dang //
NK132(no)001:1560: yon tan kun gyi mi zad mdzod du gyur //
NK132(no)001:1561: srid pa ni byung ba dang 'byung ba ste /
NK132(no)001:1562: khams gsum gyi srid pa thams cad du yang /
NK132(no)001:1563: las dang smon lam dang ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK132(no)001:1564: dbang 'byor pa'i stobs kyis 'khor zhing skye ba na /
NK132(no)001:1565: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis zad mi
NK132(no)001:1566: shes pa gong nas gong du 'phel ba rnyed pa
NK132(no)001:1567: dang / de las sems can sgrol ba la dgos
NK132(no)001:1568: pa bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi chos rdzogs pa'i thabs
NK132(no)001:1572: sems can gyi don spyod pa gsum la mkhas pa'i
NK132(no)001:1573: shes rab de gsum ka la yang mnyam gzhag lhag
NK132(no)001:1574: mthong dang / rjes thob spyod pas bsdus pa'i dbye ba can dang /
NK132(no)001:1575: nam mkha' mdzod dang dri ma med pa'i phyag rgya
NK132(no)001:1576: la sogs pa ting nge 'dzin mtha' yas pa rnams
NK132(no)001:1577: dang / rnam par thar pa ni rnam thar brgyad dang /
NK132(no)001:1578: ting nge 'dzin gsum la sogs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1581: snyoms 'jug gi sgrib pa'i khyad par re re spangs pa las /
NK132(no)001:1582: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes nyams su myong ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1583: de las byung ba'i dga' ston rnam par 'phrul pa'i rol rtsed ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1584: gzhan yang yon tan gyi khyad par kun gyi mi zad pa'i mdzod thob par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1585: de la las kyi skye ba dngos ni /
NK132(no)001:1586: sems dpa' so skye rnams yin la /
NK132(no)001:1587: der yang yon tan gyi tshogs ni rtog ge ba
NK132(no)001:1588: rnams kyis bskal ba'i bar du yang blos dpyod par
NK132(no)001:1590: 'phags mchog rnams kyis las la dbang ba'i skye ba yang /
NK132(no)001:1591: spyir las kyi dbang gis skye ba tsam yin la /
NK132(no)001:1593: dbang sgyur ba'i tshul la ni /
NK132(no)001:1594: ye shes mtha' yas yod par smos ma dgos la /
NK132(no)001:1595: smon lam gyi skye ba'ang sems rgyud kyis bzung ba ma yin mod /
NK132(no)001:1596: ye shes kyi mthu las byung zhing /
NK132(no)001:1597: ye shes dang ldan pa'i bya ba byed pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1598: de rnams las dbang sgyur ba'i skye ba can gyis lus dngos ni /
NK132(no)001:1600: de'i sprul pa 'khor ba ltar ston pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:1601: gzhan rnams ni khams gsum du 'byung ba shas che'o //
NK132(no)001:1602: tshogs gnyis ni ji skad du /
NK132(no)001:1604: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis tshogs //
NK132(no)001:1605: bsod nams ye shes mtshungs pa med //
NK132(no)001:1606: gcig gis 'khor bar mngon mtho byed //
NK132(no)001:1607: gzhan gyis nyon mongs med par 'khor //
NK132(no)001:1608: sbyin dang tshul khrims bsod nams kyi //
NK132(no)001:1609: tshogs yin shes rab ye shes kyi //
NK132(no)001:1610: gsum po gzhan ni gnyis ka'i ste //
NK132(no)001:1611: lnga char yang ni ye shes tshogs //
NK132(no)001:1614: tshegs chung ngus don chen po 'grub pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1615: rgyu chung ngu las 'bras bu chen po 'byung ba
NK132(no)001:1616: ste shes rab phun sum tshogs pa'i byed las so
NK132(no)001:1617: // tshigs su bcad pa 'di'i don ni /
NK132(no)001:1618: yangs shing rgya che la bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK132(no)001:1619: de ltar 'phags pa'i sa la gnas par gyur na /
NK132(no)001:1620: yid kyi rang bzhin gyi lus grub pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1621: rgyal ba'i spyod yul mtha' dag la lta ba'i nus pa thob pas /
NK132(no)001:1622: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhal blta zhing mchod pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:1623: don de nyid ston pa ni rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te /
NK132(no)001:1624: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
NK132(no)001:1625: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa la //
NK132(no)001:1626: byang chub spyad pa spyod cing blta bar bgyi //
NK132(no)001:1627: rdul gcig gi steng na yang /
NK132(no)001:1628: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rdul ji snyed
NK132(no)001:1629: pa'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing mthong
NK132(no)001:1630: bar 'gyur la / zhing de rnams su grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas rnams /
NK132(no)001:1631: sangs rgyas kyi sras byang sems rnams kyi dbus na bzhugs pa la /
NK132(no)001:1632: de dag dang mtshungs par lhan cig tu byang chub spyad pa yang spyod cing /
NK132(no)001:1633: sku lta ba dang gsung nyan par bgyid par smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1634: 'dir 'phags pa'i sa thob ma thag pa la /
NK132(no)001:1635: zhing gi rdul snyed kyi sangs rgyas gcig char mthong ba rang ni min yang /
NK132(no)001:1636: sa gzhi khyon che chung ma nges par sangs rgyas
NK132(no)001:1637: dang sangs rgyas kyi zhing ci rigs pa mthong bar
NK132(no)001:1639: de nas rim pas gong 'phel du gyur te /
NK132(no)001:1640: mtha' med du 'phel ba thob par 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)001:1641: sa dang po thob ma thag pa nas dngos su rang ma thob kyang /
NK132(no)001:1642: zhing gi rdul snyed lta ba'i sbyor ba la zhugs pa ni yin no //
NK132(no)001:1643: rgyud la skye tshul de ltar yin yang /
NK132(no)001:1644: smon lam 'debs ba'i tshe rgya che sa nas sbyong pa yin pas /
NK132(no)001:1645: 'dir de nyid kho na smos so //
NK132(no)001:1646: de ltar stong gsum yungs 'brur 'jug pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1647: rdul phran gcig gis phyogs bcu khyab par nus pa sogs /
NK132(no)001:1648: ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod yul yangs dog med pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1649: sa brgyad pa mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa na yin te /
NK132(no)001:1650: de dag gi dbang du byas nas /
NK132(no)001:1651: de ltar ma lus thams cad phyogs su yang //
NK132(no)001:1652: skra tsam khyon la dus gsum tshad snyed kyi //
NK132(no)001:1653: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho zhing rnams rgya mtsho dang //
NK132(no)001:1654: bskal pa rgya mtshor spyod cing rab tu 'jug /
NK132(no)001:1655: rdul gcig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing mang po bkod pa de ltar /
NK132(no)001:1656: ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i phyogs thams cad rnams su yang /
NK132(no)001:1657: skra rtse tsam gyis khyon la dus gsum gyi tshad ji snyed kyi ste /
NK132(no)001:1658: dus gsum du byung ba'i sangs rgyas grangs su bgrangs
NK132(no)001:1659: na zad mi shes pa rgya mtsho lta bu rnams
NK132(no)001:1660: / rang rang gi zhing khams rnams dang bcas pa /
NK132(no)001:1661: zhing khams rnams rgya mtsho ltar mi zad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1662: de dag re re yang dus bskal pa rgya mtsho ltar zad mi shes pa'i bar du /
NK132(no)001:1663: bdag kyang zhing khams re re byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod cing /
NK132(no)001:1665: lta zhing grol bar gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1667: skra tsam khyon la zhes pa la /
NK132(no)001:1668: byis pa'i lam du ces pa'i don du bshad nas /
NK132(no)001:1669: ma dag pa'i zhing la 'chad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1670: dzam bu gling kho na la 'char pa sogs ni /
NK132(no)001:1671: bshad pa mi bde bas ma bkod do //
NK132(no)001:1672: rdul phran gcig gi nang du sangs rgyas kyi zhing ston pa la /
NK132(no)001:1673: rmi lam na khang pa dog po'i nang du /
NK132(no)001:1674: glang po che'i khyu dang nags tshal la sogs pa bde bar spyod par snang la /
NK132(no)001:1675: sad pa'i dus na yang dran pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1676: chu snod gcig gi nang du nyi zla gza' skar yul ljongs la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:1677: chu la gzugs brnyan du 'char ba dper mdzad de /
NK132(no)001:1678: sems kyi snang ba tsam dang /
NK132(no)001:1680: de ltar snang ba mi 'gal ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1681: rnal 'byor gyi mthu stobs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir yid ches par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:1682: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa las kyang /
NK132(no)001:1683: 'jig rten mgon po skyob pa yin //
NK132(no)001:1684: bsam gtan las dang klu rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1685: sangs rgyas bdag nyid che rnams kyi //
NK132(no)001:1686: bsam gyis mi khyab bzhir bshad do //
NK132(no)001:1688: bsam gtan pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mthu dang /
NK132(no)001:1691: sangs rgyas kyi mthu bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan to //
NK132(no)001:1692: 'di legs par mthar phyin pa ji lta ba bzhin ni /
NK132(no)001:1693: chos kyi sprin la gnas pa yan chad kyi yon tan yin la /
NK132(no)001:1694: rjes mthun pa'am 'go brtsams pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1695: mi g.yo ba'i sa yan chad do //
NK132(no)001:1696: rgyal ba'i gsung mtha' dag la 'jug pa ni //
NK132(no)001:1697: gsung gcig yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra skad kyis //
NK132(no)001:1698: rgyal ba kun dbyangs yan lag rnam dag pa //
NK132(no)001:1699: 'gro ba kun gyi bsam pa ji bzhin dbyangs //
NK132(no)001:1700: sangs rgyas gsung la rtag tu 'jug par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:1701: de bzhin gshegs pa gcig gis gsung gcig kho na bka' stsal na /
NK132(no)001:1702: de yang yan lag rgya mtsho ste /
NK132(no)001:1703: gsung gi rang bzhin cha tshang ba dang cha tshang
NK132(no)001:1704: ba kho na rigs mi 'dra ba rgya mtsho ltar
NK132(no)001:1705: mtha' yas pa'i sgra skad du 'gyur te /
NK132(no)001:1707: skad dang dbyangs mtha' yas pa nyid kyi snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:1709: mos pa sna tshogs can gyi ni //
NK132(no)001:1710: 'khor mang rnams ni gnas pa la //
NK132(no)001:1711: gsung gcig bka' ni stsal ba na //
NK132(no)001:1712: gsung rnams du ma go 'gyur zhing //
NK132(no)001:1713: nga yi ched du yin no zhes //
NK132(no)001:1714: skye bo kun gyis rtogs 'gyur gang //
NK132(no)001:1715: 'di las rmad byung che ci yod //
NK132(no)001:1716: 'di las ches mtshar ci zhig yod ces so //
NK132(no)001:1717: gzhan yang de nyid rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK132(no)001:1718: gsung dbyangs kyi yan lag skyon thams cad dang bral
NK132(no)001:1719: zhing rnam par dag pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1720: ngo bo gcig tu yang gnas la /
NK132(no)001:1721: chos gang dang gang nyan par 'dod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1722: de dang des 'dul bar 'gyur ba'i 'gro ba kun
NK132(no)001:1723: gyi bsam pa ji lta ba bzhin du dbyangs de
NK132(no)001:1725: sangs rgyas gcig gi gsung gcig la khyad chos de 'dra tshang pa bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:1726: 'dren pa ma lus pa'i gsung mtha' dag kyang de dang 'dra'o //
NK132(no)001:1727: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas kyi gsung thams cad la /
NK132(no)001:1728: bdag dus rtag tu nyan pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1730: bdag gi ngag kyang rgyal ba'i gsung de dang rjes
NK132(no)001:1731: su mthun cing 'dra bar spyod pa'i tshul gyis 'jug
NK132(no)001:1732: par bagyi'o // 'di yang mthar phyin pa'i dus ni sngar ltar yin la /
NK132(no)001:1733: thog mar thob pa ni legs pa'i blo gros kyi sa la ste /
NK132(no)001:1734: der so so yang dag pa rig pa bzhi thob par bshad pa dang gnad gcig go //
NK132(no)001:1736: sangs rgyas gcig la chos nyan cing don go bzhin pa na /
NK132(no)001:1737: de dang dus mnyam kho nar sangs rgyas gzhan mang
NK132(no)001:1738: po la yang chos nyan cing tshigs 'dzin pa dang
NK132(no)001:1739: / don sems pa la gcig gis gcig la gegs
NK132(no)001:1740: mi byed cir mnyam par thos la mnyam par 'dzin
NK132(no)001:1741: cing mnyam par sems pa la dka' ba dang 'bad
NK132(no)001:1743: dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad dag /
NK132(no)001:1744: ces pa nas mgon po kun gyi drung du bdag mchi'o //
NK132(no)001:1745: zhes pa'i bar ni rgyal tshab kyi sa la gnas
NK132(no)001:1746: pa rnams kyi yon tan dang rjes su 'brel ba'i
NK132(no)001:1747: smon lam ste / de la rgyal tshab kyi sa zhes pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1748: sngags kyi theg pa la sogs pa gzhung gzhan 'ga' zhig tu /
NK132(no)001:1749: dgu pa sogs sna tshogs la bshad pa yod kyang /
NK132(no)001:1750: 'dir ni rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ba ste /
NK132(no)001:1751: bcu pa yin par shes par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:1752: de la dbang 'byor pa drug ste /
NK132(no)001:1760: dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad dag /'khor lo'i tshul rnams rab tu bskor ba yi //
NK132(no)001:1761: de dag gi yang gsung dbyangs mi zad la //
NK132(no)001:1762: blo yi stobs kyis bdag kyang rab tu 'jug /
NK132(no)001:1763: dus gsum du byon cing gshegs par 'gyur ba'i rgyal ba thams cad dag /
NK132(no)001:1764: sems can rnams grol ba'i ched du /
NK132(no)001:1765: chos kyi 'khor lo'i tshul rnams rab tu bskor ba yi /
NK132(no)001:1766: sangs rgyas de dag gi yang gsung dbyangs chos mi zad pa ste mtha' yas pa la /
NK132(no)001:1767: rang gi blo yi mthu thob pa'i stobs kyis bdag
NK132(no)001:1768: kyang gsung gi phrin las de la lhan cig tu
NK132(no)001:1769: rab tu 'jug par shog cig pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1770: 'dir snga ma gsung gcig sogs ni /
NK132(no)001:1771: chos thos pa'i dbang du byas pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:1772: 'di ni sangs rgyas kyi gsung dang ngo bo byed las 'dres par thob pa'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1773: des na sa bcu'i dbang phyug gis chos ston pa
NK132(no)001:1774: de nyid sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK132(no)001:1775: ba'ang yin la / sangs rgyas kyi zhal snga nas chos ston pa kun la'ang /
NK132(no)001:1776: byang chub sems dpa' de'i phrin las 'jug ste /
NK132(no)001:1777: don gcig la blo gros dang 'dun pa gcig tu
NK132(no)001:1778: dril ba'i dmag la sogs pa'i bya ba bzhin no
NK132(no)001:1779: // 'di'i rab tu 'jug pa zhes pa 'dres pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1780: chu klung rgya mtshor 'jug pa lta bu ste gsung
NK132(no)001:1781: nyan pa kho na la sbyor ba snga ma dang
NK132(no)001:1784: ma 'ongs bskal pa thams cad 'jug par yang //
NK132(no)001:1785: skad cig gcig gis bdag kyang 'jug par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:1786: gang yang bskal pa dus gsum tshad de dag /
NK132(no)001:1787: skad cig cha shas kyis ni zhugs par spyad //
NK132(no)001:1788: ma 'ongs pa'i bskal pa mang po thams cad du /
NK132(no)001:1789: nam mkhas gar khyab kyi 'jig rten mtha' yas pa rnams su /
NK132(no)001:1790: ji snyed pa'i chos 'byung ba thams cad la ye
NK132(no)001:1791: shes 'jug ste mngon shes kyis shes par gyur pa
NK132(no)001:1792: yang / de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis mkhyen pa de bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:1793: bdag gis kyang ye shes skad cig gcig gis 'jug pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1794: shes pa gcig gis dus thams cad kyi dngos po
NK132(no)001:1795: thams cad gcig char shes par bgyi zhes smon pa
NK132(no)001:1796: dang / gang yang bskal pa sngon 'das pa thams cad dang /
NK132(no)001:1797: da ltar dang ma 'ongs pa 'byung 'gyur te dus
NK132(no)001:1798: gsum ji tsam yod pa dang tshad mnyam pa'i bskal
NK132(no)001:1799: pa de dag thams cad skad cig gcig gi cha
NK132(no)001:1800: shas su 'jug cing bsgyur nus pa'i stobs kyis ni
NK132(no)001:1801: / bskal pa gcig nas bskal pa mtha' med pa'i
NK132(no)001:1802: bar ji ltar 'os 'os su skad cig gi nang
NK132(no)001:1804: byang chub kyi spyad pa spyod par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1806: bskal pa'am bskal pa mang po skad cig tu sdud pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1807: skad cig re re la yang bskal pa du ma ston pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1808: dper bgyi na sems can spyi mthun gyi rtsa ba'i snang ba la /
NK132(no)001:1809: skad cig gcig gam yud tsam gcig la sogs par snang ba'i dus tshod de la /
NK132(no)001:1810: byang chub sems dpa' rang nyid kyi snang ba la
NK132(no)001:1811: yang bskal pa dang skad cig mi 'gal bar 'char
NK132(no)001:1812: ba dang / rnam par 'phrul pa'i stobs kyis zhing khams 'di'i go sa dang /
NK132(no)001:1813: phyogs bcu gzhan gyi zhing khams mang por /
NK132(no)001:1814: de dang de'i sems can kun la bskal pa mang po yang dngos su myong zhing /
NK132(no)001:1815: dus de snyed du chos spyad pas tshogs rdzogs shing sgrib pa byang bar gyur pas te /
NK132(no)001:1816: skad cig gcig la bskal pa mtha' yas pa'i bar du sgrub dgos pa'i /
NK132(no)001:1818: spyod pa spyod long yang yod cing /
NK132(no)001:1819: gsog pa dang spyod nus pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1820: yang spyi mthun snang ba rtsa bde la bskal pa
NK132(no)001:1821: mang po yod kyang yun ring du thogs par ma
NK132(no)001:1822: nges te / bskal pa skad cig mar sdud pa'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)001:1823: bskal pa mang po'i bya ba nyams su myong bas yud tsam cig la 'grub par yang nus la /
NK132(no)001:1824: bya ba yud tsam gcig pu lan gcig gis bskal
NK132(no)001:1825: pa'am bskal pa mang po 'khyongs par yang byed do
NK132(no)001:1826: // de ltar na dus thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK132(no)001:1827: dus ring thung dbye ba med par spyod pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1828: 'di'i dgos pa ni skad cig la yang mtha' yas pa'i byed long yod la /
NK132(no)001:1829: bskal pa la yang yun ring bsgug mi dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK132(no)001:1830: dus thung ngu la bya ba rgya chen po mi 'grub par dogs pas /
NK132(no)001:1831: blo tsab tsob du 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1832: rgya chen po la yun ring thogs pas ngal zhing skyo bar 'gyur ba'i gnyen po'o //
NK132(no)001:1834: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge gang //
NK132(no)001:1835: de dag skad cig gcig la bdag gis blta //
NK132(no)001:1836: dus gsum du byung zhing gshegs pa'i mi'i seng ge
NK132(no)001:1837: bcom ldan 'das gang yin pa de dag thams cad
NK132(no)001:1838: skad cig gcig la dus gcig tu /
NK132(no)001:1839: lus pa med par bdag gis mngon sum du lta zhing /
NK132(no)001:1840: dus kyang thung ngu ma yin par rtag tu blta bar bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:1842: rtag tu de dag gi ni spyod yul la //
NK132(no)001:1843: sgyu mar gyur pa'i rnam thar stobs kyis 'jug /
NK132(no)001:1844: rtag tu sangs rgyas de dag gi ni spyod yul te /
NK132(no)001:1845: rtogs bya'i yul dang rtogs byed kyi ye shes dang /
NK132(no)001:1846: de dag gi rnam par thar pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1847: rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la 'jug par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:1849: mnyam gzhag gi ye shes bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK132(no)001:1850: po spros bral rnam pa thams cad pa sgyu ma
NK132(no)001:1851: lta bu'i ye shes mngon sum du rtogs pa'i nus
NK132(no)001:1852: pas / rjes thob kyi ye shes sgyu ma ltar
NK132(no)001:1853: snang bar gyur la de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK132(no)001:1854: pas / gyi stobs las / sgrib pa'i khyad par
NK132(no)001:1855: mang po las grol zhing rnam par thar pa'i stobs
NK132(no)001:1856: kyis gang la gang 'dod du sgyur thub cing spyod
NK132(no)001:1858: 'di ni don la nges par na sangs rgyas dang phrin las mnyam por spyod pa'i don no //
NK132(no)001:1860: gang yang dus gsum dag gi zhing bkod pa //
NK132(no)001:1861: de dag rdul gcig steng du mngon par sgrub //
NK132(no)001:1862: de ltar ma lus phyogs rnams thams cad du //
NK132(no)001:1863: rgyal ba dag gi zhing rnams bkod la 'jug /
NK132(no)001:1864: gang yang dus gsum du byung zin dang 'byung ba dang 'byung 'gyur dag gi /
NK132(no)001:1865: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi bkod pa de dag thams cad /
NK132(no)001:1869: rdul phra rab gcig gi steng ste go sa ru /
NK132(no)001:1871: rdul gcig po de la sgrub pa ltar /
NK132(no)001:1872: ma lus pa'i phyogs rnams thams cad du /
NK132(no)001:1873: rdul mtha' dag la rgyal ba dag gi zhing rnams sgrub cing bkod pa yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1874: rgyan gyi khyad par rnam pa thams cad pa la 'jug par gyur cig pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1876: zhing khams de lta bu ston nus pa'i bya ba la 'jug pa'o //
NK132(no)001:1877: rdul gcig pa dus gsum gyi zhing khams mtha' dag
NK132(no)001:1878: ston pa ni gzhi phra shos dang bkod pa rgya
NK132(no)001:1879: che shos kyi mtha' nas bzung ba yin pas /
NK132(no)001:1881: rdul gnyis pa'i bkod pa nas brtsams te dus gsum
NK132(no)001:1882: gyi zhing gi bar du sna tshogs par ston to
NK132(no)001:1883: // des mtshon te rim pa bzhin du sbyar nas /
NK132(no)001:1884: nyi zer rdul re re la yang dus gsum gyi
NK132(no)001:1885: zhing khams la sogs pa de ltar ston pa dang
NK132(no)001:1902: stong gsum re re la sogs pa'i bar du yang de ltar ston la /
NK132(no)001:1903: so so so sor thad mnyam pa la yang /
NK132(no)001:1904: 'jig rten gyi khams gcag la go sa tha mi dad par /
NK132(no)001:1905: 'jig rten gyi khams tha dad pa yang tshad mnyam pa du ma gcig shul du gcig ston la /
NK132(no)001:1906: gzhi tshad chen po la chung ngus khyad pa yang dpag tu med pa ston te /
NK132(no)001:1907: stong gsum gcig gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams gcig gis khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1908: dzam bu gling gcig gis khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1909: grong khyer gcig gis khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1910: lus gcig gis khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1911: skra gcig gis khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1912: rdul phran gcig gis khyab pa'i bar du yang ston to //
NK132(no)001:1913: yang rdul phran gzhan cig gi nang du chud pa de nyid kyis /
NK132(no)001:1914: gzhan stong gsum mang po yang non pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1915: gzhan du dus kyang nges pa med par ston te 'das pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1916: ma 'ongs ba dang ma 'ongs pa yang 'das par
NK132(no)001:1917: sgyur ba la sogs pa rnam par 'phrul pa bsam
NK132(no)001:1918: gyis mi khyab pa kho na 'byung ba'o //
NK132(no)001:1920: gang yang ma byon 'jig rten sgron ma rnams //
NK132(no)001:1921: de dag rim par 'tshang rgya 'khor lo bskor //
NK132(no)001:1922: mya ngan 'das pa rab tu zhi mtha' ston //
NK132(no)001:1923: mgon po kun gyi drung du bdag mchi'o //
NK132(no)001:1924: gang yang ma byon pa'i sangs rgyas 'jig rten snang bar byed pa'i sgron me de dag rnams /
NK132(no)001:1925: rang rang gi mdzad pa'i rim pa mtha' dag ston pa rnams ma 'khrugs par spyod de /
NK132(no)001:1927: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1928: mya ngan las 'das pa sdug bsngal rab tu zhi ba'i mtha' thob pa'i tshul ston par mdzad pa'i /
NK132(no)001:1929: mgon po sangs rgyas de dag kun gyi drug du bdag dus gcig tu mchis pa te /
NK132(no)001:1930: 'gro zhing bslab la phyin par bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:1931: sangs rgyas sogs mdzad pa gsum gyi mtshon pa ste /
NK132(no)001:1932: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ston pa'i gnas skabs thams cad du der phyin par byas nas /
NK132(no)001:1933: ci zhig byed ce na mchod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1934: rdzu 'phrul ston pa dang chos bstan pas sems can 'dul ba dang /
NK132(no)001:1935: chos kyi don 'dri ba la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:1936: mdor na sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa thams cad kyi dpung rogs bya ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:1937: don la bdag nyid gsar du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas zin gyi dbang du byas na ni /
NK132(no)001:1938: mdzad pa phrin las gcig pa kho nar gyur cing /
NK132(no)001:1939: sa bcu pa nyid la gnas pa'i skabs yin na yang /
NK132(no)001:1940: sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba la sangs rgyas su gyur te sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:1941: sangs rgyas su mi ston yang /
NK132(no)001:1942: sangs rgyas gzhan gyi mdzad pa'i las byed pa por 'byung ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:1944: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa gnyis kar la 'jug pa'i /
NK132(no)001:1945: rnam grangs gzhan gyi smon lam bstan pa la /
NK132(no)001:1946: sgrub pa gtso bor gyur pa stobs kyi smon lam dang /
NK132(no)001:1947: phan yon gtso bor gyur pa bsam mi khyab kyi smon lam dang /
NK132(no)001:1948: mthar thug smon lam bla na med par gcig tu bya ba ste /
NK132(no)001:1954: kun tu myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1955: kun nas sgo yi theg pa'i stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1956: kun tu yon tan spyod pa'i stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1957: kun tu khyab pa byams pa dag gi stobs //
NK132(no)001:1958: kun nas dge ba'i bsod nams stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:1959: chags pa med par gyur pa'i ye shes stobs //
NK132(no)001:1960: shes rab thabs dang ting 'dzin stobs dag gis //
NK132(no)001:1961: byang chub stobs rnams yang dag sgrub par byed //
NK132(no)001:1965: mtha' med pa'i zhing khams rnams kyang skad cig gis bgrod nus shing /
NK132(no)001:1966: zhing tha dad par du mar yang dus gcig car
NK132(no)001:1967: bgrod thub pas kun tu myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK132(no)001:1968: stobs rnams dang / kun nas sgo zhes bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:1969: sgo kun dang ldan pa'i don te /
NK132(no)001:1970: thabs tshul gyis rim pa mtha' yas pa'i sgo nas /
NK132(no)001:1971: sems can gyi don spyod pa dang ldan pa'i sems bskyed ni /
NK132(no)001:1972: de la brten nas bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bgrod nus pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1973: bzhon pa dang 'dra bas theg pa'i stobs te de rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:1974: pha rol tu phyin pa dang bsdu dngos bzhi dang tshad med bzhi la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:1975: yon tan du ma dang 'grogs pa'i snyoms 'jug dgu dang zad par bcu dang /
NK132(no)001:1977: mngon shes drug la sogs pa yon tan kun tu spyod pa'i stobs rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:1978: kun nas sems can thams cad la nye ring med
NK132(no)001:1979: par khyab pa'i byams pa la sogs pa tshad med
NK132(no)001:1980: bzhi po dag gi stobs dang kun tu sems can
NK132(no)001:1981: thams cad la phan pa dang bde ba byed pa'i
NK132(no)001:1982: phyir / rab tu dge ba'i sbyin sogs bsod nams kyi stobs rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:1983: dus gsum gyi dngos po thams cad la chags thogs med par 'jug pa'i mngon par mkhyen pa /
NK132(no)001:1985: chos dbyings ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi stobs dang /
NK132(no)001:1986: gzhan don sgrub pa la mkhas pa thabs mkhas kyi stobs dang /
NK132(no)001:1987: dmigs pa la rtse gcig pa gang zhig mngon shes
NK132(no)001:1988: dang rnam 'phrul la sogs pa yon tan bskyed pa'i
NK132(no)001:1989: rgyu / dpa' bar 'gro ba la sogs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs te /
NK132(no)001:1990: stobs dgu po de dag gi sgo nas 'bad pas /
NK132(no)001:1991: byang chub kyi stobs te bla na med pa'i byang
NK132(no)001:1992: chub 'phral du thob par byed pa'i ye shes kyi
NK132(no)001:1993: khyad par / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK132(no)001:1994: nyid dang rnam pa mthun cing rgya khyon mtshungs pa'i
NK132(no)001:1995: khyad par / / lam gyi bden pa ni /
NK132(no)001:1996: byang chub kyi stobs yin la /
NK132(no)001:1997: de yang rnam pa mtha' yas pa 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:1998: rnams shes mang po'i sgra smos te /
NK132(no)001:1999: de rnams yang dag par sgrub par byed par shog cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2001: 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin dang phal po che'i skabs
NK132(no)001:2002: gzhan las 'byung ba ltar gyi byang chub sems dpa'i
NK132(no)001:2003: stobs bcu dang phal cher 'dra bar snang ste /
NK132(no)001:2005: byang chub sems dpa'i stobs bcu ni //
NK132(no)001:2006: bsam pa lhag bsam sbyor ba dang //
NK132(no)001:2007: shes rab smon lam spyod pa dang //
NK132(no)001:2008: theg pa rnam 'phrul byang chub dang //
NK132(no)001:2009: chos 'khor bskor ba'i stobs rnams so //
NK132(no)001:2013: theg pa'i stobs ni dngos su gsal la /
NK132(no)001:2014: rnam par 'phrul pa'i stobs ni rdzu 'phrul dang bsam
NK132(no)001:2015: pa'i stobs ni byams pa dang lhag pa'i bsam pa'i
NK132(no)001:2017: sbyor ba'i stobs ni bsod nams kyi stobs dang /
NK132(no)001:2018: thabs kyi stobs gcig po'i nang tshan nas gtso bo
NK132(no)001:2019: khyad par can logs su phye ba ni smon lam
NK132(no)001:2020: gyi stobs dang / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i stobs gnyis so //
NK132(no)001:2021: de bas na ga zhung 'dir bshad pa'i ting nge
NK132(no)001:2022: 'dzin gyi stobs lhag pa ltar byung yang spyod pa
NK132(no)001:2023: dang lhag bsam du 'dus par mngon to //
NK132(no)001:2024: gnyis pa stobs kyi byed las ni /
NK132(no)001:2025: las kyi stobs rnams yongs su dag byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2026: nyon mongs stobs rnams kun tu 'joms par byed //
NK132(no)001:2027: bdud kyi stobs rnams stobs med rab byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2028: bzang po spyod pa'i stobs ni rdzogs par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2029: de la spang bar bya ba'i las ni /
NK132(no)001:2030: khams gsum po skyed par byed pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2033: las dngos kyang mi dge ba'i las dang /
NK132(no)001:2035: zag bcas kyi dge ba de yang gnyis te /
NK132(no)001:2036: 'dod khams kyis bsdus pa'i dge ba bsod nams dang /
NK132(no)001:2037: khams gong ma gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i dge ba /
NK132(no)001:2039: rjes su mthun pa'i las ni /
NK132(no)001:2040: las rnams kyis bzhag pa'i bag chags gang yin pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2041: de lta bu'i las kyi stobs rnams yongs su dag par byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2043: lus dang sems rab tu ma zhi bar rnyogs pa
NK132(no)001:2044: dang rang nyid gnod par byed pa'i rnam rtog ste
NK132(no)001:2048: the tshom te lta ba min pa lnga dang /
NK132(no)001:2053: brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin te lta ba lnga'o //
NK132(no)001:2054: de dag ni rtsa ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:2055: gzhan yang khro ba la sogs pa nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu dang /
NK132(no)001:2056: nyon mongs pa'i rab dbye phra mo gzhan rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:2057: nyon mongs pa rnams kyi bag chags dang gnas ngan len gang yin pa rnams kyang te /
NK132(no)001:2058: nyon mongs pa'i stobs rnams kun tu 'joms ste /
NK132(no)001:2059: nyon mongs phal cher spangs shing /
NK132(no)001:2060: 'ga' zhig rtsad nas rang ma spangs kyang /
NK132(no)001:2061: de la rang dbang 'byor pa'i tshul gyis /
NK132(no)001:2062: de'i stobs bcom nas lam gyi grogs su byas pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2063: skabs 'dir phyogs re mgo gnon gyi gnyen po spyad
NK132(no)001:2064: pa rnam par spyod pa dang mtha' dag dpyis 'byin
NK132(no)001:2065: gyi gnyen po bdag med gnyis dang /
NK132(no)001:2066: nyon mongs byang chub kyi yan lag tu sgyur ba'i
NK132(no)001:2067: thabs mkhas la sogs pa'i rnam gzhag rnams gzhan las
NK132(no)001:2068: 'byung ba ltar rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:2069: bdud kyi stobs rnams zhes pa la spyir bdud bzhi yin yang /
NK132(no)001:2070: nyon mongs pa'i bdud ni sngar bshad zin pas /
NK132(no)001:2071: phung po'i bdud dang 'chi bdag gi bdud dang lha'i bu'i bdud do //
NK132(no)001:2073: rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang rtag pa'i chos rdul tsam yang ma dmigs te /
NK132(no)001:2074: phung po stong par rtogs pa phung po'i bdud bcom pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2075: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni rtag cing brtan pa /
NK132(no)001:2076: skye 'jig thams cad dang bral bar rtogs pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom shing /
NK132(no)001:2077: kun rdzob tha mal gyi sdug pa dang mi sdug pa sogs yul la mngon par ma zhen la /
NK132(no)001:2078: chos nyid kyi gzugs sogs don dam pa'i spyod yul mtha' yas pa la mngon par spyod pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2079: gang zhig nyon mongs bskyed du 'jug cing /
NK132(no)001:2080: sdig to mi dge ba'i chos la 'khrid pa'i lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pas na /
NK132(no)001:2081: bdud kyi stobs rnams ni stobs med cing mi mngon par rab tu byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2082: bzang po spyod pa'i stobs ni rdzogs par bgyid pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2083: bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas thob par smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2084: gnyis pa phan yon gtso bor ston pa bsam mi khyab kyi smon lam ni /
NK132(no)001:2085: zhing rnams rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2086: sems can rgya mtsho dag ni rnam par grol //
NK132(no)001:2087: chos rnams rgya mtsho rab tu mthong byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2088: ye shes rgya mtsho rab tu rtogs par byed //
NK132(no)001:2089: spyod pa rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2090: smon lam rgya mtsho rab tu rdzogs par byed //
NK132(no)001:2091: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho rab tu mchod byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2092: bskal pa rgya mtshor mi skyo spyad par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2093: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams rgya mtsho thams cad bde ba can dang /
NK132(no)001:2094: pad+ma can gyi 'jig rten bzhin du ngan 'gro dang nad dang sdug bsngal dang /
NK132(no)001:2097: tsher ma la sogs pa spangs pa /
NK132(no)001:2098: rin po che'i sa gzhi dang ljon pa la sogs pa rgyan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2099: zhing khams rnam par dag pa ste bzang po 'ba' zhig tu byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2100: sems can rgya mtsho dag ni /
NK132(no)001:2101: sdug bsngal dang sgrib pa las rnam par grol bar byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2102: lung rtogs kyi chos rgya mtsho rnams ni /
NK132(no)001:2103: shes rab kyi mig gis rab tu mthong bar byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2104: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa'i chos mngon sum du mthong ba'i ye shes rgya mtsho rnams ni /
NK132(no)001:2105: rab tu rtogs pa ste thob par byed la /
NK132(no)001:2106: spyod pa ste bdag gzhan la phan pa'i thabs rgya mtsho lta bu dag la ni /
NK132(no)001:2107: bsam pa dri ma can la sogs pa'i skyon rnams /
NK132(no)001:2108: rnam par dag par byed cing rang gzhan gyi don
NK132(no)001:2109: gyi smon lam grangs med pa rgya mtsho rnams ni
NK132(no)001:2110: / rab tu rdzogs pa ste 'bras bu 'grub par byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2111: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho thams cad ni /
NK132(no)001:2112: mchod pa rnam pa bcu la sogs pa thams cad kyis /
NK132(no)001:2113: rab tu mchod par byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2114: de ltar zhing dag par byed pa la sogs pa bdun po de yang /
NK132(no)001:2115: bskal pa rgya mtsho ste mtha' med pa'i bar du
NK132(no)001:2116: skyo ba med cing rab tu dga' bas spyad par
NK132(no)001:2118: de ltar na rgya mtsho lta bu brgyad kyi /
NK132(no)001:2119: dang po gnyis ni zhing spyong dang sems can smin byed yin la /
NK132(no)001:2120: lhag ma lnga ni smon lam dang tshogs rdzogs pa'i thabs so //
NK132(no)001:2121: tha ma ni rdzogs smin sbyongs gsum de ji tsam du spyod pa'i dus bstan pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2122: gsum pa smon lam mthar thug bla na med par gcig tu bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2123: gang yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yi //
NK132(no)001:2124: byang chub spyod pa'i smon lam bye brag rnams //
NK132(no)001:2125: bzang po spyod pas byang chub sangs rgyas nas //
NK132(no)001:2126: de kun ma lus bdag gis rdzogs par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2127: gang yang dus gsum du byon gshegs mdzad pa'i //
NK132(no)001:2128: rgyal ba mtha' yas pa rnams kyis sngon thog ma med pa'i dus nas brtsams pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2129: byang chub spyod pa'i smon lam gyi bye brag mtha' yas pa de rnams kun /
NK132(no)001:2130: ma lus par bdag gis rdzogs par bgyi bar smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2131: de yang dus nam gyi tshe rdzogs par 'gyur snyam na /
NK132(no)001:2132: bzang po spyod pa spyad pas bla na med pas
NK132(no)001:2133: byang chub tu sangs rgyas par gyur nas zhes pa'o
NK132(no)001:2134: // de lta bu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi smon lam bdag gis rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2135: rgyal sras mchog gnyis dang yang smon lam gcig tu bya ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2136: rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi thu bo pa //
NK132(no)001:2137: gang gi ming ni kun tu bzang zhes bya //
NK132(no)001:2138: mkhas pa de dang mtshungs par spyad pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)001:2139: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK132(no)001:2140: de yang rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi mchog thu bo pa /
NK132(no)001:2141: gang gi ming ni kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar grags pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2142: mkhas pa de dang mtshungs par chos la spyod pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2143: bdag gi dge ba 'di dag thams cad thams cad rab tu bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK132(no)001:2144: 'di la kun tu bzang po nyid kyis rang dang
NK132(no)001:2145: mtshungs par smon lam byed par mi 'thad do snyam
NK132(no)001:2146: na / 'di ni gzhon nu nor bzang la sogs
NK132(no)001:2147: pa rjes 'jug rnams kyi 'debs pa'i don du gsungs
NK132(no)001:2149: kun bzang nyid kyis rang don du ni smon lam
NK132(no)001:2150: gzhan rnams kyang 'debs mi dgos par khyad med do
NK132(no)001:2152: lus dang ngag dang yid kyang rnam dag cing //
NK132(no)001:2153: spyod pa rnam dag zhing rnams yongs dag dang //
NK132(no)001:2154: bsngo ba'ang bzang po mkhas pa ci 'dra ba //
NK132(no)001:2155: de 'drar bdag kyang de dang mtshungs par shog /
NK132(no)001:2156: sems can gang la gang 'dul gyis lus mtha' yas par ston pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2157: dbyangs gcig 'gro ba kun gyi skad dang 'byor ba'i ngag dang /
NK132(no)001:2158: rnam par mi rtog bzhin du ma 'dres par shes
NK132(no)001:2159: la snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la yang
NK132(no)001:2161: sgo gsum rnam par dag par gyur cing /
NK132(no)001:2162: phar phyin drug gi spyod pa la /
NK132(no)001:2163: ser sna sogs kyi dri ma rnam par dag pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2164: zhing ma dag pa rnams kyang yongs su dag par 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2165: bsngo ba bzang po mtha' dang bral ba btab pas mkhas pa byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams /
NK132(no)001:2166: kun bzang dang lhan cig spyod pa ci 'dra ba
NK132(no)001:2167: de 'drar bdag kyang kun tu bzang po dang mtshungs
NK132(no)001:2168: par shog cig /'grel pa kha cig las /
NK132(no)001:2169: mkhas pa bzang po bsngo ba ci 'dra ba /
NK132(no)001:2171: don la khyad cher med do //
NK132(no)001:2172: kun nas dge ba bzang po spyod pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)001:2173: 'jam dpal gyi ni smon lam spyad par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2174: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
NK132(no)001:2175: de yi bya ba ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2176: thog mtha' bar gsum kun tu kun nas dag pa'i chos /
NK132(no)001:2177: bzang po spyod pa spyad pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2178: 'phags mchog 'jam dpal gyi smon lam ji lta ba
NK132(no)001:2179: bzhin du bdag gis kyang spyad spyod par gyur cig
NK132(no)001:2180: / sangs rgyas rnams dang kun bzang dang 'jam dpal gyi smon lam de kun /
NK132(no)001:2181: ma 'ongs mtha' med pa'i bskal pa kun tu mi skyo zhing /
NK132(no)001:2183: rgyal ba sras bcas de'i bzhed don gyi bya ba
NK132(no)001:2184: ma lus pa bdag gis rdzogs par bgyi bar smon
NK132(no)001:2185: pa'o // gsum pa don bsdu ni /
NK132(no)001:2186: spyod pa dag ni tshad yod ma gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:2187: yon tan rnams kyang tshad gzung med par shog /
NK132(no)001:2188: spyod pa tshad med pa la gnas nas kyang //
NK132(no)001:2189: de dag 'phrul pa thams cad 'tshal bar bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2190: bdag gi sbyin pa la sogs pa rgyu spyod pa dag gi mtha' ni /
NK132(no)001:2191: 'di tsam mo zhes tshad gzung du yod par ma gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:2192: de las 'byung ba'i 'bras bu gzungs dang spobs pa la sogs pa'i yon tan rnams kyang /
NK132(no)001:2193: tshad gzung du med par shog cig /
NK132(no)001:2194: de ltar spyod pa dang yon tan tshad gzung du med pa la gnas par bya nas kyang /
NK132(no)001:2195: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de dag rnams kyi /
NK132(no)001:2196: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam par 'phrul pa thams cad bdag gis 'tshal ba ste /
NK132(no)001:2197: thog mar mthong zhing shes la /
NK132(no)001:2198: mthar thob par 'gyur bar smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2199: gzhung 'dir 'bras bu mthar thug sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul /
NK132(no)001:2200: yang nas yang du byung yang /
NK132(no)001:2202: sgos su rgyas shing gsal bar mi 'byung ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2203: bzang po spyod pa po 'dod chen pa ma yin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK132(no)001:2204: dang po'i sems bskyed pa dang 'brel ba'i smon lam gyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2205: sems dpa' chen po'i gnas skabs na /
NK132(no)001:2206: rang don yid byed kyi khyad par gzhan ni cher mi 'byung la /
NK132(no)001:2207: bdag don du byang chub gnyer ba tsam zhig 'byung nye na /
NK132(no)001:2208: de spang pa'i phyir du yang bzang po spyod pa'i dam bca' byed pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2209: so so skye bo'i gnas skabs thams cad du yang /
NK132(no)001:2210: rang don yid byed 'gog pa la /
NK132(no)001:2211: dam bca' 'di kho na gal che zhing /
NK132(no)001:2212: bdag gzhan rje ba'i byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba
NK132(no)001:2213: dang mthar thug pa yang bzang po spyod pa'i dam
NK132(no)001:2214: bca' la ltos pa yin pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2215: byang chub bsgrub pa la ngang thung ba spong pa'i go cha chen po yang 'adi'o //
NK132(no)001:2216: gsum pa smon lam gyi mtha' dang phan yon bstan pa la /
NK132(no)001:2217: smon lam gyi mtha' bshad pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2220: nam mkha'i mthar thug gyur pa ji tsam par //
NK132(no)001:2221: sems can ma lus mtha' yang de bzhin te //
NK132(no)001:2222: ji tsam las dang nyon mongs mthar thug pa //
NK132(no)001:2223: bdag gi smon lam mtha' yang de tsam mo //
NK132(no)001:2224: nam mkha'i mthar thug par gyur par ces pa la /
NK132(no)001:2225: nam mkha' la mtha' med pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2226: phyogs bcu mtha' med pa ji tsam par /
NK132(no)001:2227: sems can ma lus pa'i mtha' yang de bzhin te mtha' med pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2228: sems ji tsam par las dang nyon mongs pa yang de tsam ste /
NK132(no)001:2229: ji tsam las dang nyon mongs pa'i mtha' tshad gzung du med par gyur pa de bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:2230: bdag gi smon lam gyi mtha' yang de tsam dang mnyam pa'i phyir tshad med pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2231: mdor na sems can thams cad kyi las dang nyon
NK132(no)001:2232: mongs gcig kyang ma lus pa bdag gis sel ba
NK132(no)001:2233: dang / sems can gcig kyang ma lus par thams
NK132(no)001:2234: cad bla na med pa'i byang chub la 'god pa'i
NK132(no)001:2235: dang / smon lam dang / de ma rdzogs kyi
NK132(no)001:2236: bar du yang sems can rnams kyi sdug bsngal dang
NK132(no)001:2237: mi 'dod pa mtha' dag bdag gis 'joms pa dang
NK132(no)001:2238: dang / smon lam dang / / gang dang gang
NK132(no)001:2239: du ji ltar 'os pa'i phun sum tshogs pa thams
NK132(no)001:2240: cad kyang bdag gis sgrub par smon cing /
NK132(no)001:2241: de ltar smon pa yang dad pa dang snying stobs shin tu brtan pa la gzhi byas /
NK132(no)001:2243: 'dun pa dang brtson 'grus drag pos mtshams sbyar /
NK132(no)001:2244: de thams cad stong nyid rtogs pa'i ye shes dang
NK132(no)001:2245: ji ltar dmigs pa de ltar thams cad la dbang
NK132(no)001:2246: 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi nang du bcug ste
NK132(no)001:2247: / dus bskal pa mtha' med par sgyur byed kyi
NK132(no)001:2248: grogs tshogs bsags pa'i sgo grangs med pas yongs su
NK132(no)001:2249: sgyur te bsngosa shing smon lam btab pa yin pa'i
NK132(no)001:2250: / phyir / smon lam de yang ji ltar bsngosa pa dang mthun par ni 'grub la /
NK132(no)001:2251: 'khor ba'i gnas na sems can gcig kyang ma lus par rdzogs pa ni mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2252: smon lam 'di yi 'bras bu rdzogs zin nas zad pa ni mi srid pa /
NK132(no)001:2253: des na sems can mtha' yas pa zhig rgyun mi 'chad par grol bar 'gyur yang /
NK132(no)001:2254: sems can gyi khams la 'phel 'grib med de mi zad pa bzhin du /
NK132(no)001:2255: smon lam 'di yang ji ltar smon pa dang mthun
NK132(no)001:2256: pa'i gzhan don rlabs chen rgyun mi 'chad pa'i 'bras
NK132(no)001:2257: bu 'byin bzhin du phyi ma'i mu mthar thug par
NK132(no)001:2259: de'i 'bras bu zad cing rdzogs pa ni mi srid do //
NK132(no)001:2260: des na smon lam rdzogs pa ni 'grub rung thams cad 'grub nus pa'i don yin /
NK132(no)001:2261: sngar rdzogs zin pa'i don min no //
NK132(no)001:2262: tshigs bcad 'di yang smon lam gyi ngo bo shin
NK132(no)001:2263: tu bzang zhing rgya che bar ston pa yin pas
NK132(no)001:2264: dang / grub 'bras kyi che ba ston pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2265: phan yon gyi don chen du 'dus so snyam pa ni bdag gi rnam par rtog pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2266: kha cig smon lam ji tsam du 'debs pa'i tshad bstan pa zer te mi legs so //
NK132(no)001:2267: gnyis pa phan yon dngos bstan pa la /
NK132(no)001:2272: gang yang phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams mtha' yas pa //
NK132(no)001:2273: rin chen brgyan te rgyal ba rnams la 'bul //
NK132(no)001:2274: lha dang mi yi bde ba'i mchog rnams kyang //
NK132(no)001:2275: zhing gi rdul snyed bskal par phul ba bas //
NK132(no)001:2276: gang gis bsngo ba'i rgyal po 'di thos nas //
NK132(no)001:2277: byang chub mchog gi rjes su rab mos shing //
NK132(no)001:2278: lan cig tsam yang dad pa bskyed pa ni //
NK132(no)001:2279: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:2280: 'dis ni bsod nams khyad par du 'phags pa yongs su sdud pa bstan pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2281: mchod pa'i yul zhing gi mchog sangs rgyas la //
NK132(no)001:2282: mchod pa'i dngos po rgya che sna tshogs phan byed mang //
NK132(no)001:2284: khyad par bzhi ldan phul ba de 'jig rten du bsod nams ches che bar grags na /
NK132(no)001:2285: de bas bsngo ba 'di la mos pa bskyed pa yang phan yon che ste /
NK132(no)001:2286: 'di la 'di dang phyi ma'i phan yon gzhan mtha' yas yod pa lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK132(no)001:2288: gang yang phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams zhing rnams mtha' yas pa rab tu rgya che ba rnams /
NK132(no)001:2289: mchod pa'i khyad par sna tshogs pa /
NK132(no)001:2290: rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK132(no)001:2291: in dra n+ai la'i ri bo la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:2292: rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs pas brgyan cing bkang nas /
NK132(no)001:2293: de las gzhan phan par byed pa'i dngos po /
NK132(no)001:2294: lha dang mi'i bde ba'i rgyu mchog ste /
NK132(no)001:2295: kha zas dang gos dang gnas khang dang bang mdzod dang /
NK132(no)001:2298: gzhan yang 'dod pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa dang
NK132(no)001:2299: bcas pa'i phyogs bcu'i zhing khams de dag rnams kyang
NK132(no)001:2300: / grangs ces mang ba zhing gi rdul snyed dang /
NK132(no)001:2301: dus mang ba bskal pa'i bar du rgyun mi 'chad par /
NK132(no)001:2302: zhing gi dmar rgyal ba rnams la phul na bsod nams shin tu che'o zhes grags so //
NK132(no)001:2303: de ni gong du smos pa ltar /
NK132(no)001:2306: sgyur ba khyad par can bzhi po des ma zin cing /
NK132(no)001:2307: byang chub tu ma bsngosa na nan ta ra na de tsam du ches che ba ma yin te /
NK132(no)001:2308: bsod nams de yang zag pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2309: rnam smin myong nas zad par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2310: de bas ni 'di bzang ste gang gis bzang po spyod pa bsngo ba'i rgyal po 'di /
NK132(no)001:2311: thos shing thos byung gi shes rab kyis go nas
NK132(no)001:2312: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog gi rjes su
NK132(no)001:2314: byang chub la mtha' yas pa'i yon tan dang ldan par nges shes skyes shing /
NK132(no)001:2315: des drangs te snying thag pa nas byang chub la
NK132(no)001:2316: dang ba'i dad pa lan cig tsam yang bskyed cing
NK132(no)001:2318: snga ma de bas ches khyad par du 'phags pa'i bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'gyur te /
NK132(no)001:2319: dad pa po'i dad pas smon lam 'debs pa po 'di ni de 'drar 'gyur ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2320: yang na 'dir dad pa bskyed pa kho na'i phan yon la sbyar kyang chog ste /
NK132(no)001:2321: gzhung gi dngos bstan de tsam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2322: de las de mchog yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni phyi
NK132(no)001:2323: ma 'di ni zag pa med pa'i dge ba yin
NK132(no)001:2324: pa dang / 'di las nges par sangs rgyas kyi sa bon thebs nas /
NK132(no)001:2325: phugs kyi 'bras bu mi zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2326: rjes su mos pa'i don ni /
NK132(no)001:2327: byang chub nyid kyi gnas tshul dang mthun par /
NK132(no)001:2328: mos pa byas pa'i don yin te /
NK132(no)001:2329: mos pa gang dag mos yul dngos po'i rjes su mi 'gro ba /
NK132(no)001:2330: lha nag po dang drag po dbang phyug la sogs
NK132(no)001:2331: pa nyon mongs kun tu spyod pa la nyon mongs
NK132(no)001:2332: med par 'dod pa sogs mos pa dang dngos po
NK132(no)001:2333: dang rjes su mi mthun pa de rnams dgag pa'i
NK132(no)001:2334: don no // thos nas zhes pas /
NK132(no)001:2336: mos pa dang dad pa zhes bstan pas gzhan gyis bskul ba dang 'gran pa'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)001:2337: g.yam rgyugs su smon lam 'debs pa sogs /
NK132(no)001:2338: 'di dag la dngos su phan yon chen po de lta bu mi 'byung ngo //
NK132(no)001:2340: 'on kyang bsam pa dag pa dang ma dag pa gang yin yang rung te /
NK132(no)001:2341: chos 'di dang 'brel ba thob pa'i phyir ma 'ongs
NK132(no)001:2342: pa na don chen po dang 'phrad pa'i rgyu ni
NK132(no)001:2345: gang gis bzang spyod smon lam 'di btab pa //
NK132(no)001:2346: des ni ngan song thams cad spang bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2347: des ni grogs po ngan pa spangs pa yin //
NK132(no)001:2348: snang ba mtha' yas de yang des myur mthong //
NK132(no)001:2349: de dag rnyed pa rab rnyed bde bar 'tsho //
NK132(no)001:2350: mi tshe 'dir yang de dag legs par 'ong //
NK132(no)001:2351: kun tu bzang po de yang ci 'dra bar //
NK132(no)001:2352: de dag ring por mi thogs de bzhin 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2353: mtshams med lnga po dag gi sdig pa rnams //
NK132(no)001:2354: gang gis mi shes dbang gis byas pa dag /
NK132(no)001:2355: de yis bzang po spyod pa 'di brjod na //
NK132(no)001:2356: myur du ma lus yongs su byang bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2357: ye shes dang ni gzugs dang mtshan rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:2358: rigs dang kha dog rnams dang ldan par 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2359: bdud dang mu stegs mang pos de mi thub //
NK132(no)001:2360: 'jig rten gsum po kun na'ang mchod par 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2361: byang chub shing dbang drung du de myur 'gro //
NK132(no)001:2362: song nas sems can phan phyir der 'dug ste //
NK132(no)001:2363: byang chub 'tshang rgya 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK132(no)001:2364: bdud rnams sde dang bcas pa thams cad btul //
NK132(no)001:2365: skyes bu gang gi dad pa phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pas /
NK132(no)001:2366: phan yon rnam pa bcu gsum po 'di dag rim gyis thob par 'gyur te /
NK132(no)001:2368: skyes bu gang zhig gis smon lam 'di brtson pas btab par byas nas /
NK132(no)001:2369: ngan song du skye 'gyur gyi sdig pa thams cad byang nas /
NK132(no)001:2370: des ni re zhig las kyi dbang gis ngan song du 'gro ba thams cad spangs par 'gyur ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2373: tshe 'di dang phyi ma thams cad du grogs po ngan pa spangs pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:2374: grogs ngan dang 'phrad par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK132(no)001:2375: sngar 'phrad pa'i rgyun dang 'bral ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:2376: de la grogs po ngan pa ni sdig pa'i grogs po nyon mongs pa 'phel bar byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2377: las ngan sdig pa la sbyor bar byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2378: tshul khrims dang thos bsam sgom gsum 'phel ba la bar du gcod pa'i byed pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2380: dgra gnyen la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i bya ba la sbyor ba'am /
NK132(no)001:2381: thar pa'i lam du rlom yang rung ste /
NK132(no)001:2382: lta ba dang spyod pa log pa la sbyor ba /
NK132(no)001:2383: de dag ni bla ma'am rje dpon nam /
NK132(no)001:2385: g.yog gam slob mar gyur pa yin yang te /
NK132(no)001:2386: mi dge ba'i bshes gnyen nam sdig pa'i grogs po dang /
NK132(no)001:2387: bdud kyi dpung gnyen zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)001:2389: sbrul gdug reg pa dug can ltar ring du spong dgos rgyu'o //
NK132(no)001:2390: de 'dra ba'i sdig grogs rang min yang /
NK132(no)001:2391: theg chen du zhugs pa dag theg dman du sbyor ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2392: zab pa dang rgya che la mos pa drang don
NK132(no)001:2393: gyi chos la sbyor ba sogs kyang grogs ngan no
NK132(no)001:2395: snang ba mtha' yas de yang des myur mthong /
NK132(no)001:2396: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa snang ba mtha'
NK132(no)001:2397: yas te 'od dpag tu med pa zhing khams bde
NK132(no)001:2398: ba can dang bcas pa yang /
NK132(no)001:2399: gson pa'i tshe la myur du mthong ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2400: sangs rgyas de las chos thos pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2401: shi nas kyang zhing khams der skye ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2402: phan yon bzhi pa ni smon lam 'di la brtson
NK132(no)001:2403: pa de dag chen po 'grub pa'i phyir rnyed pa
NK132(no)001:2405: 'bad rtsol med par chos dang ldan pa'i zas gos
NK132(no)001:2406: bsod snyoms la sogs pa rab tu rnyed pa ste
NK132(no)001:2409: bde bar 'tsho ba ste bde ba'i don ni legs pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:2410: des na tshe gang du legs par spyod pa /
NK132(no)001:2411: dge ba dang ma bral bas 'tsho ba'am /
NK132(no)001:2412: dgra dang gdon dang nad la sogs pa'i nyer 'tshe med pas bde bar 'tsho ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2414: mi tshe 'dir yang smon lam 'debs pa de dag /
NK132(no)001:2415: mir skyes pa don yod par 'gyur bas legs par 'ongs pa te /
NK132(no)001:2416: mi tshe don ldan du byung zhes pa'i don no //
NK132(no)001:2417: de yang 'dir dge ba 'phel bar 'gyur bas /
NK132(no)001:2418: skye ba shin tu mang por bde ba'i rgyu grub zin pa'i don no //
NK132(no)001:2419: yang na smon lam 'di 'debs pa de dag mi tshe 'dir yang tshe ring ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2421: 'khor dang nye du sogs rtsa 'jings rgyas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2424: snyan par grags pa sogs legs tshogs thams cad dang ldan par 'ongs te /
NK132(no)001:2425: 'ongs zhes pa 'byung 'gyur la byung ba'i sgras bstan pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2427: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa thob pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2428: phan yon drug po de tsam du ma zad 'phags
NK132(no)001:2429: pa kun tu bzang po yon tan dang rnam par
NK132(no)001:2431: mchod pa dang smon lam rgya mtsho la dbang 'byor pa de ci 'dra ba de 'dra bar yang /
NK132(no)001:2432: dus ring por mi thogs par smon lam 'debs pa
NK132(no)001:2433: de dag kun bzang nyid kyis ji ltar yon tan
NK132(no)001:2434: brnyes pa'i go rim dang mthun pa de bzhin du
NK132(no)001:2435: 'gyur ro // de la kun tu bzang po'i rnam par thar pa cung zad grub pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2436: sa dang po rab tu dga' ba nas yin la /
NK132(no)001:2437: phal cher grub pa ni sa brgyad pa nas dang /
NK132(no)001:2438: legs par grub pa ni sa bcu pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2439: phan yon brgyad pa ni las sgrib byad pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2440: mtshams med pa lnga po dag gi las kyi sgrib pa rnams las /
NK132(no)001:2441: gang yang rung ba zhig skyes bu gang gis sdig
NK132(no)001:2442: pa'i nyes dmigs mi shes pa'i dbang gis snga rol
NK132(no)001:2444: phyis de yis dad pa bskyed nas bzang po spyod pa 'di snying thag pa nas brjod na /
NK132(no)001:2445: de yi mtshams med kyi sdig pa de dag ma
NK132(no)001:2446: lus pa myur du yongs su byang bar 'gyur ba'o
NK132(no)001:2447: // mi dge ba'i las thams cad dug gsum gang rung gis 'phen cing sbyor ba yin la /
NK132(no)001:2448: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang gis 'phen cing sbyor ba rnams la'ang /
NK132(no)001:2449: gti mug gis 'phen pa sngon du 'gro dgos pas
NK132(no)001:2450: sdig pa thams cad mi shes pa'i dbang gis byas
NK132(no)001:2451: pa'o // byang chub tu sems bskyed cing dad pas smon lam 'di yang yang btab pas /
NK132(no)001:2452: mtshams med byas pa'ang tshe 'di la byang bar nus na /
NK132(no)001:2453: sdig pa phra mo rnams lta smos kyang ci dgos so //
NK132(no)001:2454: phan yon dgu pa ni ye shes phun sum tshogs pa thob pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2455: gong du bstan pa ltar khyad par bzhi ldan gyi bsngo ba 'dis yongs su bsngo ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2456: 'phags pa'i ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa thob pa'i rgyu drung po yin la /
NK132(no)001:2457: dang ni zhes pa gzugs sogs dang so sor 'byed pa'i tshig go //
NK132(no)001:2458: phan yon bcu pa ni lus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2459: yid kyi rang bzhin gyi lus kyi gzugs dang /
NK132(no)001:2460: de'i yon tan mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK132(no)001:2461: dpe byad brgyad cu ste mtshan gyi yon tan brgyad dang bcu gnyis la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK132(no)001:2462: 'gro ba drug tu skyes pa'i tshe yang /
NK132(no)001:2463: bram ze chen po dang rgyal rigs mchog la sogs pa /
NK132(no)001:2465: kha dog gi yon tan rnams dang ldan pa'i gzugs mdzes par 'gyur ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2467: rgya skad du war+na te rus la 'jug pas /
NK132(no)001:2469: 'od srung la sogs pa bram ze dang /
NK132(no)001:2471: nyi ma'i rigs la sogs pa rgyal rigs kyi rus te /
NK132(no)001:2472: rus che zhing khungs btsun pa rnams so //
NK132(no)001:2473: phan yon bcu gcig pa ni thub par dka' ba ste /
NK132(no)001:2474: bdud dang bdud kyi rigs kyi lha dang 'byung po rnams kyis glags lta bar mi nus shing /
NK132(no)001:2475: gang sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'di las phyi rol du gyur pa /
NK132(no)001:2476: lta ba ngan pa'i thibs po can de dag ni mu stegs byed de /
NK132(no)001:2477: de dag gi shes rab dang stobs kyis 'di thub par mi 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:2478: gzhan du na bdud dang mu stegs de dag rnams phar zin gyis gnon par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:2479: gzhung phal cher du bdud dang mu stegs mang pos de mi thub ces 'byung ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2480: 'grel pa rngog lo chen pos bsgyur ba ltar na /
NK132(no)001:2481: bdud dang mu stegs tshogs kyis de mi thub ces
NK132(no)001:2482: 'byung ba don la 'dra bas ji ltar bde bar
NK132(no)001:2483: spyar ro // phan yon bcu gnyis pa ni mchod 'os su 'gyur ba'i yon tan te /
NK132(no)001:2484: sa 'og dang sa steng dang nam mkha' la spyod
NK132(no)001:2485: pa'i 'jig rten gsum po kun na yang lha dang
NK132(no)001:2486: mi dang 'byung po rnams kyis smon lam 'di 'debs
NK132(no)001:2487: pa po de la dngos dang brgyud pa'i sgo nas
NK132(no)001:2489: gus pa dang phan 'dogs par 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:2490: phan yon bcu gsum pa ni mthar thug gi phan yon no //
NK132(no)001:2491: smon lam 'di 'debs par byed cing btab pa mthar phyin pa'i phan yon ni /
NK132(no)001:2492: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs nas bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par 'gyur ba ste /
NK132(no)001:2493: de ni byang chub kyi shing gi dbang po'i drung du myur du 'gro zhing /
NK132(no)001:2494: song nas sems can thams cad la phan pa'i phyir shing drung der 'dug ste /
NK132(no)001:2495: bdud kyi rgyal po rnams rang rang gi 'khor gyi sde dang bcas pa thams cad btul nas /
NK132(no)001:2496: byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te /
NK132(no)001:2497: chos kyi 'khor lo rab tu bskor bar 'gyur ro //
NK132(no)001:2498: de ltar na byang chub kyi snying por gshegs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2502: mdzad pa bzhi po dngos su bstan pas /
NK132(no)001:2503: mdzad pa mtha' yas pa thams cad kyang shugs la go ba'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2504: 'dir 'grel pa rnams kyi go rim 'di ltar du mdzad pa /
NK132(no)001:2505: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi rim pa dang mthun zhing /
NK132(no)001:2506: gzhung gi dkyus ltar na bdud btul ba'i mdzad pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2507: byang chub snying por bdud btul ba gcig pur ma zad /
NK132(no)001:2508: snga phyi thams cad du bdud kyi las yang dang yang du 'joms par mdzad pa nyid yin te /
NK132(no)001:2509: mdo sde nyi ma'i snying po dang /
NK132(no)001:2510: 'dus pa rin po che tog la sogs pa las 'byung ba lta bu ste /
NK132(no)001:2511: snga phyi thams cad du sbyor dgos pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2512: mjug tu smos pa yin pa /
NK132(no)001:2513: sangs rgyas gnyis pa lta bu'i lo ts+aa ba ye shes sdes kyang de bzhin du bshad do //
NK132(no)001:2514: byang chub kyi snying por gshegs pa la sogs pa 'di rnams /
NK132(no)001:2515: gtso bor gzugs kyi sku mchog gi sprul sku'i mdzad pa yin mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:2516: des de ltar ston pa la rgyu ni 'og min
NK132(no)001:2517: gyi gnas su longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i rnam 'phrul
NK132(no)001:2518: la yang de bzhin du 'char ba yin no //
NK132(no)001:2519: longs sku rtag tu bzhugs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2520: 'og min gyi gnas na bdud kyi 'jug pa med pas /
NK132(no)001:2521: yab yum gyi skye ba ston pa dang bdud 'dul
NK132(no)001:2522: ba sogs longs sku'i mdzad pa la mi 'grig go
NK132(no)001:2523: snyam pa ni shin tu blo chung ngu gnas 'di
NK132(no)001:2524: dag la mun par gyur pa'i gtam yin te /
NK132(no)001:2525: longs sku de'i ba spu'i khung bu gcig la yang /
NK132(no)001:2526: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa mtha' dag ston pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2527: de tsam gyis longs sku mya ngan las 'das par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK132(no)001:2528: de na bdud yod par thal ba yang ma yin no //
NK132(no)001:2529: de ltar na phan yon dang po gnyis dang /
NK132(no)001:2530: brgyad pa las sgrib byang ba ste /
NK132(no)001:2531: gsum po de ni mi mthun phyogs spangs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2534: drug pa legs par thob pa ste gsum po de ni /
NK132(no)001:2535: mthun rkyen 'byor pa'i phan yon te /
NK132(no)001:2537: las dang po pa nyid nas 'phral du 'byung ba rnams so //
NK132(no)001:2538: gzugs phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2540: gtso bor smon lam la brtson pa nas bzung ba'i skye ba gnyis pa phan chad du'o //
NK132(no)001:2542: 'di dang phyi ma gnyis kar na te /
NK132(no)001:2543: de'i phyogs gcig phar zil gyis mnan pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2545: bdun pa kun bzang gi spyod pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2546: bcu pa gzugs phun sum tshogs pa'i phyogs gcig yid kyi lus ni /
NK132(no)001:2547: sa thob pa'i dus kyi phan yon no //
NK132(no)001:2548: bcu gsum pa ni sangs rgyas thob pa'i dus kyi ste /
NK132(no)001:2549: phan yon bcu gsum po yang mthong ba'i chos la 'byung ba'i phan yon dang /
NK132(no)001:2550: tshe phyi ma so so skye ba'i gnas skabs kyi dang /
NK132(no)001:2552: mthar thug gi gnas skabs kyi phan yon te sde tshan bzhir 'dus pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:2554: gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam 'di //
NK132(no)001:2555: 'chang ba dang ni ston tam klog pa yi //
NK132(no)001:2556: de yi rnam par smin pa sangs rgyas mkhyen //
NK132(no)001:2557: byang chub mchog la som nyi ma byed cig /
NK132(no)001:2558: skyes bu gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam gyi rgyal po 'di'i /
NK132(no)001:2559: don dang tshig dang glegs bam gus pas 'chang ba dang kha ton du 'don pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2560: glegs bam klog par byed na yang rung te /
NK132(no)001:2561: de yi rnam par smin pa ste 'bras bu ni /
NK132(no)001:2562: mtha' yas shing bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK132(no)001:2563: ji lta ba bzhin du ni sangs rgyas kho nas mkhyen gyi /
NK132(no)001:2564: nyan thos dang rang rgyal gyi yang spyod yul ma yin na /
NK132(no)001:2565: so so skye bo rnams kyi lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK132(no)001:2567: byang chub kyi mchog bla na med par thob par 'gyur ba la /
NK132(no)001:2568: som nyi ma byed cig ste the tshom med pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2569: 'dir sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel pa la ni rgyu
NK132(no)001:2570: mthun pa'i 'bras bu mngon par mtho ba'i phun sum
NK132(no)001:2572: nyan rang sogs kyis bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2573: bsod nams kyi rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu byang chub mchog ces 'chad do //
NK132(no)001:2574: rtsa ba'i bzhi pa phan yon can gyi smon lam nyid bsngo ba la /
NK132(no)001:2575: sras byang sems kyis bsngosa pa la 'jug pa /
NK132(no)001:2576: rgyal bas bsngosa pa la 'jug pa /
NK132(no)001:2577: smon lam gyi 'bras bu mngon gyur du bsngo ba /
NK132(no)001:2578: dngos su lung bstan thob par bsngo ba /
NK132(no)001:2579: sems can la phan pa sgrub par bsngo ba ste lnga las /
NK132(no)001:2581: 'jam dpal ji ltar mkhyen cing dpa' ba ltar //
NK132(no)001:2582: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
NK132(no)001:2583: de dag kun gyi rjes su dag slob cing //
NK132(no)001:2584: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK132(no)001:2586: 'jam dpal ji ltar mkhyen cing dpa' ba ltar ces 'byung ba ltar na /
NK132(no)001:2587: 'di ltar 'jam dpal shes bya thams cad mkhyen cing 'gro ba'i don la dpa' ba ltar /
NK132(no)001:2588: de ltar kun tu bzang po yang ngo zhes par 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:2589: 'gyur 'di ltar la dpa' ba dang zer ba yig nor tsam mo //
NK132(no)001:2590: rgya 'grel rnams dang mkhan po ye shes sde'i 'grel pa las /
NK132(no)001:2591: 'jam dpal dpa' bos ji ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK132(no)001:2593: 'phags pa 'jam dpal bdud kyi sde 'joms pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2595: shes rab mchog gis dngos por 'dzin pa 'joms pa la /
NK132(no)001:2597: ji ltar bsngo ba thugs su chud cing mkhyen pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2598: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin du dpa' bo chen po yin la /
NK132(no)001:2599: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bsngo ba thugs su chud pa yang de bzhin te /
NK132(no)001:2600: byang chub sems dpa'i mchog de dag kun gyi rjes su ste /
NK132(no)001:2601: de dang 'dra bar bdag kyang slob par 'dod cing 'dod pa'i bsam pas /
NK132(no)001:2602: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam btab pa'i dge ba
NK132(no)001:2603: ji srid mchis pa 'di dag thams cad rab tu
NK132(no)001:2604: bsngo bar bagyi'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2605: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK132(no)001:2606: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu basngagasa pa des //
NK132(no)001:2607: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun kyang //
NK132(no)001:2608: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2609: dus gsum du sems can gyi don la byon cing
NK132(no)001:2610: gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis mchog tu basngagasa
NK132(no)001:2611: shing bstod pa'i bsngo ba'i rgyal po bzang zhing rgya
NK132(no)001:2612: che ba'i bsngo ba mtha' yas pa gang dang gang
NK132(no)001:2613: la / mchog tu basngagasa par mdzad pa'i bsngo ba de rnams kyis /
NK132(no)001:2614: bdag gis smon lam 'di btab pa la sogs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun kyang /
NK132(no)001:2615: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa thob pa'i phyir rab tu bsngo bar bagyi'o ste /
NK132(no)001:2616: de'i don ni bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di /
NK132(no)001:2617: sangs rgyas rnams kyi smon lam dang gcig tu 'dres te /
NK132(no)001:2618: dge rtsa 'dis smon lam de rnams 'grub par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:2619: de rnams kyis kyang 'di 'grub par gyur cig ces dang /
NK132(no)001:2620: smon lam de rnams kyi grub 'bras kyang kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2621: 'jam dpal dpa' bos zhes sogs tshigs bcad 'di gnyis ni /
NK132(no)001:2622: bsngo ba ma lus pa thams cad 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2623: bla na med pa'i bsngo ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2625: bdag ni 'chi ba'i dus byed gyur pa na //
NK132(no)001:2626: sgrib pa thams cad dag ni phyir bsal te //
NK132(no)001:2627: mngon sum snang ba mtha' yas de mthong nas //
NK132(no)001:2628: bde ba can gyi zhing der rab tu 'gro //
NK132(no)001:2629: der song nas ni smon lam 'di dag kyang //
NK132(no)001:2630: thams cad ma lus mngon du 'gyur bar shog /
NK132(no)001:2631: de ltar ma lus bdag gis yongs su bkang //
NK132(no)001:2632: 'jig rten ji srid sems can phan par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2633: bdag ni nam zhig 'chi ba'i dus byed par gyur ba na /
NK132(no)001:2634: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa thams cad dag ni phyir bsal zhing med par byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2635: sgrib pa spyi dang khyad par du 'gyod pa la sogs pa'i sgrib pa lnga po dang /
NK132(no)001:2636: sangs rgyas mngon sum du mthong ba la bar du gcod pa'i sgrib pa rnams byang ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2637: de nas sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas de mngon du mthong bar 'gyur ba la /
NK132(no)001:2638: de mthong bas kyang slar yang sgrib pa mang po zhig ni dag /
NK132(no)001:2639: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo du ma thob nas /
NK132(no)001:2640: gnad gcod la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal med cing /
NK132(no)001:2641: 'chi ba'i sems de yang rab tu rnam par dkar
NK132(no)001:2642: ba'i ting nge 'dzin du ma dang bcas par 'gyur
NK132(no)001:2643: zhing / de song ma thag tu gzhan 'phrul dbang
NK132(no)001:2644: byed kyi lha'i rgyal po'i lus dang mtshungs pa'i bar
NK132(no)001:2646: skad cig thang cig yud tsam de la bde ba can gyi zhing khams der rab tu 'gro zhing /
NK132(no)001:2647: der song nas ni rin po che'i pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru'i khang par bardzusa te skye ba blang nas /
NK132(no)001:2648: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam btab pa 'di rnams
NK132(no)001:2649: kyi 'bras bu de dag kyang thams cad ma lus
NK132(no)001:2650: pa mngon du 'gyura zhing 'grub par shog la /
NK132(no)001:2651: de ltar bdag gi smon lam gyi 'bras bu de
NK132(no)001:2652: dag ma lus pa rang rgyud la dgos pa rnams
NK132(no)001:2653: kyang yongs su bskang zhing rdzogs la /
NK132(no)001:2654: sems can gzhan rnams kyi don du dgos pa kun yang /
NK132(no)001:2655: yongs su rdzogs shing re ba bskang bar byas nas /
NK132(no)001:2656: 'jig rten ji srid ma stong pa de srid du /
NK132(no)001:2657: sems can rnams la phan pa mtha' yas pa rtag tu bgyid par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:2659: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor bzang zhing dga' ba der //
NK132(no)001:2660: pad+mo dam pa shin tu mdzes las skyes //
NK132(no)001:2661: snang ba mtha' yas rgyal bas mngon sum du //
NK132(no)001:2662: lung bstan pa yang dag gis der thob shog /
NK132(no)001:2663: rgyal ba 'od dpag tu med pa'i zhing khams phun
NK132(no)001:2664: sum tshogs pa der spyod pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor
NK132(no)001:2665: bde zhing skyid pas bzang zhing dga' ba'am /
NK132(no)001:2666: yang na gzugs bzang zhing yid yon tan gyis dga' bar gyur pa zhes 'chad pa ltar ram /
NK132(no)001:2667: yon tan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan cing /
NK132(no)001:2668: gnas ngan len gyi spyod pa spangs pas bzang ba /
NK132(no)001:2669: nang du ting nge 'dzin gyi dga' ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2670: phyi rol tu smon lam gyi stobs las grub pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2671: gnas dang yo byad dang 'dod pa'i yon tan thams
NK132(no)001:2672: cad kyis dga' bar gyur pa rnams kyi dbus der
NK132(no)001:2673: / pad+mo dam pa rin po che'i pad+mo shin tu mdzes pa las /
NK132(no)001:2674: bardzusa te skyes nas byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa
NK132(no)001:2675: spyod pa'i tshe rgyal ba snang ba mtha' yas kyis
NK132(no)001:2676: mngon sum du khyod 'jig rten gyi khams 'di zhes
