NK132(no)001:2677: bya bar bskal pa 'di zhes bya ba la /
NK132(no)001:2678: sangs rgyas 'di lta bur 'gyur ro zhes lung ston pa yang bdag gis /
NK132(no)001:2679: dus de skabs su dang gnas dang grogs kyi khyad
NK132(no)001:2680: par 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor der thob par shog cig
NK132(no)001:2682: der ni bdag gi lung bstan rab thob nas //
NK132(no)001:2683: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya yis //
NK132(no)001:2684: blo yi stobs kyis phyogs bcu rnams su yang //
NK132(no)001:2685: sems can rnams la phan pa mang po bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2686: bde ba can gyi zhing der ni smon lam 'debs pa po bdag gis /
NK132(no)001:2687: lung bstan de lta bu rab tu thob nas /
NK132(no)001:2688: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya la sogs pa mtha' las 'das pa yis /
NK132(no)001:2689: gzhan don gcig tu gzhol ba'i blo'i stobs kyis phyogs
NK132(no)001:2690: bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus pa rnams su
NK132(no)001:2691: yang / skad cig re re yang sems can mtha' yas pa rnams la /
NK132(no)001:2692: ngan song gi sdug bsngal las skyob pa nas brtsams te /
NK132(no)001:2695: bla na med pa'i byang chub la 'god pa'i bar gyi /
NK132(no)001:2696: phan pa mang po ji srid 'khor ram stong gi
NK132(no)001:2697: bar du bgyid pa ste sgrub par shog ces pa'o
NK132(no)001:2698: // sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK132(no)001:2699: sprul pa bye ba phrag brgya du ma yis //
NK132(no)001:2701: der song nas ni zhes pa'i sho lo ka gcig po de /
NK132(no)001:2702: phan pa mang po bgyid ces pa'i rjes 'dir 'don par snang ngo //
NK132(no)001:2703: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam btab pa yi sogs /
NK132(no)001:2704: sho lo ka gnyis ni sdong po bkod pa'i mdo
NK132(no)001:2705: dngos bod du yod pa 'di las mi 'byung zhing
NK132(no)001:2706: / rgya 'grel gzhan rnams na yang bshad pa med do //
NK132(no)001:2707: sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel par ni 'byung zhing /
NK132(no)001:2708: bzang spyod kyi glegs bam logs su byas pa'i rgya dpe gcig na yang snang ngo //
NK132(no)001:2709: mkhan po ye shes sdes kyang bshad pa mdzad pas /
NK132(no)001:2710: spyir mdo sde'i tshig ni yin par bya dgos so //
NK132(no)001:2711: des na 'di sngar gyi sa bcad lnga po la mi the yang /
NK132(no)001:2712: gzhan don kho nar yongs su bsngo ba zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)001:2714: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam bton pa yi //
NK132(no)001:2715: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
NK132(no)001:2716: des na 'gro ba'i smon lam dge ba rnams //
NK132(no)001:2717: skad cig gcig gis thams cad 'byor bar shog /
NK132(no)001:2718: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam glegs bam bklags pa dang kha ton du byas pa ni bton pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2719: de las bdag gis dge ba cung zad ci bsags pa des ni /
NK132(no)001:2720: 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi yid la smon cing /
NK132(no)001:2721: ngag gi gyur cig par brjod pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2722: smon lam gyi rigs las dge bar gtogs pa rnams thams cad 'bad rtsol med cing /
NK132(no)001:2723: yun ring du thogs pa ma yin par /
NK132(no)001:2724: skad gcig gis te myur du thams cad 'byor zhing 'grub par shog cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2725: 'dis ni bdag nyid kyi bzang spyod bton pa'i dge
NK132(no)001:2726: bas sems can thams cad kyi bzang smon 'grub par
NK132(no)001:2728: gzhan don kho nar bsngo ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2730: gang yang bzang po spyod pa 'di bsngosa pas //
NK132(no)001:2731: bsod nams mtha' yas dam pa gang thob des //
NK132(no)001:2732: 'gro ba sdug bsngal chu bor bying ba rnams //
NK132(no)001:2733: 'od dpag med pa'i gnas rab thob par shog /
NK132(no)001:2735: bzang spyod yongs su bsngosa pa'i bsod nams ni /
NK132(no)001:2736: mtha' yas shin tu khyad 'phags gang thob des //
NK132(no)001:2738: bzang po spyod pa'i bsngo ba byas pa 'di yis /
NK132(no)001:2739: gang yang bdag gi rgyud la bsod nams te dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya che bas mtha' yas shing /
NK132(no)001:2740: ngo bo bzang bas dam par gyur pa gang zhig thob pa des /
NK132(no)001:2741: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can skye rga na
NK132(no)001:2742: 'chi la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal gyi chu bor bying
NK132(no)001:2743: ba rnams / bcom ldan 'das 'od dpag med pa'i
NK132(no)001:2744: gnas bde ba can gyi zhing khams sdug bsngal gyi
NK132(no)001:2746: rtag tu bde ba'i gnas de rab tu thob par shog cig pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2747: der skye bar gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2748: bzang po spyod pa'i gzhug 'di la /
NK132(no)001:2749: sngon bstan pa snga 'gyur gyi dus su /
NK132(no)001:2750: lo pan sprul pa'i skyes mchog rnams kyis bsgyur ba la /
NK132(no)001:2751: slob dpon chen po dpal phyogs kyi glang po dang /
NK132(no)001:2755: bzhi po des mdzad pa'i 'grel ba dag 'gyur la /
NK132(no)001:2756: de rnams kyi don legs bsdus kyi steng du /
NK132(no)001:2757: mkhas pa'i gsung dang mdo don 'ga' zhig gis brgyan pa /
NK132(no)001:2758: mkhan po ye shes sdes rjed byang gi 'grel chen mdzad do //
NK132(no)001:2759: slob dpon chen po dbyig gnyen gyis mdzad zer ba'i 'grel pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2760: rngog 'gyur glu sgrub kyis mdzad zer ba'i 'grel pa de gnyis rgyan bzang po'i 'grel pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2762: dpe thog ma dbang btsan par byas te rgyan bzang po'i yin gyi /
NK132(no)001:2763: slob dpon chen po de gnyis kyi min no //
NK132(no)001:2764: rgyan bzang po 'grel pa 'di yang phyogs glang gi 'grel pa'i bsdus don bor zhing /
NK132(no)001:2765: mgo zhabs su tshigs bcad bsnan pa tsam ma gtogs lhag ma rnams bris bshus lta bu snang ngo //
NK132(no)001:2766: sangs rgyas grags pa'i 'grel pa ni ma mthong la
NK132(no)001:2767: 'dir phyogs glang dang sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel pa'i
NK132(no)001:2768: don gyi snying po gal che ba rnams tshang bar
NK132(no)001:2769: byas la / phal cher ye shes sde'i gsung gi yang rjes su 'brangs shing /
NK132(no)001:2770: rang blos rtogs pa'i legs bshad cung zad kyis kyang brgyan te bshad pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:2771: de ltar na sdong po bkod pa nyid las 'byung ba dang /
NK132(no)001:2773: sh+lo ka drug cu yin la /
NK132(no)001:2774: sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi 'grel pa ltar na phyi ma gnyis po bsnan pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2775: 'di nyid kyi sgos kyi glegs bam bod ma phal cher gyi mjug tu /
NK132(no)001:2776: smon lam rgyal po 'di dag mchog gi gtso //
NK132(no)001:2777: mtha' yas 'gro ba kun la phan byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2778: kun tu bzang pos brgyan pa'i zhing grub ste //
NK132(no)001:2779: ngan song gnas rnams ma lus stong bar shog /
NK132(no)001:2782: sngar smos pa bdag gis mthong ba'i 'grel ba rnams na mi snang zhing /
NK132(no)001:2783: sangs rgyas grags pa'i 'grel pa na yang med par grags la /
NK132(no)001:2784: pa gor bee ro tsa na rak+shi ta la sogs
NK132(no)001:2785: pa 'di'i gzhung 'grel rnams 'gyur mdzad pa'i lo ts+aa
NK132(no)001:2786: ba dag gis / 'gyur gyi smon lam gyi tshul du mdzad pa yin no zhes grags ste /
NK132(no)001:2787: de ltar yin pa yang sems la /
NK132(no)001:2788: de na ni bzang po zhig ste /
NK132(no)001:2789: smon lam gyi rgyal po 'di dag ni /
NK132(no)001:2790: mchog gi gtso bo sangs rgyas su 'grub cing /
NK132(no)001:2791: mtha' yas pa'i 'gro ba kun la phan pa byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2792: khyad par du phyogs bcu'i zhing khams ma lus pa'i
NK132(no)001:2793: ngan song gi gnas thams cad ma lus par stong
NK132(no)001:2794: pa dang / phyogs thams cad kun tu bzang po'i smon lam gyis brgyan pa'i /
NK132(no)001:2795: zhing khams khyad par can du bsgrubs pas grub par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2796: de ltar na tshigs bcad tha ma de gsum ni /
NK132(no)001:2797: sdong po bkod pa nyid las mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:2798: ma bton yang chad pa'i nyes pa med par shes par bya'o //
NK132(no)001:2800: zab cing rgya che'i smon lam dam pa 'di //
NK132(no)001:2801: bdag lta rmongs po'i spyod yul ma yin mod //
NK132(no)001:2802: rang gi blo gros rnam par sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)001:2803: dam pa'i gsung gi rjes zhugs skyon med snyam //
NK132(no)001:2804: stong pa nyid dang snying rje'i rang snang las //
NK132(no)001:2805: ting 'dzin spyod yul dam pa'i 'jig rten dang //
NK132(no)001:2806: yid kyi lus dang bsam mi khyab pa yi //
NK132(no)001:2807: skye dang 'chi 'pho rnam 'phrul mtha' yas pa //
NK132(no)001:2808: de ni rgyal dang sems dpa' che rnams kyi //
NK132(no)001:2809: spyod yul nyid yin gzhan gyi ma lags mod //
NK132(no)001:2810: smon lam 'dis ni de don rdzogs par ston //
NK132(no)001:2811: de phyir 'phags pa'i spyod yul nyag gcig go //
NK132(no)001:2812: zhes pa ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2813: de la byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa gang yin pa de yang /
NK132(no)001:2814: skyes bu chen po'i rnam par rtog pa brgyad du 'dus pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:2815: rnam pa brgyad po de la ni byang chub sems
NK132(no)001:2816: dpa' rnams nyin dang mtshan du mngon par phyogs par
NK132(no)001:2817: byed do // de la sdom ni /
NK132(no)001:2818: sdug bsngal sel dang 'byor pa dang //
NK132(no)001:2822: brgyad pa bdag gzhan rje ba yin //
NK132(no)001:2824: bdag gis sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal nam zhig sel bar 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2826: sems can dbul po rnams 'byor pa chen po la bdag gis nam sbyor bar 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2828: sha khrag dang bcas pa'i lus 'dis sems can gyi don nam byed snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2831: sems can rnams la nam zhig phan 'dogs par 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2833: bdag gis 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'byor pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2834: rdzu 'phrul dang longs spyod dang yon tan dang yon
NK132(no)001:2835: tan rnams kyis sems can gyi re ba rdzogs par
NK132(no)001:2838: bdag sangs rgyas su gyur nas sems can 'khor ba las nam zhig drangs par 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2840: sems can la phan pa rgya chen po mi 'byung
NK132(no)001:2841: na skye ba dang spyod pa dang longs spyod ches
NK132(no)001:2842: phun sum tshogs pa zhig yin yang rung nam yang
NK132(no)001:2843: mi 'dod cing skra rtse bskyod pa tsam dang dbug
NK132(no)001:2845: sems can la phan pa kho na byed nus par nam zhig 'gyur snyam pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2846: brgyad pa ni sems can gyi sdig pa dang sdug bsngal bdag la smin par gyur cig /
NK132(no)001:2847: bdag gi bde ba dang dge ba sems can la 'byung bar gyur cig ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2848: byang chub sems dpa' rnams smon lam 'debs pa'i rtsa
NK132(no)001:2849: ba bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa ni de dag
NK132(no)001:2850: yin te / de la smon lam dngos ni /
NK132(no)001:2851: ngag nas brjod pa la mi bya ste yid kyis so //
NK132(no)001:2853: brtan pa rnams kyi smon lam ni //
NK132(no)001:2854: sems pa bdun dang bcas pa ste //
NK132(no)001:2856: skabs 'dir yang smon lam bya ba'i gnas brgyad po de la /
NK132(no)001:2857: rtag tu sems par byed cing /
NK132(no)001:2858: thob par 'dun pa ni smon lam dngos so //
NK132(no)001:2860: gzhung 'dis gsal bar bstan pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:2861: skyes bu chen po'i rnam rtog dang po sems can
NK132(no)001:2862: rnams sdug bsngal med cing bde bar 'dod pa ni
NK132(no)001:2863: / phyogs bcu'i sems can gang rnams ji snyed pa //
NK132(no)001:2864: de dag rtag tu nad med bde bar 'gyur //
NK132(no)001:2866: gnyis pa 'byor pa thob par 'dod pa ni //
NK132(no)001:2867: zhing sbyong ba dang mchod pa'i tshigs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:2868: de yi bya ba ma lus rdzogs par bgyi ces pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2869: gsum pa rang lus kyis sems can la phan 'dogs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2870: lus dang ngag dang yid kyang rnam dag ste //
NK132(no)001:2871: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2872: sgo gsum gzhan don du spyod na rnam par dag par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2873: bzhi pa ngan 'gror zhugs nas kyang gzhan don byed pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2874: sems can dag gi spyod dang mthun par 'jug /
NK132(no)001:2876: lnga pa sems can gyi re ba skong ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2877: 'gro ba kun gyi chos kyi don rnams ni //
NK132(no)001:2879: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos ston to //
NK132(no)001:2881: drug pa sangs rgyas thob nas 'gro ba sgrol ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2882: byang chub shing dbang drung du de myur 'gro sogs dang /
NK132(no)001:2883: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya yis //
NK132(no)001:2885: bdun pa don dam du 'gyur ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2886: gang yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yi //
NK132(no)001:2888: gzhan yang shugs bstan la mang ngo //
NK132(no)001:2889: brgyad pa bdag gzhan rje ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2890: zhing gi khyon dang phyogs rnams ji tsam par //
NK132(no)001:2891: ngan song sdug bsngal rab tu zhi bar byed //
NK132(no)001:2892: bde ba dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing //
NK132(no)001:2893: sems can thams cad la ni phan par bgyid //
NK132(no)001:2895: yang byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa rnams kyi smon lam grangs med pa 'bum phrag bcu ni /
NK132(no)001:2896: smon lam chen po bcur 'dus pa yin la /
NK132(no)001:2897: de dag kyang 'phags pa sa bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)001:2898: sa dang po'i don bsdu tshigs bcad kyi skabs su 'di skad ces 'byung ste /
NK132(no)001:2899: rgyal ba lta ba'i don du smon lam mngon par sgrub //
NK132(no)001:2900: dam chos yongs su bzung zhing drang srong drung 'gro dang //
NK132(no)001:2901: sbyong ba mchog gi don du smon lam mngon par sgrub //
NK132(no)001:2902: sems can yongs su smin bya sangs rgyas zhing spyong ste //
NK132(no)001:2903: de yi zhing mchog rgyal sras kun gyis gang gyur zhing //
NK132(no)001:2904: rgyal sras rnams dang bsam pa gcig cing don mthun phyir //
NK132(no)001:2905: skra sbubs kun du don gyi dam pa mngon 'tshang rgya //
NK132(no)001:2906: de dag smon lam du ma mngon par sgrub par byed //
NK132(no)001:2907: de dag mtha' yas yangs shing mthar thug med dang ldan //
NK132(no)001:2908: nam mkha'i khams dang chos nyid mya ngan 'das mkhas dang //
NK132(no)001:2909: 'jig rten mthar thug rgyal ba 'byung dang ye shes dang //
NK132(no)001:2910: sems kyis yul dang ye shes 'jug pa'i mthar thug dang //
NK132(no)001:2911: rnam gsum rgyud rnams mthar thug 'gro ba'i mur thug pa //
NK132(no)001:2912: rnam pa re tshul bdag smon mtha' yas thug gyur cing //
NK132(no)001:2913: de dag mthar thug ji bzhin bdag sbyod de 'drar shog /
NK132(no)001:2915: de la smon lam chen po bcu'i sdoms ni /
NK132(no)001:2916: mchod dang dam chos yongs su bzung //
NK132(no)001:2917: kun 'gro'i lus dang spyod pa dang //
NK132(no)001:2918: yongs su smin dang zhing spyong dang //
NK132(no)001:2919: sbyangs pa'i zhing de'i khyad par sgrub //
NK132(no)001:2920: rgyal sras kun dang mthun par spyod //
NK132(no)001:2922: de ltar smon lam bcu po la //
NK132(no)001:2923: mthar thug gnas kyang rnam bcu ste //
NK132(no)001:2924: sems can 'jig rten nam mkha' dang //
NK132(no)001:2926: ye shes khams dang sems kyi dmigs //
NK132(no)001:2927: ye shes mngon sgrub khams mthar thug /
NK132(no)001:2928: rgyud gsum khams par smon lam 'debs //
NK132(no)001:2929: 'jig rten chos dang ye shes kyi //
NK132(no)001:2930: rgyud de skabs 'dir rgyud gsum mo //
NK132(no)001:2931: smon lam chen po bcu ni /
NK132(no)001:2932: sangs rgyas thams cad la mchod pa thams cad kyis mchod par smon pa ni dang po'o //
NK132(no)001:2933: dam pa'i chos thams cad yongs su bzung zhing bsrung bar smon pa ni gnyis pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2934: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams mdzad pa ngo mtshar can
NK132(no)001:2935: mdzad pa thams cad kyi drung du thogs pa med
NK132(no)001:2936: pa'i lus kyis bdag 'gro zhing bya ba khyad par
NK132(no)001:2937: can byed par smon pa ni gsum pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2938: rtag tu byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa thams cad spyod par smon pa ni bzhi pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2939: bdag gis sems can thams cad yongs su smin par byed par smon pa ni lnga pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2940: 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ba'i zhing 'jig rten gyi khams
NK132(no)001:2941: mtha' yas pa grub par smon pa ni drug pa'o
NK132(no)001:2942: // mngon par sgrub pa'i zhing khams rnams kyang mtha'
NK132(no)001:2943: yas pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i spyod yul can
NK132(no)001:2944: // las / byang chub sems dpa' mchog gis gang
NK132(no)001:2945: ba sogs dag pa rab 'byams 'ba' zhig tu sbyong
NK132(no)001:2946: bar smon pa ni bdun pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2947: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang bdag nyid bsam sbyor gcig par smon pa ni brgyad pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2948: spyod pa dang nyams len thams cad don gyi mchog
NK132(no)001:2949: kho na mtha' yas pa 'grub par smon pa ni
NK132(no)001:2950: dgu pa'o // nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa thams cad
NK132(no)001:2951: du mdzad pa mtha' yas pa ston pa'i tshul gyis
NK132(no)001:2952: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par smon pa ni
NK132(no)001:2953: dgu pa'o // bcu pa'o // de las dang po mchod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2954: bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'i ched dang gnyis pa dam chos yongs su bzung ba ni /
NK132(no)001:2955: ye shes kyi tshogs kyi ched du'o //
NK132(no)001:2956: gsum pa la sogs pa lnga ni sems can yongs su smin pa'i ched du yin te /
NK132(no)001:2957: gsum pa kun tu 'gro ba'i lus ni /
NK132(no)001:2958: rten lus kyi khyad par ci 'dra bas dang /
NK132(no)001:2959: bzhi pa spyod pa mtha' dag la slob pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2960: sems la sogs pa'i spyod pa ci 'dra bas gzhan smin par byed pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2961: lnga pa ni smin par byed pa dngos te /
NK132(no)001:2962: gang smin par bya ba'i sems can gyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2964: gnas gang du smin par byed pa'i zhing khams sgrub pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2965: bdun pa ni rnam pa ji lta bus smin par 'gyur ba'i thabs ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2966: brgyad pa sems dpa' kun dang mthun par spyod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2967: rang gi sa'i yon tan gyi khyad par rtogs pa'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)001:2968: dgu pa don yod par spyod pa ni /
NK132(no)001:2969: khyad par rtogs pa gong nas gong du 'gro ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)001:2970: bcu pa byang chub kyi smon lam ni 'bras bu mthar thug gi phyir ro //
NK132(no)001:2971: de lta bu'i smon lam bcu po de yang /
NK132(no)001:2972: bzang po spyod pa 'di la yongs su rdzogs par tshang ba yin te /
NK132(no)001:2973: 'jig rten du dag ni gang bzhugs mchod par gyur ces dang /
NK132(no)001:2974: de dag la yang mchod pa rgya cher bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2975: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho rab tu mchod byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2976: ces pa la sogs pas dang po'i dbang du byas te sangs rgyas mchod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2977: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK132(no)001:2979: byang chub spyod pa dag ni bdag spyod cing //
NK132(no)001:2980: ces rang gis spyod pa dang /
NK132(no)001:2981: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK132(no)001:2982: ces gzhan la ston pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2983: de sogs mang po zhig ni gnyis pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2985: byang chub spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
NK132(no)001:2987: rtag tu de dag gi ni spyod yul la //
NK132(no)001:2988: sgyu mar gyur pa'i rnam thar stobs kyis 'jug /
NK132(no)001:2989: ces pa la sogs pas ni gsum pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2990: kun tu 'gro ba'i lus kyis sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul lta ba'o //
NK132(no)001:2991: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyang ba yang //
NK132(no)001:2992: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyad par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:2993: ces sogs mang po zhig ni /
NK132(no)001:2994: bzhi pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:2995: spyod pa thams cad la bslab pa'o //
NK132(no)001:2996: bde ba dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing //
NK132(no)001:2998: sems can rgya mtsho dag ni rnam par grol //
NK132(no)001:2999: ces pa la sogs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:3000: lnga pa dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3001: sems can yongs su smin pa byed pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3002: de ltar ma lus phyogs rnams thams cad du //
NK132(no)001:3003: rgyal ba dag gi zhing rnams bkod la 'jug /
NK132(no)001:3004: ces pa la sogs pa drug pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3005: zhing mtha' yas pa sgrub pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3006: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te //
NK132(no)001:3007: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
NK132(no)001:3009: mya ngan 'das pa rab tu zhi mtha' ston //
NK132(no)001:3011: zhing rnams rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
NK132(no)001:3013: bdun pa'i dbang du byas pa ste //
NK132(no)001:3014: zhing khams rnam par dag par spyod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3015: gang yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yis //
NK132(no)001:3016: byang chub spyod pa'i smon lam bye brag rnams //
NK132(no)001:3018: lus dang bag dang yid kyang rnam dag cing //
NK132(no)001:3020: de dag 'phrul pa thams cad 'tshal bar bgyi //
NK132(no)001:3022: bdag gi spyod dang mtshungs pa gang spyod pa //
NK132(no)001:3023: zhes sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang /
NK132(no)001:3024: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge gang //
NK132(no)001:3025: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK132(no)001:3026: tshe rabs kun tu 'chi 'pho skye ba dang //
NK132(no)001:3027: ces pa la sogs pa ni brgyad pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3028: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang spyod pa mthun par spyod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3029: kun tu yon tan spyod pa'i stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:3031: spyod pa rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
NK132(no)001:3033: yon tan rnams kyang tshad bzung med par shog /
NK132(no)001:3035: de yi bya ba ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
NK132(no)001:3036: zhes pa la sogs pa mang po dag ni dgu pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3037: 'bras bu don yod pa kho nar spyod pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3038: bzang po spyod pas byang chub sangs rgyas nas //
NK132(no)001:3040: skra tsam khyon la dus gsum tshad snyed kyi sogs dang //
NK132(no)001:3041: yon tan kun gyi mi zad mdzod du gyur ces pa dang /
NK132(no)001:3042: kun tu myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs rnams dang //
NK132(no)001:3044: chags pa med par gyur pa'i ye shes stobs //
NK132(no)001:3045: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK132(no)001:3046: bcu pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3047: nam mkha'i mthas gtugs par mdzad pa mtha' yas par ston pa'i sangs rgyas su smon pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3048: smon lam de rnams kyi mthar thug pa'i gnas bcu la /
NK132(no)001:3049: sems can gyi khams kyi mthar thug pa ni /
NK132(no)001:3050: sems can ji tsam yod pa'i sa phyogs su smon lam gyis khyab cing /
NK132(no)001:3051: ma 'ongs pa na sems can ma zad kyi bar
NK132(no)001:3052: du smon lam gyi 'bras bu yang mi zad pa'o
NK132(no)001:3057: 'jig rten dang nam mkhas khyab tshad kyi yul dang /
NK132(no)001:3058: de gnyis ji srid yod pa'i bar gyi dus de dag tu smon lam mi zad pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3059: gzhan rnams la'ang mthar thug tshul de kho na bzhin yin la /
NK132(no)001:3060: chos kyi dbyings dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i khams dang /
NK132(no)001:3061: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi khams rnams ngo bo gcig ste /
NK132(no)001:3062: ngo bo chos dbyings sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po yin la /
NK132(no)001:3063: 'on kyang 'dul ba'i don du chos ston pa'i gzhi yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:3065: mthar thug sems can gang du 'dul ba'i gnas yin pa'i phyir mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK132(no)001:3066: de bzhin nyid dang rnam pa mthun par sgom pa'i chos kyi dmigs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:3067: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi khams zhes bstan pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:3069: ye shes mngon par sgrub pa'i khams kyang don gcig ste /
NK132(no)001:3070: ngo bo ni lam gyi bden pa yin te /
NK132(no)001:3073: ngo bo'i dbang du byas nas ye shes mngon par sgrub pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3074: sems kyi dmigs pa'i khams ni shes bya thams cad do //
NK132(no)001:3075: rgyud gsum la 'jig rten gyi rgyud ni /
NK132(no)001:3077: chos kyi rgyud ni 'gog pa'i bden pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3078: ye shes kyi rgyud ni lam gyi bden pa ste /
NK132(no)001:3079: de dag ji srid yod kyi bar du /
NK132(no)001:3080: smon lam 'di'i 'bras bu yod par gyur cig pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3081: de ltar na smon lam bcu po yang /
NK132(no)001:3082: mthar thug pa'i gnas rnam pa bcu'i sgo nas 'debs dgos pa las /
NK132(no)001:3083: de yang nam mkha'i mthar thug gyur pa ji tsam par /
NK132(no)001:3084: sems can ma lus mtha' yang de bzhin te /
NK132(no)001:3085: ji tsam las dang nyon mongs mthar gyur pa /
NK132(no)001:3086: bdag gi smon lam mtha' yang de tsam mo //
NK132(no)001:3087: zhes gsungs pa'i don la 'dus pa yin no //
NK132(no)001:3088: smon lam bcu po 'di dag rgyas par 'phags pa sa bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK132(no)001:3089: sa dang po'i rgyas bshad kyi skabs na yod la /
NK132(no)001:3090: zhib mor shes 'dod na mdo de nyid dang /
NK132(no)001:3091: rgyal sras chen po 'phags pa dbyig gnyen gyi 'brel pa dang bcas pa las rtog par bya la /
NK132(no)001:3092: rgyas bshad kyi mdo'i tshig dang /
NK132(no)001:3093: 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam gyi tshig phal cher zhib tu sbyor rgyu yod mod kyi /
NK132(no)001:3094: 'dir ni ha cang mang par gyur gyi dogs pas ma bkod do //
NK132(no)001:3095: phyis byung ba mkhas par rloms pa kha cig gis /
NK132(no)001:3096: smon lam chen po bcu'i tshigs bcad sbyar ba mthong ste /
NK132(no)001:3097: des ni mdo rtsa 'grel ma mthong zhing /
NK132(no)001:3098: bzang spyod kyi don la sbyor tshul yang ma go bas /
NK132(no)001:3099: ming tsam las don ma rtogs pa'i bzhad gad kyi gnas kyang snang ngo //
NK132(no)001:3100: de bas na rgyal sras kyi smon lam thams cad
NK132(no)001:3101: smon lam chen po grangs med pa 'bum phrag bcur
NK132(no)001:3102: 'dus la / de yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam 'dus par shes nas /
NK132(no)001:3103: rtag tu 'di nyid khyad par bzhi dang ldan pas
NK132(no)001:3104: kha ton du byed pa la brtson par bya ste
NK132(no)001:3105: / theg pa chen po la rnal 'byor du byed pa rnams kyis so //
NK132(no)001:3106: 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa smon lam gyi rgyal po'i rgya cher 'grel pa /
NK132(no)001:3107: 'phags mchog rnams kyi gsang ba'i mdzod ces bya ba /
NK132(no)001:3108: rgyal khams pa t+aa ra n+aa thas nags rgyal gyi dben gnas jo nang du smras pa'o //
NK132(no)001:3109: las dang po pa la phan pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)001:3110: phyag rgya lnga yi mdo rnams la //
NK132(no)001:3111: rnam bshad shin tu go bla zhing //
NK132(no)001:3112: zab mo'i don dang ldan par sbyar //
NK132(no)001:3113: 'di las dge ba gang thob des //
NK132(no)001:3114: 'gro ba kun gyis chos kyi sku //
NK132(no)001:3115: mtha' yas snying po de thob nas //
NK132(no)001:3116: ye shes rgya mtshor ro gcig gyur //
NK132(no)001:3117: theg chen shin tu rgyas pa'i smon lam mdo'i //
NK132(no)001:3118: dgongs 'grel chos sbyin mdzad med 'jo ba'i par //
NK132(no)001:3119: dbon sprul karma bstan 'dzin rab rgyas kyis //
NK132(no)001:3120: thub bstan chos 'khor gling gi gdan sar bsgrubs //
NK132(no)001:3122: chos kyi 'phrul par bzhengs pa'i dge ba yis //
NK132(no)001:3123: 'gro kun tshe 'dir bde skyid dpal la rol //
NK132(no)001:3124: 'chi khar nad gcod sdug bsngal mi myong zhing //
NK132(no)001:3125: phyi ma dag pa'i zhing du 'tshang rgya shog /
NK132(no)001:3126: rgyal ba'i bka' bsdu rigs gsum sems dpa' mchog /
NK132(no)001:3127: mchog tu zab pa nang rgyud sde gsum lugs //
NK132(no)001:3128: lugs mthun sgrub nus kun bzang sar phyin par //
NK132(no)001:3129: par gzhi sgrig po byang chub rgya mtshos smon //
NK132(no)001:3130: zhes snga 'gyur bka' ma'i gzhung phyi mo dang rgyab
NK132(no)001:3131: chos mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs te rtsis 'phrul
NK132(no)001:3132: gyi par gzhi bzhengs skabs nges pa don gyi rdzogs
NK132(no)001:3133: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa mkhan chen bla ma
NK132(no)001:3134: mun sel gyi gus slob tha ma'i yang tha chos
NK132(no)001:3135: rdzogs chen du song yang gang zag rdzogs chen du
NK132(no)001:3136: ma song bas / rang rgyud tha mal du lus
NK132(no)001:3137: pa'i snyom las pa byang chub rgya mtshos zhal bshus
